'''林書豪'''（{{lang-en|Jeremy Shuhow Lin}}，{{bd|1988年|8月23日||}}）是生於美國[[加利福尼亚州|加州]][[托倫斯|托倫斯]]的職業[[籃球|籃球]]運動員，主打[[控球後衛|控球後衛]]位置。

林書豪在[[舊金山灣區|舊金山灣區]]長大，高中時獲得[[北加利福尼亞州|北加州]]年度最佳球員榮耀。在沒有大學提供體育獎學金的情況下，選擇就讀[[哈佛大學|哈佛大學]]，於大學四年間三次入選[[常春藤盟校|常春藤盟校]]年度隊伍。林書豪一開始進入[[國家籃球協會|國家籃球協會]]（NBA）並不順利，在{{tsl|en|List of National Basketball Association undrafted players|NBA選秀落選球員列表|NBA選秀會上落選}}，[[2010-11_NBA賽季|2010年]]與家鄉球隊[[金州勇士|金州勇士]]簽約，但菜鳥年只有零星上場機會，三次被下放至[[D-League|發展聯盟]]。[[2011-12_NBA赛季|2011–12年賽季]]開打前，遭金州勇士和[[休士頓火箭|休士頓火箭]]釋出，後加入[[紐約尼克|紐約尼克]]。

於紐約尼克初期未有上場機會而待在發展聯盟，直到2012年2月林書豪意外帶領紐約尼克創下七連勝、成為球隊先發陣容，期間的表現不僅幫助紐約尼克進入[[2012年NBA季後賽|季後賽]]，也使林書豪一夕成名、風靡全球，掀起一陣「[[#「林來瘋」|林來瘋]]」熱潮，並被《[[時代雜誌|時代雜誌]]》列為2012年[[时代百大人物|百大最具影響力人物]]。林書豪之後效力過休士頓火箭、[[洛杉磯湖人|洛杉磯湖人]]、[[夏洛特黄蜂|夏洛特黄蜂]]、[[布魯克林籃網|布魯克林籃網]]和[[亞特蘭大老鷹|亞特蘭大老鷹]]，[[2019年NBA總決賽|2019年]]隨著[[多倫多暴龍|多倫多暴龍]]奪下NBA總冠軍，同年8月離開NBA轉戰[[中国男子篮球职业联赛|中国男子篮球职业联赛]]（CBA）[[北京鸭首钢篮球俱乐部|北京首鋼]]，並入選[[2020年中国男子篮球职业联赛全明星赛|CBA全明星賽]]，2021年1月加入[[NBA_G聯盟|NBA G聯盟]][[聖克魯斯勇士|聖克魯斯勇士]]，同年6月宣布重返CBA北京首鋼。

== 早年 ==
林書豪（{{lang|en|Jeremy Shuhow Lin}}<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.californiabirthindex.org/birth/jeremy_shuhow_lin_born_1988_18641112 |title=The birth of Jeremy Lin |publisher={{tsl|en|California Birth Index|加州出生索引}} |access-date=2018-06-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180612140206/https://www.californiabirthindex.org/birth/jeremy_shuhow_lin_born_1988_18641112 |archive-date=2018-06-12 |dead-url=no }}</ref>）1988年8月23日在[[加利福尼亚州|加州]][[托倫斯|托倫斯]]出生<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.nba.com/draft2010/prospects/jeremy-lin/ |title=Prospect Profile: Jeremy Lin |work=NBA |accessdate=2016-03-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120210023304/http://www.nba.com/draft2010/prospects/jeremy-lin/ |archive-date=2012-02-10 |dead-url=yes }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |last=McMenamin |first=Dave |title=Jeremy Lin welcomed by Lakers |date=2014-07-24 |publisher=ESPN |accessdate=2020-09-04 |url=https://www.espn.com/los-angeles/nba/story/_/id/11261015/jeremy-lin-introduced-los-angeles-lakers |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20200325184627/https://www.espn.com/los-angeles/nba/story/_/id/11261015/jeremy-lin-introduced-los-angeles-lakers |archivedate=2020-03-25 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite video|title=Jeremy Lin Introductory Press Conference|url=http://www.nba.com/lakers/video/2014/07/24/140724LinPressConmov-3336322/|date=2014-07-24|publisher=NBA|time=3:00|accessdate=2014-07-25|quote=It's good to be back in the state of California. I was born in Torrance, not too far away from here.|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140811004843/http://www.nba.com/lakers/video/2014/07/24/140724LinPressConmov-3336322/|archive-date=2014-08-11|dead-url=no}}</ref>，出身[[舊金山灣區|舊金山灣區]][[帕羅奧圖|帕羅奧圖]]的[[基督徒|基督教]]家庭<ref name="howard-cooper"/><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.thegospelcoalition.org/blogs/justin-taylor/the-faith-of-jeremy-lin-an-interview/|title=The Faith of Jeremy Lin: An Interview|publisher=TheGospelCoalition|date=2012-02-10|accessdate=2012-02-13|archive-date=2018-03-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180323165622/https://www.thegospelcoalition.org/blogs/justin-taylor/the-faith-of-jeremy-lin-an-interview/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite video |title=Jeremy Lin Postgame: Knicks 107 Wiz 93 |url=http://www.nba.com/knicks/video/2012/02/09/postgamelin020812mov-1994988 |date=2012-02-09 |publisher=NBA |time=2:16 |accessdate=2012-02-11 |quote=I was raised in NorCal, but I was actually born in L.A. |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140429170103/http://www.nba.com/knicks/video/2012/02/09/postgamelin020812mov-1994988 |archive-date=2014-04-29 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。林書豪父母的身高剛好都是168公分<ref>{{cite news |last=Hochman |first=Benjamin |title=Hochman: Lin isn't your typical NBA rookie |newspaper=The Denver Post |date=2010-11-28 |url=https://www.denverpost.com/2010/11/27/hochman-lin-isnt-your-typical-nba-rookie/ |accessdate=2010-11-29 |quote=The 6-foot-3 Lin is the son of two 5–6 Taiwanese immigrants and, though the Warriors can't confirm it, it's assumed he's the first Asian-American in the NBA since Wat Misaka played for the New York Knicks in 1947. |archive-date=2018-06-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180628123706/https://www.denverpost.com/2010/11/27/hochman-lin-isnt-your-typical-nba-rookie/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>，外祖母的家庭成員都很高，其中外曾祖父[[陳惟儉|陳惟儉]]身高超過183公分<ref name="brandsher02152012"/>。父親林繼明在[[基督教青年会|基督教青年会]]（YMCA）教導三位兒子打籃球<ref name="ONeil">{{cite web |last=O'Neil |first=Dana |title=Immigrant dream plays out through son: Harvard's do-it-all star learned the game from his father and a host of NBA legends |publisher=ESPN |date=2009-12-10 |url=https://www.espn.com/mens-college-basketball/columns/story?columnist=oneil_dana&id=4730385 |accessdate=2010-11-12 |archive-date=2017-10-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171001032025/http://www.espn.com/mens-college-basketball/columns/story?columnist=oneil_dana&id=4730385 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。母親吳信信協助在帕羅奧圖成立全國青少年籃球（National Junior Basketball）項目，並與教練共事確保籃球運動沒影響到林書豪的學業。儘管吳信信遭到朋友批評讓林書豪花太多時間打籃球，但她因為看到籃球會使林書豪快樂而讓林書豪打球<ref name="New York Times"/>。

林書豪高中就讀{{link-en|帕羅奧圖高中|Palo Alto High School}}，並參加籃球校隊，之後成為球隊隊長。高中十年級（2005年至2006年）在{{link-en|加州校際聯盟|California Interscholastic Federation}}系列賽繳出場均15.1分、6.2籃板、7.1助攻、5.0抄截的成績<ref name="Harvard">{{Cite web |url=https://gocrimson.prestosports.com/sports/mbkb/2009-10/bios/Jeremy_Lin_Bio |title=Jeremy Lin Harvard Basketball Guard |publisher=Go Crimson |date=2010-11-08 |accessdate=2012-02-14 |archive-date=2020-11-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201121175757/https://gocrimson.prestosports.com/sports/mbkb/2009-10/bios/Jeremy_Lin_Bio |dead-url=no }}</ref>，而所屬球隊整個賽季取得32勝1負的戰績，包括决賽以51比47戰勝在美國排名較高的{{tsl|en|Mater Dei High School (Santa Ana, California)|聖母高校}}，贏得加州校際聯盟乙組（CIF Division II）冠軍<ref name="Harvard"/><ref>{{cite news |last=Stephens |first=Mitch |title=BOYS PLAYER OF THE YEAR: Jeremy Lin/A knack for the big play |date=2006-04-02 |newspaper=San Francisco Chronicle |accessdate=2020-09-04 |url=https://www.sfgate.com/preps/article/BOYS-PLAYER-OF-THE-YEAR-Jeremy-Lin-A-knack-for-2538272.php |quote=Palo Alto won 32 of them this season (losing only one), including a 51–47 upset of nationally ranked Mater Dei for the CIF State Division II title at Arco Arena two weeks ago. |archive-date=2020-02-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200209135629/https://www.sfgate.com/preps/article/BOYS-PLAYER-OF-THE-YEAR-Jeremy-Lin-A-knack-for-2538272.php |dead-url=no }}</ref>。林書豪則獲得北加州乙組最佳球員（Northern California Division II Player of the Year）並入選全加州最佳陣容（first-team All-State）<ref name="Harvard"/><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.chnet.co.nz/Html/2013-4-20/News_48329.html|title=人生如「學習做自己」的競賽，關鍵對手是自己！|publisher=先驅報|date=2013-04-20|access-date=2013-05-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131112170331/http://www.chnet.co.nz/Html/2013-4-20/News_48329.html|archive-date=2013-11-12|dead-url=no}}</ref>。[[ESPN|ESPN]]記者丹娜·歐尼爾（Dana O'neal）將林書豪評價為「幾乎各加州相關報導刊物皆會看中的最佳球員」<ref name="ONeil"/>。

== 大學生涯 ==
[[File:Jeremy_Lin.jpg|thumb]]
林書豪高中畢業後將自己的比賽畫面剪輯成[[DVD|DVD]]爭取入學機會，寄送給[[常春藤盟校|常春藤盟校]]八所大學、[[加州大學柏克萊分校|加州大學柏克萊分校]]、[[加州大學洛杉磯分校|加州大學洛杉磯分校]]以及夢寐以求的[[史丹佛大學|史丹佛大學]]<ref name="harvard_school"/><ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.nba.com/hornets/news/hornetscom_1on1_golden_sta_2011_01_06.html|title=Hornets.com 1-on-1: Golden State’s Jeremy Lin|publisher=紐奧良黃蜂|author=Calder Hynes|date=2011-01-05|accessdate=2012-02-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110226105402/http://www.nba.com/hornets/news/hornetscom_1on1_golden_sta_2011_01_06.html|archive-date=2011-02-26|dead-url=yes}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.telegraph.co.uk/sport/othersports/basketball/9074519/Jeremy-Lins-amazing-journey-from-sofa-surfing-to-NBA-stardom-with-New-York-Knicks-in-the-space-of-a-week.html|title=Jeremy Lin's amazing journey from sofa surfing to NBA stardom with New York Knicks - in the space of a week|publisher=The Telegragh|author=Rosa Price|date=2012-02-10|accessdate=2012-02-14|archive-date=2012-02-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120213050608/http://www.telegraph.co.uk/sport/othersports/basketball/9074519/Jeremy-Lins-amazing-journey-from-sofa-surfing-to-NBA-stardom-with-New-York-Knicks-in-the-space-of-a-week.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。[[太平洋十大學聯會|太平洋十大學聯會]]學校希望他成為校隊[[練習生_(體育)|練習生]]，而不是透過招募或提供{{tsl|en|athletic scholarship|體育獎學金}}入隊。[[哈佛大学绯红队|哈佛大學]]和{{tsl|en|Brown Bears|布朗大學熊隊|布朗大學}}是唯二能保證林書豪在球隊中可佔有一席之地的大學籃球隊，但[[常春藤盟校|常春藤盟校]]大學並不提供體育獎學金<ref name="part2_qa">{{cite news |title=Part 2: Q&A with Lin |newspaper=San Francisco Chronicle |date=2010-07-22 |url=https://blog.sfgate.com/warriors/2010/07/22/part-2-qa-with-lin/ |accessdate=2010-11-12 |quote=The Pac-10 schools wanted me to walk-on. The Ivy League schools, Harvard and Brown, were the two ones that really wanted me to go there and play for them. I was deciding mainly between those two conferences.... I didn't really want to walk on. I wanted to go somewhere the team wanted me. Not somewhere I'd have to go and potentially not have a spot on the team. |archive-date=2012-02-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120214223149/http://blog.sfgate.com/warriors/2010/07/22/part-2-qa-with-lin/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。前NBA球員{{tsl|en|Rex Walters|雷克斯·沃爾特斯}}表示，[[國家大學體育協會|國家大學體育協會]]（NCAA）對教練招募考察的限制減少林書豪的機會，「大多數大學在看到一個人的五分鐘之內就會決定招募他，因為他跑得非常快、跳得非常高、做事情迅速，這很容易去評估」<ref name="culpepper">{{Cite web|url=https://www.nytimes.com/2010/09/15/sports/basketball/15nba.html|title=An All-Around Talent, Obscured by His Pedigree|publisher=NY Times|author=Chuck Culpepper|date=2010-09-15|accessdate=2012-02-14|archive-date=2020-03-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200325184835/https://www.nytimes.com/2010/09/15/sports/basketball/15nba.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

哈佛大學助理教練比爾·荷頓（Bill Holden）起初對林書豪的場上能力不以為然，並告訴林書豪的高中籃球教練彼得·迪彭布洛克（Peter Diepenbrock），林書豪是「{{tsl|en|NCAA Division III|NCAA第三級別|第三級別}}的球員」。後來比爾·霍頓看了林書豪在一場競爭十分激烈的比賽中一有機會就帶著「殺手本能（instincts of a killer）」帶球上籃，於是他成為哈佛大學的頭號招募對象<ref>{{cite news|last=Armstrong|first=Kevin|title=Jeremy Lin: The true Hollywood story of the Knick sensation who's taken over New York in less than a week|newspaper=New York Daily News|date=2012-02-11|accessdate=2020-09-04|url=http://www.nydailynews.com/sports/basketball/knicks/jeremy-lin-true-hollywood-story-knick-sensation-york-a-week-article-1.1021119|archive-date=2012-02-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120214184159/http://www.nydailynews.com/sports/basketball/knicks/jeremy-lin-true-hollywood-story-knick-sensation-york-a-week-article-1.1021119|dead-url=no}}</ref>{{r|viera20120213}}。當時哈佛大學的教練們擔心，在林書豪高中對面的史丹佛大學會向他提供獎學金，但史丹佛大學並沒有提供獎學金，最後林書豪選擇進入哈佛大學就讀<ref name="viera20120213">{{cite news |last=Viera |first=Mark |title=Colleges Passed on Lin Before the N.B.A. Did. |date=2012-02-13 |newspaper=The New York Times |accessdate=2020-09-04 |page=D1 |url=https://www.nytimes.com/2012/02/13/sports/basketball/for-knicks-lin-erasing-a-history-of-being-overlooked.html |archive-date=2020-02-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200218033225/https://www.nytimes.com/2012/02/13/sports/basketball/for-knicks-lin-erasing-a-history-of-being-overlooked.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。當時金州勇士老闆、史丹佛大學校內體育俱樂部負責人[[喬·拉科布|喬·拉科布]]曾說，史丹佛大學沒能招募到林書豪「真的很愚蠢，這孩子就在街道對面，（如果）你不能認知到這點，那你就有問題」<ref>{{cite news |last=Kawakami |first=Tim |title=Lacob interview, Part 3: On Jeremy Lin, Ellison, Larry Riley, bold moves and poker |newspaper=San Jose Mercury News |date=2010-08-17 |url=http://blogs.mercurynews.com/kawakami/2010/08/17/lacob-interview-part-3-on-jeremy-lin-ellison-larry-riley-bold-moves-and-poker/ |accessdate=2010-11-08 |quote=I'm a big Stanford fan, but that was really stupid. The kid was right across the street. You can't recognize that, you've got a problem. |archive-date=2020-06-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200627001148/http://blogs.mercurynews.com/kawakami/2010/08/17/lacob-interview-part-3-on-jeremy-lin-ellison-larry-riley-bold-moves-and-poker/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。曾提供林書豪校隊練習生機會的加州大學洛杉磯分校助理教練{{tsl|en|Kerry Keating|凱里·基廷}}事後表示，林書豪原本有機會成為加州大學洛杉磯分校的先發[[控球后卫|控球后卫]]<ref>{{cite news |last=Kroner |first=Steve |title=Playing hard and smart goes a long way for Lin |newspaper=San Francisco Chronicle |date=2010-01-03 |url=https://www.sfgate.com/sports/article/Playing-hard-and-smart-goes-a-long-way-for-Lin-3276751.php |accessdate=2010-11-12 |quote='It's not like I didn't know he wasn't good four or five years ago,' Keating said. 'I watched him win a championship.... In hindsight now, given UCLA's current state, he'd probably be starting for UCLA at point guard.' |archive-date=2012-07-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120719080020/http://www.sfgate.com/sports/article/Playing-hard-and-smart-goes-a-long-way-for-Lin-3276751.php |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

一位哈佛大學教練記得林書豪在大一賽季的時候是「球隊裡（身體）最虛弱的傢伙」<ref name="beck20120225">{{cite news |url=https://www.nytimes.com/2012/02/25/sports/basketball/the-evolution-of-jeremy-lin-as-a-point-guard.html |title=The evolution of a point guard |work=The New York Times |date=2012-02-25 |accessdate=2012-02-26 |author=Beck, Howard |page=D1 |archive-date=2019-08-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190808064918/https://www.nytimes.com/2012/02/25/sports/basketball/the-evolution-of-jeremy-lin-as-a-point-guard.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>，但到大二賽季，林書豪以場均得分12.6分入選常春藤盟校年度第二隊<ref name="Harvard"/>，他到了大三賽季名列[[NCAA第一级别|NCAA第一级别]]前十名最佳男子籃球運動員，並入選常春藤盟校年度第一隊<ref name="ONeil"/>。林書豪在大四賽季於客場對陣排名第12名的[[康涅狄格大学哈士奇队|康乃狄克大學]]時獲得全美關注，他攻下個人在大學比賽記錄裡最高的30分，並抓下9籃板、3助攻、3抄截、2阻攻<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://gocrimson.com/news/2009/12/6/12_6_2009_2528.aspx |title=Lin Dazzles With 30 Points But No. 13 UConn Hangs On, 79–73 |publisher=GoCrimson.com |date=2009-12-06 |accessdate=2012-02-14 |archive-date=2020-11-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201121172519/https://gocrimson.com/news/2009/12/6/12_6_2009_2528.aspx |dead-url=no }}</ref>，康乃狄克名人堂教練{{tsl|en|Jim Calhoun|吉姆·卡爾霍恩}}在比賽結束後表示，「林書豪具有對抗我所見過的任一大學球隊的能力，他在球場上冷靜的表現讓他知道如何面對比赛」<ref name="ONeil"/>。當年林書豪再次入選常春藤盟校年度第一隊，同時被提名進入{{link-en|約翰·伍登獎|John R. Wooden Award}}、[[鮑伯·庫西獎|鮑伯·庫西獎]]候選名單<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://gocrimson.com/news/2010/1/4/1_4_2010_2551 |title=Lin Named John R. Wooden Award Midseason Top 30 Candidate |publisher=GoCrimson.com |date=2010-01-04 |accessdate=2012-02-14 |archive-date=2020-11-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201121172504/https://gocrimson.com/news/2010/1/4/1_4_2010_2551 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.paloaltoonline.com/news/2010/02/09/jeremy-lin-among-11-finalists-for-the-bob-cousy-award |title=Jeremy Lin among 11 finalists for the Bob Cousy Award |publisher=Palo Alto Online |date=2010-02-09 |accessdate=2012-02-14 |archive-date=2014-04-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140427144504/http://www.paloaltoonline.com/news/2010/02/09/jeremy-lin-among-11-finalists-for-the-bob-cousy-award |dead-url=no }}</ref>，並受邀參加{{link-en|普茲茅斯邀請賽|Portsmouth Invitational Tournament}}<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://gocrimson.com/news/2010/2/22/2_22_2010_2581 |title=Lin Selected For Portsmouth Invitational |publisher=GoCrimson.com |date=2010-11-18 |accessdate=2012-02-14 |archive-date=2020-11-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201121172514/https://gocrimson.com/news/2010/2/22/2_22_2010_2581 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。ESPN籃球解說員{{tsl|en|Fran Fraschilla|法蘭·法希納}}將林書豪列為當年度最具才華的12名籃球運動員之一<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://gocrimson.com/news/2009/10/7/10_7_2009_2502 |title=ESPN Names Lin One Of Country's Most Versatile Players |publisher=GoCrimson.com |author=Fran Fraschilla |date=2009-10-07 |accessdate=2012-02-14 |archive-date=2020-11-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201121172519/https://gocrimson.com/news/2009/10/7/10_7_2009_2502 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。林書豪在哈佛校隊的期間，共取得1483分、487籃板、406助攻、225抄截的表現<ref name="Harvard"/>。2010年林書豪以3.1學級分獲得哈佛大學[[经济学|经济学]]學位<ref name="ocregister">{{cite news |author1=Kevin Ding |title=Lin is the NBA’s Asian-American inspiration |url=https://www.ocregister.com/2010/09/03/lin-is-the-nbas-asian-american-inspiration/ |accessdate=2020-09-03 |work=Orange County Register |date=2010-09-03 |archive-date=2020-03-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200325184603/https://www.ocregister.com/2010/09/03/lin-is-the-nbas-asian-american-inspiration/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

== 職業生涯 ==
=== 金州勇士（2010年至2011年） ===
林書豪在大學畢業後參加[[2010年NBA選秀|2010年NBA選秀]]，但未獲得任何球隊的合約<ref>{{cite news|title=After Backing a Dark Horse, Lin's Agent Is Riding High|url=https://www.nytimes.com/2012/03/10/sports/basketball/jeremy-lins-agent-roger-montgomery-is-riding-high.html|newspaper=The New York Times|date=2012-03-10|page=D5|accessdate=2012-03-10|archive-date=2012-03-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120310000427/http://www.nytimes.com/2012/03/10/sports/basketball/jeremy-lins-agent-roger-montgomery-is-riding-high.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。當時球探看到一篇《紐約時報》的文章，描述林書豪是「聰明的傳球員，但跳投有缺陷，而且身材瘦弱。他在NBA可能不具備足夠力量和運動能力進行防守，無法為自己創造投籃機會或是成功上籃」{{r|beck20120225}}。之後林書豪受[[達拉斯獨行俠|達拉斯獨行俠]]總管{{tsl|en|Donnie Nelson||唐尼·尼爾森}}邀請，參加在[[洛杉磯|洛杉磯]]舉辦的[[NBA夏季聯賽|NBA夏季聯賽]]<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://mavsblog.dallasnews.com/archives/2010/06/mavericks-to-bring-in-lin.html |title=Mavericks to bring in Lin |publisher=The Dallas Morning News |author=Eddie Sefko |date=2010-06-25 |accessdate=2012-02-14 |archive-date=2010-06-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100628005229/http://mavsblog.dallasnews.com/archives/2010/06/mavericks-to-bring-in-lin.html |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。林書豪表示，「唐尼很照顧我，他的眼光與大多數人不同」<ref name="part2_qa"/>。林書豪在5場夏季聯賽中擔任控球後衛，場均9.8分、3.2籃板、1.8助攻、1.2抄截<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.nba.com/warriors/news/warriors_sign_jeremy_lin_072110.html|title=WARRIORS: Warriors Sign Free Agent Guard Jeremy Lin|publisher=NBA|date=2010-07-21|accessdate=2012-02-14|archive-date=2012-02-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120212024803/http://www.nba.com/warriors/news/warriors_sign_jeremy_lin_072110.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.espn.com/los-angeles/nba/news/story?id=5392883|title=Harvard guard Lin piques L.A.'s interest|publisher=ESPN|author=David McMenamin|date=2010-07-19|accessdate=2012-02-14|archive-date=2016-10-31|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161031082628/http://www.espn.com/los-angeles/nba/news/story?id=5392883|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=http://voices.washingtonpost.com/dcsportsbog/2010/07/john_wall_vs_jeremy_lin.html|title=John Wall vs. Jeremy Lin|publisher=Washingtonpost|author=Dantitle Steinberg|date=2010-07-16|accessdate=2012-02-14|archive-date=2020-03-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200325185030/http://voices.washingtonpost.com/dcsportsbog/2010/07/john_wall_vs_jeremy_lin.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。達拉斯獨行俠、[[洛杉磯湖人|洛杉磯湖人]]、[[金州勇士|金州勇士]]和[[東區聯盟_(NBA)|東區]]不具名球隊在夏季聯賽結束後向林書豪提出合約<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.thecrimson.com/article/2010/7/20/lin-nba-summer-sign/|title=Jeremy Lin To Sign With Warriors, Reports Say|publisher=The Harvard Crimson|author=Martin Kessler|date=2010-07-20|accessdate=2012-02-14|archive-date=2012-02-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120210084403/http://www.thecrimson.com/article/2010/7/20/lin-nba-summer-sign/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

[[File:Jeremy_Lin_cropped.jpg|thumb]]
2010年7月21日，林書豪與家鄉球隊金州勇士簽下一份兩年部份保障合約，其中第二年為球隊選擇權<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.mercurynews.com/2010/07/20/golden-state-warriors-sign-ex-palo-alto-high-star-jeremy-lin/|title=Golden State Warriors sign ex-Palo Alto High star Jeremy Lin|publisher=Oakland Tribune|author=Marcus Thompson II|date=2010-07-21|accessdate=2012-02-14|archive-date=2017-05-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170508065019/http://www.mercurynews.com/2010/07/20/golden-state-warriors-sign-ex-palo-alto-high-star-jeremy-lin/|dead-url=no}}</ref>，成為繼1954年[[紐約尼克|紐約尼克]]的{{link-en|艾德·史密斯|Ed Smith (basketball)}}之後，第二位進入NBA的哈佛畢業生<ref>{{cite news |author1=Tim Williamson |title=Jeremy Lin ’10 signs with Warriors |url=https://news.harvard.edu/gazette/story/2010/07/jeremy-lin-signs-with-warriors/ |accessdate=2020-09-03 |work=Harvard Gazette |date=2010-07-21 |archive-date=2017-08-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170826042522/http://news.harvard.edu/gazette/story/2010/07/jeremy-lin-signs-with-warriors/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。金州勇士在林書豪簽約後為他召開記者會，結果全國媒體都出席。時任金州勇士總教練{{tsl|en|Keith Smart|基思·斯馬特}}說，「對於一位落選的新秀來說，令人驚訝看到這景象…」<ref>{{cite news |last=Clemmons |first=Anna Katherine |title=Jeremy Lin: NBA's Cinderella story |date=2011-03-16 |publisher=ESPN |url=https://www.espn.com/nba/news/story?page=Lin-110316 |accessdate=2020-09-04 |archive-date=2020-05-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200525082333/https://www.espn.com/nba/news/story?page=Lin-110316 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。《[[聖荷西信使報|聖荷西信使報]]》寫道，林書豪「簽約後有一種[[邪典追捧|邪典追捧]]的感覺」<ref name="thompson_12282011">{{cite news |last=Thompson II |first=Marcus |title=Injured Curry misses practice |date=2011-12-28 |newspaper=San Jose Mercury News |accessdate=2020-09-04 |page=C2 |url=https://www.mercurynews.com/2011/12/27/golden-state-warriors-notebook-stephen-curry-misses-practice-with-bad-ankle/ |archive-date=2020-03-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200325185057/https://www.mercurynews.com/2011/12/27/golden-state-warriors-notebook-stephen-curry-misses-practice-with-bad-ankle/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。擁有大量美國亞裔的[[舊金山灣區|舊金山灣區]]為他的到來慶祝<ref name="beck_12292011">{{cite news |author1=Howard Beck |title=Newest Knick Out to Prove He’s Not Just a Novelty |url=https://www.nytimes.com/2011/12/29/sports/basketball/jeremy-lin-knicks-newest-addition-is-out-to-prove-hes-not-just-a-novelty.html |accessdate=2020-09-03 |work=The New York Times |date=2011-12-28 |archive-date=2019-12-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191209084125/https://www.nytimes.com/2011/12/29/sports/basketball/jeremy-lin-knicks-newest-addition-is-out-to-prove-hes-not-just-a-novelty.html |dead-url=no |quote=Lin, whose parents are from Taiwan, is the N.B.A.’s first American-born player of Chinese or Taiwanese descent. }}</ref>。而林書豪成為首位[[华裔美国人|華裔]]或<!-- 參照來源，來源寫「或」 -->[[臺灣裔美國人|臺裔]]{{tsl|en|Race and ethnicity in the NBA|NBA的種族與族群|美國人在NBA出賽}}<ref name="beck_12292011"/><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.nba.com/2010/news/07/28/lin.taiwan.ap/index.html |title=Warriors' Lin hopes to break new ground in NBA |publisher=NBA |date=2010-07-28 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20101231054535/http://www.nba.com/2010/news/07/28/lin.taiwan.ap/index.html |archivedate=2010-12-31 |accessdate=2010-11-12 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>{{notetag|林書豪2010年在NBA出賽前，已有下列來自亞洲的球員在NBA出賽過：[[王治郅|王治郅]]（中華人民共和國，1999年[[達拉斯獨行俠|達拉斯獨行俠]]）、[[孟克巴特尔|孟克巴特尔]]（中華人民共和國，2001年[[丹佛金塊|丹佛金塊]]）、[[姚明|姚明]]（中華人民共和國，2002年[[休士頓火箭|休士頓火箭]]）、[[田臥勇太|田臥勇太]]（日本，2004年[[鳳凰城太陽|鳳凰城太陽]]）、[[河升鎮|河升鎮]]（韓國，2004年[[波特蘭拓荒者|波特蘭拓荒者]]）、[[易建聯|易建聯]]（中華人民共和國，2007年[[密爾瓦基公鹿|密爾瓦基公鹿]]）、[[孙悦_(篮球运动员)|孙悦]]（中華人民共和國，2008年[[洛杉矶湖人|洛杉矶湖人]]）、[[哈米德·埃哈达迪|哈米德·埃哈达迪]]（伊朗，2008年[[曼非斯灰熊|曼非斯灰熊]]）<ref>{{cite news |author1=Justin Block |title=The Complete History of Asian Players in the NBA |url=https://www.complex.com/sports/2013/09/the-complete-history-of-asian-players-in-the-nba/ |accessdate=2020-09-03 |work=Complex |date=2013-09-13 |archive-date=2019-10-31 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191031214445/https://www.complex.com/sports/2013/09/the-complete-history-of-asian-players-in-the-nba/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |editor=五月清风 |title=亚裔球员20+排行榜 姚明247次领跑林书豪需努力 |url=https://sports.sohu.com/20120207/n333905836.shtml |accessdate=2020-09-03 |work=扬州晚报 |date=2012-02-07 |archive-date=2012-08-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120824232021/http://sports.sohu.com/20120207/n333905836.shtml |dead-url=no }}</ref>。首位在NBA出賽的亞裔美籍球員為[[三阪亙|三阪亙]]（日裔美籍，1947年[[紐約尼克|紐約尼克]]），之後還有{{tsl|en|Raymond Townsend|雷蒙德·唐森}}（菲裔美籍，1978年[[金州勇士|金州勇士]]）、{{tsl|en|Rex Walters|雷克斯·沃爾特斯}}（日裔美籍，1993年[[紐澤西籃網|紐澤西籃網]]）等等球員<ref name="ocregister"/><ref name="beck_12292011"/><ref name="Bleacher Report"/>；美國主流媒體稱林書豪為第四位在NBA出賽的亞裔美籍球員<ref name="ocregister"/><ref name="beck_12292011"/><ref name="Bleacher Report">{{cite news |author1=Peter Chen |title=Five Fast Facts About Jeremy Lin |url=https://bleacherreport.com/articles/1062520-five-fast-facts-about-jeremy-lin |accessdate=2020-09-09 |work=Bleacher Report |date=2012-02-12 |archive-date=2017-05-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170528013305/http://bleacherreport.com/articles/1062520-five-fast-facts-about-jeremy-lin |dead-url=no }}</ref>。}}。

林書豪很感激球迷對他的支持，尤其是來自美國亞裔社區的支持，但他更偏向專注於自己在球場上的表現<ref name="howard-cooper">{{cite news |last=Howard-Cooper |first=Scott |title=Lin faces the rookie grind as an entire community watches on |publisher=NBA |date=2010-10-23 |url=http://www.nba.com/2010/news/features/scott_howard_cooper/10/22/lin-rookie/ |accessdate=2010-11-08 |quote='I think that's tricky, because on one hand you want to be able to focus and play your game and to have the distractions left on the side. But at the same time, to be able to have that type of support is unbelievable.' |archive-date=2018-12-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181215230251/http://www.nba.com/2010/news/features/scott_howard_cooper/10/22/lin-rookie/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>，該賽季林書豪獲得的出賽時間不多，因為金州勇士的兩位當家控球後衛[[史蒂芬·柯瑞|史蒂芬·柯瑞]]和[[蒙塔·埃利斯|蒙塔·埃利斯]]都是球隊主力<ref name="beck_02102012"/>。10月10日，林書豪於對陣[[洛杉磯快艇|洛杉磯快艇]]的熱身賽第四節首度上場<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.espn.com/nba/recap?id=301008009|title=Warriors 127, Clippers 87|publisher=ESPN|date=2010-10-09|accessdate=2012-02-14|archive-date=2017-09-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170909234109/http://www.espn.com/nba/recap?id=301008009|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.sfgate.com/sports/article/Lin-grabs-spotlight-in-exhibition-3171108.php|title=WARRIORS 127, CLIPPERS 87/Lin grabs spotlight in exhibition|newspaper=San Francisco Chronicle|author=Rusty Simmons|date=2010-10-10|accessdate=2012-02-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190327123020/https://www.sfgate.com/sports/article/Lin-grabs-spotlight-in-exhibition-3171108.php|archive-date=2019-03-27|dead-url=no}}</ref>。[[2010-11_NBA賽季|2010–11年賽季]]例行賽開始之初，林書豪被技術性列入傷兵名單<ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.sfgate.com/sports/article/Warriors-Yao-Ming-Jeremy-Lin-ride-bench-3168874.php|title=Warriors: Yao Ming, Jeremy Lin ride bench|newspaper=San Francisco Chronicle|author=Rusty Simmons|date=2010-10-28|accessdate=2012-02-14|quote=Most of the media, and maybe even most of the fans, at Oracle Arena on Wednesday night were there to see Houston center Yao Ming and Warriors guard Jeremy Lin sit the benches on their respective team's inactive lists.|archive-date=2013-06-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130622031928/http://www.sfgate.com/sports/article/Warriors-Yao-Ming-Jeremy-Lin-ride-bench-3168874.php|dead-url=no}}</ref>。但林書豪在下一場金州勇士的亞裔傳統之夜（Asian Heritage Night）首次於NBA亮相，在比賽最後幾分鐘進場時獲得全場的起立鼓掌<ref>{{cite news|title=Monta Ellis, Dorell Wright lead Warriors; Stephen Curry reinjures ankle|publisher=ESPN|agency=Associated Press|date=2010-10-29|url=https://www.espn.com/nba/recap?gameId=301029009|accessdate=2010-11-01|quote=It was Asian Heritage Night at Oracle Arena and the crowd of 17,408 rose in a standing ovation when reserve Jeremy Lin checked into the game with 2:32 remaining in the fourth quarter.|archive-date=2016-08-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160821082237/http://www.espn.com/nba/recap?gameId=301029009|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|last=Lepper|first=Geoff|title=Clippers-Warriors notebook|publisher=NBA|date=2010-10-30|url=http://www.nba.com/games/20101029/LACGSW/gameinfo.html|accessdate=2010-11-01|quote=He was credited with a steal after tying up Cook and watching the Warriors win the ensuing jump ball.|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121109185444/http://www.nba.com/games/20101029/LACGSW/gameinfo.html|archive-date=2012-11-09|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。在接下來對陣洛杉磯湖人的比賽中，林書豪替補上場16分鐘，投進個人NBA生涯首球外帶3助攻4抄截的數據，最後5犯下場<ref>{{cite news|last=Chu|first=Bryan|title=Warriors-Lakers notebook|publisher=NBA|date=2010-11-01|url=http://www.nba.com/games/20101031/GSWLAL/gameinfo.html|accessdate=2010-11-01|quote=The Palo Alto native played only three minutes all season, but played logged 16 minutes, including 11 minutes in the third quarter.|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121109190243/http://www.nba.com/games/20101031/GSWLAL/gameinfo.html|archive-date=2012-11-09|dead-url=yes}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|title=Pau Gasol, Kobe Bryant come up big as Lakers crush Warriors|publisher=ESPN|agency=Associated Press|date=2010-10-31|url=https://www.espn.com/nba/recap?gameId=301031013|accessdate=2010-11-01|quote=Lin committed five fouls in his first 11 minutes, but also played a role in Golden State's 12–1 run in the third.|archive-date=2016-08-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160820234846/http://www.espn.com/nba/recap?gameId=301031013|dead-url=no}}</ref>。11月8日，[[多伦多猛龙|多伦多猛龙]]配合林書豪與金州勇士的到訪，舉行亞裔傳統之夜（Asian Heritage Night）。多倫多20多家華文媒體對比賽進行了報導<ref>{{cite news |title=Stephen Curry scores season-high 34 points; Monta Ellis taken for X-rays |publisher=ESPN |agency=Associated Press |date=2010-11-08 |url=https://www.espn.com/nba/recap?gameId=301108028 |accessdate=2010-11-10 |quote=More than 20 members of Toronto's Chinese media covered the game on Asian Heritage Night, timed to coincide with the visit of Golden State rookie guard Jeremy Lin. |archive-date=2018-11-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181116055453/http://www.espn.com/nba/recap?gameId=301108028 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |last=Thompson II |first=Marcus |title=Golden State Warriors update: Stephen Curry eager to lose his ankle brace sooner than later |newspaper=The Oakland Tribune |date=2010-11-08 |url=https://www.eastbaytimes.com/2010/11/08/golden-state-warriors-update-stephen-curry-eager-to-lose-his-ankle-brace-sooner-than-later/ |accessdate=2010-11-10 |quote=Rookie guard Jeremy Lin saw 15 minutes of action, most of them in the first half. |archive-date=2020-11-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201121172732/https://www.eastbaytimes.com/2010/11/08/golden-state-warriors-update-stephen-curry-eager-to-lose-his-ankle-brace-sooner-than-later/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

