該賽季林書豪三次被下放至金州勇士於[[D-League|發展聯盟]]的附屬球隊[[雷諾大角羊|雷諾大角羊]]<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.nba.com/warriors/news/lin_assigned_dleague_031711.html|title=Warriors Assign Jeremy Lin To Reno Bighorns|work=NBA|date=2010-12-28|accessdate=2012-02-14|archive-date=2012-02-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120210012437/http://www.nba.com/warriors/news/lin_assigned_dleague_031711.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="transactions">{{Cite web|url=http://www.nba.com/dleague/dleague/transactions.html|title=2010–11 transactions|work=NBA|author=|date=2011-01-09|accessdate=2012-02-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20111101144313/http://www.nba.com/dleague/dleague/transactions.html|archive-date=2011-11-01|dead-url=yes}}</ref><ref name="paloaltoon">{{Cite web|url=https://www.paloaltoonline.com/news/2011/12/12/lin-waived-by-warriors-but-picked-up-by-rockets|title=Lin waived by Warriors but picked up by Rockets|work=PaloAltoOnline|date=2011-12-12|accessdate=2012-02-14|archive-date=2013-11-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131112173306/http://www.paloaltoonline.com/news/2011/12/12/lin-waived-by-warriors-but-picked-up-by-rockets|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news |title=Warriors reassign Lin to Bighorns |date=2011-03-17 |newspaper=Reno Gazette-Journal |url=http://www.rgj.com/article/20110318/SPORTS10/103180391 |accessdate=2011-03-18 |quote=Golden State reassigned Jeremy Lin to the Reno Bighorns, the team announced Thursday.}}</ref>，之後都被金州勇士召回<ref name="transactions"/><ref>{{cite news |title=Warriors Recall Jeremy Lin From Reno Bighorns of NBA Development League |url=https://www.nba.com/warriors/news/warriors_recall_jeremy_lin_020511.html |accessdate=2020-09-03 |work=NBA |date=2011-02-05 |archive-date=2013-05-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130530074533/http://www.nba.com/warriors/news/warriors_recall_jeremy_lin_020511.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |title=Warriors Recall Jeremy Lin From Reno Bighorns Of NBA Developmental League |url=https://www.nba.com/warriors/news/warriors_recall_jeremy_lin_032711.html |accessdate=2020-09-03 |work=NBA |date=2011-03-27 |archive-date=2013-05-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130530063627/http://www.nba.com/warriors/news/warriors_recall_jeremy_lin_032711.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。他參加過發展聯盟表演賽，並在2011年1月14日入選發展聯盟表演賽第一隊。在雷諾大角羊20場出賽中，場均18分、5.8籃板和4.4助攻{{r|beck20120225}}。當時金州勇士將林書豪視為史蒂芬·柯瑞的潛在替補{{r|beck20120225}}。喬·拉科布表示，林書豪在發展聯盟時，球隊收到不止一份交易報價，並補充「他是最低限度、廉價的資產。你需要把他看作成長中的資產。但他是否會成為超級明星？不會」<ref>{{cite news |last=Steinmetz |first=Matt |authorlink=Matt Steinmetz |title=Q&A with Warriors owner Joe Lacob |publisher=Comcast SportsNet Bay Area |date=2011-01-20 |accessdate=2020-09-04 |url=http://www.csnbayarea.com/01/20/11/QA-with-Warriors-owner-Joe-Lacob/landing_warriors.html?blockID=395085&feedID=2539 |archive-date=2011-10-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110126094629/http://www.csnbayarea.com/01/20/11/QA-with-Warriors-owner-Joe-Lacob/landing_warriors.html?blockID=395085&feedID=2539 |dead-url=yes }}{{Cbignore}}</ref>。林書豪在29場比賽中以投籃命中率38.9%和場均2.6分完成他的新秀NBA賽季<ref name="paloaltoon"/>。

=== 東莞新世紀（2011年） ===
林書豪於[[2011年NBA停摆|2011年NBA停摆]]期間從{{tsl|en|patellar ligament|膝蓋髕骨韌帶}}傷勢痊癒<ref name="brown_02232012">{{cite news |last=Brown |first=Daniel |title=Bay Area trainers helped make Knicks guard Jeremy Lin better, stronger, faster |date=2012-02-23 |newspaper=San Jose Mercury News |accessdate=2020-09-04 |url=https://www.mercurynews.com/2012/02/23/bay-area-trainers-helped-make-knicks-guard-jeremy-lin-better-stronger-faster/ |archive-date=2019-03-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190327123205/https://www.mercurynews.com/2012/02/23/bay-area-trainers-helped-make-knicks-guard-jeremy-lin-better-stronger-faster/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。林書豪2011年9月底代表[[CBA|CBA]][[东莞新世纪马可波罗|东莞新世纪]]出賽{{tsl|en|ABA Club Championship|男籃亞俱杯}}，共出賽3場繳出場均12.5分、6籃板、3助攻，入選男籃亞俱杯最佳陣容，並獲選為男籃亞俱杯最有價值球員<ref>{{cite web|publisher=新浪体育|title=2011男篮亚俱杯广州开战 林书豪将代表东莞出战|url=http://sports.sina.com.cn/cba/2011-09-27/01305763319.shtml|author=马萨|date=2011-09-27|accessdate=2011-09-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110930101758/http://sports.sina.com.cn/cba/2011-09-27/01305763319.shtml|archive-date=2011-09-30|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news |author1=冯爱军 |title=林书豪独木难支仍捧MVP 作别东莞返美备战NBA |url=https://sports.qq.com/a/20111002/000168.htm |accessdate=2020-09-23 |work=信息时报 |date=2011-10-02 |archive-date=2020-11-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201106000418/https://sports.qq.com/a/20111002/000168.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news|author1=亢雪松|title=东莞遗憾未留下林书豪 主帅:他能改变CBA格局|url=https://sports.qq.com/a/20120213/000425.htm|accessdate=2020-08-26|work=北京晨报|date=2012-02-13|archive-date=2020-08-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200826142335/https://sports.qq.com/a/20120213/000425.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

=== 紐約尼克（2011年至2012年） ===
林書豪於休賽季期間努力改善自己的跳投，放棄從八年級開始就一直使用的投籃姿勢。他還增加自己的力量，把他能[[深蹲|深蹲]]的重量增加一倍（從{{convert|110|lb|kg}}增加到{{convert|231|lb|kg}}），並把他能做[[引體上升|引體上升]]的次數增加近三倍（從12次增加到30次）<ref name="brown_02232012"/>。他把自己的體重從{{convert|200|lb|kg}}增加到{{convert|212|lb|kg}}（包括{{convert|15|lb|kg}}肌肉）。他還分別增加立定[[縱跳|縱跳]]和跑動縱跳的範圍（{{convert|3.5|in|cm}}與{{convert|6|in|cm}}），橫向速度則提高32%{{r|beck20120225}}<ref>{{cite news |last=Ostler |first=Scott |title=Lin shows Warriors' insanity |date=2012-02-26 |newspaper=San Francisco Chronicle |accessdate=2020-09-04 |page=B2 |url=https://www.sfgate.com/sports/article/Lin-shows-Warriors-insanity-3361773.php |archive-date=2019-03-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190327135536/https://www.sfgate.com/sports/article/Lin-shows-Warriors-insanity-3361773.php |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

由於NBA停擺，林書豪一直沒有機會與金州勇士新任總教練[[马克·杰克逊_(1965年)|马克·杰克逊]]訓練<ref>{{cite news |last=Spears |first=Mark J. |title=Jeremy Lin: Knicks' star is Warriors' loss |date=2012-02-13 |publisher=Yahoo! Sports |accessdate=2020-09-04 |url=https://ca.sports.yahoo.com/news/jeremy-lin-knicks-star-warriors-022200048--nba.html |archive-date=2020-11-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201121172904/https://ca.sports.yahoo.com/news/jeremy-lin-knicks-star-warriors-022200048--nba.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。2011年12月9日，金州勇士在訓練營首日為了調整隊伍的[[NBA工资帽|薪資上限]]將林書豪釋出<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://blogs.mercurynews.com/kawakami/2011/12/09/warriors-start-camp-short-handed-wait-for-moves-adapt-to-mark-jackson/|title=Warriors start camp short-handed, wait for moves, adapt to Mark Jackson|publisher=Media News Group|author=Tim Kawakami|date=2011-12-09|accessdate=2012-02-14|archive-date=2020-06-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200629130312/http://blogs.mercurynews.com/kawakami/2011/12/09/warriors-start-camp-short-handed-wait-for-moves-adapt-to-mark-jackson/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.espn.com/blog/truehoop/post/_/id/34619/sources-knicks-warriors-eyeing-jeremy-lin|title=Sources: Knicks, Warriors eyeing Lin|work=ESPN|author=Mark Stein|date=2011-12-27|accessdate=2012-02-14|archive-date=2018-11-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181116055918/http://www.espn.com/blog/truehoop/post/_/id/34619/sources-knicks-warriors-eyeing-jeremy-lin|dead-url=no}}</ref>。12月12日，休士頓火箭簽下林書豪<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.nba.com/2011/news/12/12/rockets-morris.ap/index.html?rss=true|title=Rockets sign rookie forward Morris|work=NBA|date=2011-12-12|accessdate=2012-02-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130925101403/http://www.nba.com/2011/news/12/12/rockets-morris.ap/index.html?rss=true|archive-date=2013-09-25|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。12月24日，休士頓火箭考量到隊上控衛已有[[凱爾·洛里|凱爾·洛里]]、[[戈倫·卓吉奇|戈倫·卓吉奇]]和[[乔尼·弗林|乔尼·弗林]]<ref>{{cite news |last=Thompson II |first=Marcus |title=Jeremy Lin says faith in God triggered 'Lin-sanity' |date=2012-02-13 |newspaper=The San Jose Mercury News |accessdate=2020-09-04 |url=https://www.mercurynews.com/2012/02/13/exclusive-jeremy-lin-says-faith-in-god-triggered-lin-sanity/ |archive-date=2019-03-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190327172358/https://www.mercurynews.com/2012/02/13/exclusive-jeremy-lin-says-faith-in-god-triggered-lin-sanity/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news|last=Jenkins|first=Bruce|title=Jeremy Lin flies in face of conventional wisdom|newspaper=San Francisco Chronicle|date=2012-02-12|url=https://www.sfgate.com/sports/article/Jeremy-Lin-flies-in-face-of-conventional-wisdom-3305474.php|accessdate=2012-02-14|archive-date=2013-06-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130622023209/http://www.sfgate.com/sports/article/Jeremy-Lin-flies-in-face-of-conventional-wisdom-3305474.php|dead-url=no}}</ref>，並打算簽下[[萨缪尔·戴勒姆波特|萨缪尔·戴勒姆波特]]而需清出名單空間，在球季開打前一天將林書豪釋出<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://blog.chron.com/ultimaterockets/2011/12/rockets-release-lin-to-make-room-on-roster-for-dalembert/|title=Rockets release Lin to make room on roster for Dalembert|publisher=Houston Chronicle|author=Jonathan Feigen|date=2011-12-25|accessdate=2012-02-14|archive-date=2012-02-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120211201944/http://blog.chron.com/ultimaterockets/2011/12/rockets-release-lin-to-make-room-on-roster-for-dalembert/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

