紐約尼克將得分後衛[[昌西·比卢普斯|昌西·比卢普斯]]釋出以換取{{tsl|en|cap space|薪資空間}}簽下中鋒[[泰森·钱德勒|泰森·钱德勒]]{{r|mahoney20120211}}。12月27日，紐約尼克在後衛[[伊曼·香珀特|伊曼·香珀特]]受傷後簽下林書豪，擔任[[托尼·道格拉斯|托尼·道格拉斯]]和[[迈克·毕比|迈克·毕比]]的替補後衛，而當時剛簽下的後衛[[貝倫·戴維斯|貝倫·戴維斯]]也受了傷，距離能夠上場比賽還需幾週的時間<ref name="beck_02102012">{{cite news|url=https://www.nytimes.com/2012/02/10/sports/basketball/jeremy-lins-success-with-knicks-surprises-everyone.html|title=Lin’s Success Surprising to Everyone|newspaper=The New York Times|author=Howard Beck|date=2012-02-10|accessdate=2012-02-14|archive-date=2019-04-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190414081541/https://www.nytimes.com/2012/02/10/sports/basketball/jeremy-lins-success-with-knicks-surprises-everyone.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="Howard Beck"/><ref>{{cite news |last=Stein |first=Mark |title=Knicks claim guard Jeremy Lin |date=2011-12-27 |publisher=ESPN |accessdate=2020-09-04 |url=https://www.espn.com/new-york/nba/story/_/id/7392484/new-york-knicks-claim-guard-jeremy-lin-waivers-houston-rockets |archive-date=2020-05-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200525074539/https://www.espn.com/new-york/nba/story/_/id/7392484/new-york-knicks-claim-guard-jeremy-lin-waivers-houston-rockets |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |last=Brennan |first=Sean |title=Harvard grad Jeremy Lin claimed off waivers by NY Knicks; Asian-American guard offers backcourt insurance |date=2011-12-27 |newspaper=New York Daily News |accessdate=2020-09-04 |url=https://www.nydailynews.com/sports/basketball/knicks/harvard-grad-jeremy-lin-claimed-waivers-ny-knicks-asian-american-guard-offers-backcourt-insurance-article-1.997304 |archive-date=2019-04-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190405041853/https://www.nydailynews.com/sports/basketball/knicks/harvard-grad-jeremy-lin-claimed-waivers-ny-knicks-asian-american-guard-offers-backcourt-insurance-article-1.997304 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。教練因為NBA停擺，幾乎沒有機會看到林書豪的實力，於是將他排在控衛{{tsl|en|Depth chart|深度圖表|板凳深度}}的第四位{{r|beck20120225}}。林書豪表示自己是在「爭奪一個替補位置」，還說有人把他「看成是名單上第12到15號的傢伙」<ref name="thompson_12282011"/>；他持續在訓練中第一位到場、最後一位離開、專心研究比賽影片、和教練一起努力加強自己的腳步和判斷力{{r|beck20120225}}。林書豪在紐約尼克客場對陣金州勇士的比賽中首次賽季亮相，回到甲骨文球館的他受到全場歡呼<ref name="Howard Beck">{{cite news |last=Beck |first=Howard |title=Knicks' Strengths Vanish, and So Do Hopes of Winning |date=2011-12-29 |newspaper=The New York Times |accessdate=2020-09-04 |url=https://www.nytimes.com/2011/12/29/sports/basketball/warriors-use-second-half-run-to-beat-the-knicks.html |archive-date=2020-03-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200325185342/https://www.nytimes.com/2011/12/29/sports/basketball/warriors-use-second-half-run-to-beat-the-knicks.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。2012年1月，林書豪被下放到發展聯盟的[[伊利海鷹|伊利海鷹]]<ref>{{cite news|last=Beck|first=Howard|title=Knicks Send Two Bench Warmers to D-League|date=2012-01-17|newspaper=The New York Times|url=http://offthedribble.blogs.nytimes.com/2012/01/17/knicks-demote-two-bench-warmers|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120118231948/http://offthedribble.blogs.nytimes.com/2012/01/17/knicks-demote-two-bench-warmers/|dead-url=yes|archive-date=2012-01-18|accessdate=2012-01-19}}</ref><ref>{{cite news |title=〈NBA〉林書豪下放發展聯盟　生涯第4度 |url=http://www.espnstar.com.tw/news/basketball/2012/0118/225627.htm |publisher=ESPN中文網 |date=2012-01-18 |accessdate=2012-02-09 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120221031605/http://www.espnstar.com.tw/news/basketball/2012/0118/225627.htm |archivedate=2012-02-21 }}</ref>，1月20日在伊利海鷹以122比113戰勝[[緬因紅爪|緬因紅爪]]的比賽中攻下28分、11籃板和12助攻的三雙成績<ref>{{cite news |title=Lin Picks Up Triple-Double As Erie Drops Maine 122–113 |date=2012-01-20 |url=http://www.nba.com/dleague/games/20120120/ERIMNE/gameinfo.html |publisher=NBA |accessdate=2012-01-20 |dead-url=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120123052215/http://www.nba.com/dleague/games/20120120/ERIMNE/gameinfo.html |archivedate=2012-01-23 }}</ref>。三天後林書豪被紐約尼克召回<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.nba.com/dleague/erie/knicks_recall_jordan__lin_2012_01_23.html |title=Knicks Recall Jordan & Lin |publisher=NBA |accessdate=2012-01-23 |dead-url=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120131223246/http://www.nba.com/dleague/erie/knicks_recall_jordan__lin_2012_01_23.html |archivedate=2012-01-31 }}</ref>，但非常害怕再次被裁，於是在賽前的祈禱儀式上請一位牧師為他祈禱<ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.nytimes.com/2012/02/25/sports/basketball/lins-new-challenge-media-onslaught-at-all-star-weekend.html|title=Lin's New Challenge: Media Onslaught at All-Star Weekend|date=2012-02-25|newspaper=The New York Times|accessdate=2012-02-26|author=Beck, Howard|archive-date=2012-02-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120225225709/http://www.nytimes.com/2012/02/25/sports/basketball/lins-new-challenge-media-onslaught-at-all-star-weekend.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

1月28日，貝倫·戴維斯因肘部感染和背部疼痛而推遲在紐約尼克的首秀<ref name="beck_02122012"/><ref name="berman"/>，球隊盤算簽下另一名球員，正考慮將林書豪釋出<ref name="berman"/>。然而在2月3日輸給[[波士顿凯尔特人|波士顿凯尔特人]]的比賽，紐約尼克浪費掉第四節的領先優勢，總教練[[迈克·德安东尼|迈克·德安东尼]]在絕望中決定給林書豪一個上場機會<ref name="berman">{{cite news |last=Berman |first=Marc |title=Phenom nearly found himself out of NBA |date=2012-02-12 |accessdate=2019-10-07 |newspaper=New York Post |url=https://nypost.com/2012/02/12/phenom-nearly-found-himself-out-of-nba/ |archive-date=2019-10-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191007114154/https://nypost.com/2012/02/12/phenom-nearly-found-himself-out-of-nba/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。總教練說，「他很幸運，因為我們打得太差了」<ref name="berman"/>；三分射手已經無法運行迈克·德安东尼的進攻戰術，而且球迷要求球隊解僱總教練{{r|mahoney20120211}}。林書豪在紐約尼克的前23場比賽中只打了55分鐘，球隊在過去的13場比賽中輸了11場；然而他卻意外帶領紐約尼克重新崛起<ref>{{cite news |title=Jeremy Lin: How long will stardom last for the surprising New York Knicks' phenom? Poll |date=2012-02-13 |publisher=cleveland |accessdate=2020-09-04 |url=https://www.cleveland.com/ohio-sports-blog/2012/02/jeremy_lin_how_long_will_stard.html |archive-date=2020-11-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201121173055/https://www.cleveland.com/ohio-sports-blog/2012/02/jeremy_lin_how_long_will_stard.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |last=Schneider |first=Christian |title=Jeremy Lin and the Element of Surprise |date=2012-02-20 |publisher=National Review Online |accessdate=2020-09-04 |url=https://www.nationalreview.com/corner/jeremy-lin-and-element-surprise-christian-schneider/ |archive-date=2021-05-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210512160000/https://www.nationalreview.com/corner/jeremy-lin-and-element-surprise-christian-schneider/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

2月4日，在對陣新澤西籃網和[[NBA全明星赛|全明星]]後衛[[德隆·威廉姆斯|德隆·威廉姆斯]]的比賽中，林書豪替補上場36分鐘，得到全場最高的25分，外帶7助攻、5籃板和2抄截的成績，帶領紐約尼克以99比92獲得勝利。隊友[[卡梅隆·安东尼|卡梅隆·安东尼]]在中場休息時向迈克·德安东尼建議讓林書豪下半場多上場。賽後迈克·德安东尼表示，林書豪有一個控球後衛的靈魂，「他在外面（球場）所作的一切都有自己的節奏或理由」<ref>{{cite news|last=Back|first=Howard|title=Lin Sparks Knicks, to Crowd's Delight and D'Antoni's Relief|url=https://www.nytimes.com/2012/02/05/sports/basketball/lin-leads-knicks-over-nets.html|newspaper=The New York Times|date=2012-02-05|accessdate=2012-02-11|archive-date=2020-02-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200215221440/https://www.nytimes.com/2012/02/05/sports/basketball/lin-leads-knicks-over-nets.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="thompson_02132012"/><ref name="ap_02202012"/><ref>{{cite news |title=主帥表態讓林書豪先發：他有控衛的靈魂 |url=http://www.espnstar.com.tw/news/basketball/2012/0206/227182.htm |publisher=ESPN中文網 |date=2012-02-06 |accessdate=2012-02-09 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120209025254/http://www.espnstar.com.tw/news/basketball/2012/0206/227182.htm |archivedate=2012-02-09 }}</ref>。2月6日，林書豪在沒有卡梅隆·安东尼和[[阿玛雷·斯塔德迈尔|阿玛雷·斯塔德迈尔]]的情況下，主場對戰猶他爵士的比賽中迎來職業生涯的首次先發。林書豪帶領紐約尼克以99比88擊敗對手。林書豪上場45分鐘，再次得到全場最高的28分，外帶8助攻，此場生涯首度先發成績，在NBA歷史名列第二；僅次於1981年[[底特律活塞|底特律活塞]]控衛[[以賽亞·湯瑪斯|以賽亞·湯瑪斯]]生涯首度先發，得到31分11助攻的成績<ref>{{cite news |title=數據：林書豪破30年紀錄 石佛納許不服老 |url=http://www.espnstar.com.tw/news/basketball/2012/0208/227416.htm |publisher=ESPN中文網 |date=2012-02-08 |accessdate=2012-02-09 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120211150424/http://www.espnstar.com.tw/news/basketball/2012/0208/227416.htm |archivedate=2012-02-11 }}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.wsj.com/articles/SB10001424052970204369404577207891254439140|title=Knicks 99, Jazz 88: Depleted Knicks Still Get Best of Jazz|date=2012-02-06|work=The Wall Street Journal|accessdate=2012-02-07|archive-date=2015-04-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150405114625/http://www.wsj.com/articles/SB10001424052970204369404577207891254439140|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="toronto_feb14"/>。迈克·德安东尼在賽後表示，他打算「以怪異的[[秘書處_(競賽馬)|秘書處]]方式」駕馭著林書豪<ref>{{cite news|title=Jeremy Lin leads Knicks with Stoudemire gone|date=2012-02-07|work=CBS News|agency=Associated Press|accessdate=2020-09-04|url=http://www.cbsnews.com/8301-400_162-57372427/jeremy-lin-leads-knicks-with-stoudemire-gone|archive-date=2012-04-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120424171451/http://www.cbsnews.com/8301-400_162-57372427/jeremy-lin-leads-knicks-with-stoudemire-gone|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="torre_03272015"/>。阿玛雷·斯塔德迈尔和卡梅隆·安东尼分別缺席接下來的3場和7場比賽<ref name="ap_02202012">{{cite news |title=Deron Williams pours in 38 as Nets thwart Jeremy Lin, Knicks in Carmelo Anthony's return |date=2012-02-20 |publisher=ESPN |agency=Associated Press |accessdate=2020-09-04 |url=https://www.espn.com/nba/recap?gameId=320220018 |archive-date=2019-12-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191227101925/https://www.espn.com/nba/recap?gameId=320220018 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="toronto_feb14"/>。
{{quote box|align=left|width=30%|style=padding:10px|quote=表現如此優異的球員們通常不會突然冒出來。他們看似突然冒出來，但如果你能回過頭看看，他（林書豪）的球技或許在一開始就具備，可能只是被忽視。|source=—[[科比·布莱恩特|科比·布莱恩特]]，2012年2月10日<ref>{{cite news |last=Hunt |first=Christopher |title=Lin makes Lakers believe the hype |date=2012-02-11 |publisher=ESPN |accessdate=2020-09-04 |url=https://www.espn.com/blog/new-york/knicks/post/_/id/11352/lin-makes-lakers-believe-the-hype |quote=Players playing that well don't usually come out of nowhere. It seems like they come out of nowhere, but if you can go back and take a look, his skill level was probably there from the beginning. It probably just went unnoticed. |archive-date=2020-05-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200525101736/https://www.espn.com/blog/new-york/knicks/post/_/id/11352/lin-makes-lakers-believe-the-hype |dead-url=no }}</ref>。}}
2月8日，紐約尼克客場出戰[[華盛頓巫師|華盛頓巫師]]，林書豪對上[[约翰·沃尔|约翰·沃尔]]再度繳出23分、10助攻、5籃板的表現，達成NBA生涯首次[[两双|两双]]<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.espn.com/nba/recap?gameId=320208027|title=Jeremy Lin dazzles again as Knicks rip Wiz for 3rd straight win|publisher=ESPN|date=2012-02-09|accessdate=2012-02-09|archive-date=2020-03-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200325185426/https://www.espn.com/nba/recap?gameId=320208027|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2月10日，在主場[[麥迪遜花園廣場|麥迪遜花園廣場]]對陣[[洛杉矶湖人|洛杉矶湖人]]的比賽中攻下38分，另送出7助攻，得分贏過對手[[科比·布莱恩特|科比·布莱恩特]]的34分，率領紐約尼克以92比85戰勝洛杉磯湖人<ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.foxnews.com/sports/lin-scores-38-to-lead-knicks-over-lakers-92-85|title=Lin scores 38 to lead Knicks over Lakers 92–85|date=2012-02-10|agency=Associated Press|accessdate=2012-02-11|archive-date=2020-11-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201106000729/https://www.foxnews.com/sports/lin-scores-38-to-lead-knicks-over-lakers-92-85|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news |last=Pedulla |first=Tom |title=Even Kobe impressed by 'Lin-sational' Knicks |date=2012-02-09 |accessdate=2020-09-04 |url=https://usatoday30.usatoday.com/sports/basketball/nba/story/2012-02-09/Lins-third-career-high-in-a-row-leads-Knicks-past-Lakers/53045018/1 |archive-date=2014-11-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141102070658/http://usatoday30.usatoday.com/sports/basketball/nba/story/2012-02-09/Lins-third-career-high-in-a-row-leads-Knicks-past-Lakers/53045018/1 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。當時《紐約時報》想知道林書豪是否是自[[1985年NBA选秀|1985年NBA选秀]]遴選[[帕特里克·尤因|帕特里克·尤因]]以來，「紐約尼克最重大的一筆財富」<ref>{{cite news |last=Araton |first=Harvey |title=Lin Keeps His Cool; Around Him, Heads Spin |date=2012-02-12 |newspaper=The New York Times |accessdate=2020-09-04 |page=SP3 |url=https://www.nytimes.com/2012/02/12/sports/basketball/the-knicks-jeremy-lin-keeps-his-cool-as-heads-spin-around-him.html |archive-date=2019-10-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191006040203/https://www.nytimes.com/2012/02/12/sports/basketball/the-knicks-jeremy-lin-keeps-his-cool-as-heads-spin-around-him.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。2月11日，林書豪在以100比98險勝[[明尼苏达森林狼|明尼苏达森林狼]]的比賽中得到20分和8助攻，其中在比賽還剩4.9秒時罰進超前球<ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.nytimes.com/2012/02/12/sports/basketball/lin-lifts-knicks-past-timberwolves.html|title=Lin LIfts Knicks past Timberwolves|first=Pat|last=Borzi|date=2012-02-11|newspaper=The New York Times|accessdate=2020-09-04|archive-date=2019-10-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191006035713/https://www.nytimes.com/2012/02/12/sports/basketball/lin-lifts-knicks-past-timberwolves.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。林書豪被評為[[2011-12_NBA赛季|東區單週最佳球員]]，他在4場比賽中場均27.3分、8.3助攻和2.0抄截；紐約尼克在這4場比賽中保持不敗<ref>{{cite press release |publisher=National Basketball Association |title=Knicks' Lin, Thunder's Westbrook named Players of the Week |date=2012-02-13 |accessdate=2020-09-04 |url=https://pr.nba.com/jeremy-lin-russell-westbrook-nba-players-of-the-week/ |archive-date=2020-11-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201121173215/https://pr.nba.com/jeremy-lin-russell-westbrook-nba-players-of-the-week/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

2月14日，林書豪在紐約尼克以90比87戰勝[[多倫多暴龍|多倫多暴龍]]的比賽最後還剩不到1秒的時候，投進終場致勝三分球<ref name="toronto_feb14">{{cite web|url=https://www.espn.com/nba/recap?id=320214028|title=Jeremy Lin hits game-winning 3 as Knicks top Raptors|publisher=ESPN|accessdate=2012-02-15|date=2012-02-14|archive-date=2018-08-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180823210657/http://www.espn.com/nba/recap?id=320214028|dead-url=no}}</ref>，這波進球讓在電視前觀賽的洛杉磯湖人驚呆，其中老將[[慈善·福特-阿堤斯|慈善·福特-阿堤斯]]跑到記者身邊大喊「Linsanity！Linsanity！」，並將雙手揮舞到頭頂上<ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.espn.com/los-angeles/nba/story/_/id/7579495/when-los-angeles-lakers-let-fun-shows|title=When Lakers have fun, it shows|publisher=ESPN|date=2012-02-15|accessdate=2012-02-19|author=McMenamin, Dave|archive-date=2016-09-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160904221956/http://www.espn.com/los-angeles/nba/story/_/id/7579495/when-los-angeles-lakers-let-fun-shows|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.latimes.com/sports/la-xpm-2012-feb-14-la-sp-lakers-hawks-20120215-story.html|title=Lakers and Kobe Bryant keep hitting low points, even in victory|work=Los Angeles Times|date=2012-02-14|accessdate=2012-02-19|author=Bresnahan, Mike|archive-date=2019-12-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191227102146/https://www.latimes.com/sports/la-xpm-2012-feb-14-la-sp-lakers-hawks-20120215-story.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。林書豪成為首位在前五次先發都能得到至少20分、並有7助攻的NBA球員<ref>{{cite news |last=Brown |first=Daniel |title=Jeremy Lin: Fernando Valenzuela understands Lin-Sanity first hand |date=2012-02-16 |newspaper=San Jose Mercury News |accessdate=2020-09-04 |url=https://www.mercurynews.com/2012/02/16/jeremy-lin-fernando-valenzuela-understands-lin-sanity-first-hand/ |archive-date=2018-08-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180828085458/https://www.mercurynews.com/2012/02/16/jeremy-lin-fernando-valenzuela-understands-lin-sanity-first-hand/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。林書豪在職業生涯的前3次、4次和5次先發中分別共攻下89分、109分和136分，這三項總得分都是自1976-77年[[美國籃球協會|美國籃球協會]]（ABA）和NBA合併以來所有球員的最佳紀錄<ref>{{cite news|last=Smith|first=Sekou|title=Linsanity ... Five and Counting!|date=2012-02-13|publisher=NBA|url=http://hangtime.blogs.nba.com/2012/02/12/linsanity-five-and-counting/|access-date=2012-02-13|archive-date=2012-02-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120215074637/http://hangtime.blogs.nba.com/2012/02/12/linsanity-five-and-counting/|dead-url=yes}}</ref><ref>{{cite news |last=Zwerling |first=Jared |title=Five Lin-sane stats from Lakers game |date=2012-02-11 |publisher=ESPN |accessdate=2020-09-04 |url=https://www.espn.com/blog/new-york/knicks/post/_/id/11337/five-lin-sane-stats-from-lakers-game |archive-date=2020-05-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200525055248/https://www.espn.com/blog/new-york/knicks/post/_/id/11337/five-lin-sane-stats-from-lakers-game |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news|title=Lin-vestigating History|publisher=ESPN|url=https://www.espn.com/blog/truehoop/post/_/id/36972/lin-vestigating-history|date=2012-02-15|accessdate=2012-02-15|archive-date=2018-08-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180823210626/http://www.espn.com/blog/truehoop/post/_/id/36972/lin-vestigating-history|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

