在接下來對陣[[沙加緬度國王|沙加緬度國王]]的比賽中，林書豪傳出13次助攻，帶領紐約尼克以100比85獲勝、重回勝率50%<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.espn.com/nba/recap?gameId=320215018|title=Jeremy Lin dishes out 13 assists in Knicks' rout of Kings|publisher=ESPN|accessdate=2012-02-15|date=2012-02-15|archive-date=2018-10-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181018201748/http://www.espn.com/nba/recap?gameId=320215018|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2月17日，球隊的七連勝在主場以85比89輸給[[新奧尔良黃蜂|新奧尔良黃蜂]]後中止；林書豪得到26分，但有9次失誤。他職業生涯前7場先發比賽的45次失誤，是自1977–78年賽季開始追蹤個人失誤以來最多的一次<ref>{{cite news |title=Hornets slow down Jeremy Lin, snap Knicks' winning streak |agency=Associated Press |date=2012-02-17 |accessdate=2020-09-04 |url=https://www.espn.com/nba/recap?gameId=320217018 |archive-date=2019-04-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190405054744/http://www.espn.com/nba/recap?gameId=320217018 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

2月19日，在以104比97戰勝達拉斯獨行俠的比賽中，林書豪得到28分、生涯新高的14助攻和5抄截。《今日美國》寫道，「無論達拉斯向林書豪拋出什麼，雙人包夾、陷阱、突擊、高大的防守者…比較矮小的防守者…身材高大的、瘦弱的，林書豪都能找到辦法…取得對戰NBA衛冕軍的勝利」<ref>{{cite news|url=https://usatoday30.usatoday.com/sports/basketball/nba/story/2012-02-19/Lin-leads-Knicks-past-defending-champion-Mavericks/53154848/1|title=Lin keeps improving as Knicks beat the Mavericks|work=USA Today|date=2012-02-19|accessdate=2012-02-23|author=Zillgitt, Jeff|archive-date=2018-07-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180725112536/https://usatoday30.usatoday.com/sports/basketball/nba/story/2012-02-19/Lin-leads-Knicks-past-defending-champion-Mavericks/53154848/1|dead-url=no}}</ref>。在對陣邁阿密熱火的比賽中，他的表現不盡如人意，11投1中、出現8次失誤。[[勒布朗·詹姆斯|勒布朗·詹姆斯]]、[[德维恩·韦德|德维恩·韦德]]、[[克里斯·波什|克里斯·波什]]以及其他目標劍指NBA總冠軍的隊友，將他們的全部防守都集中在林書豪身上，他將這次經歷形容為「受寵若驚、嚴峻的…我感覺他們都像老鷹一樣圍著我轉、雙眼直視著我」{{r|leitch201211}}。

圍繞著林書豪突然崛起的熱潮被稱作廣為所知的「[[#「林來瘋」|林來瘋]]」（Linsanity）。在全明星賽前的12場比賽中，林書豪場均22.5分和8.7助攻，紐約尼克的戰績為9勝3負<ref>{{cite news |last=Smallwood |first=John |title=Setting the stage for NBA second half |date=2012-02-28 |newspaper=Philadelphia Daily News |accessdate=2020-09-04 |url=http://www.philly.com/philly/sports/sixers/140677303.html |archive-date=2012-03-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120301090025/http://www.philly.com/philly/sports/sixers/140677303.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。林書豪最初被遺漏在[[NBA新秀挑战赛|NBA新秀挑战赛]]18人名單之外，但在林書豪突然間成名後名單擴大至20人，破例增列林書豪和邁阿密熱火後衛[[诺里斯·科尔|诺里斯·科尔]]<ref>{{cite news|last=Beck|first=Howard|newspaper=The New York Times|accessdate=2020-09-04|title=Lin, a Rising Star, Needs a Break|date=2012-02-24|url=http://offthedribble.blogs.nytimes.com/2012/02/24/lin-a-rising-star-needs-a-break/|archive-date=2019-10-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191001001441/https://offthedribble.blogs.nytimes.com/2012/02/24/lin-a-rising-star-needs-a-break/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news |title=Jeremy Lin added to Rising Stars game |url=https://www.espn.com/new-york/nba/story/_/id/7581045/nba-adds-new-york-knicks-jeremy-lin-miami-heat-norris-cole-rookie-sophomore-game |accessdate=2020-09-03 |work=ESPN |date=2012-02-16 |archive-date=2017-03-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170305135345/http://www.espn.com/new-york/nba/story/_/id/7581045/nba-adds-new-york-knicks-jeremy-lin-miami-heat-norris-cole-rookie-sophomore-game/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。一些美國媒體，包括《[[今日美國|今日美國]]》、《[[洛杉磯時報|洛杉磯時報]]》和{{tsl|en|CBSSports.com|CBSSports.com}}，認為林書豪值得參加[[2012年NBA全明星賽|NBA全明星賽]]<ref>{{cite news |last=Brennan |first=Christine |title=NBA, Stern missing All-Star opportunity with Lin |date=2012-02-15 |newspaper=USA Today |accessdate=2020-09-04 |url=https://usatoday30.usatoday.com/sports/columnist/brennan/story/2012-02-15/david-stern-should-put-jeremy-lin-in-all-star-game/53111474/1 |archive-date=2019-06-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190628064930/https://usatoday30.usatoday.com/sports/columnist/brennan/story/2012-02-15/david-stern-should-put-jeremy-lin-in-all-star-game/53111474/1 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |last=Schilken |first=Chuck |title=Should the Knicks' Jeremy Lin play in the All-Star game? |date=2012-02-16 |accessdate=2020-09-04 |url=https://www.latimes.com/sports/sportsnow/la-sp-sn-jeremy-lin-poll-20120217-story.html |archive-date=2018-12-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181205134012/https://www.latimes.com/sports/sportsnow/la-sp-sn-jeremy-lin-poll-20120217-story.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |last=Doyel |first=Gregg |title=When it comes to All-Star Game, forget rules and let Lin play |date=2012-02-17 |publisher=CBSSports.com |accessdate=2020-09-04 |url=https://www.cbssports.com/nba/story/17304162/when-it-comes-to-allstar-game-forget-rules-and-let-lin-play |archive-date=2015-12-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151211210902/http://www.cbssports.com/nba/story/17304162/when-it-comes-to-allstar-game-forget-rules-and-let-lin-play |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

