紐約尼克在3月迎來新任總教練[[麥克·伍德森|麥克·伍德森]]將迈克·德安东尼換下，麥克·伍德森減少了擋拆戰術、增加了單打機會。林書豪在迈克·德安东尼執教下曾擅長執行擋拆戰術<ref>{{cite news |last=Begley |first=Ian |title=Jeremy Lin still Knicks starter |date=2012-03-16 |publisher=ESPN |accessdate=2020-09-04 |url=https://www.espn.com/new-york/nba/story/_/id/7696738/mike-woodson-jeremy-lin-remain-new-york-knicks-starting-pg |archive-date=2018-08-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180823210724/http://www.espn.com/new-york/nba/story/_/id/7696738/mike-woodson-jeremy-lin-remain-new-york-knicks-starting-pg |dead-url=no }}</ref>。在3月24日對[[底特律活塞|底特律活塞]]的比賽後，林書豪抱怨膝蓋疼痛，經[[核磁共振成像|核磁共振成像]]檢查顯示左膝[[半月板|半月板]]小範圍撕裂。林書豪選擇接受膝蓋手術，並缺席賽季剩餘的例行賽<ref>{{cite news|last=Beck|first=Howard|title=Lin Out for Rest of Regular Season With Knee Injury|url=https://www.nytimes.com/2012/04/01/sports/basketball/jeremy-lin-to-have-knee-surgery-will-miss-rest-of-regular-season.html|work=The New York Times|date=2012-04-01|accessdate=2012-03-31|archive-date=2012-04-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120401015632/http://www.nytimes.com/2012/04/01/sports/basketball/jeremy-lin-to-have-knee-surgery-will-miss-rest-of-regular-season.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.espn.com/new-york/nba/story/_/id/7759848/jeremy-lin-new-york-knicks-surgery-torn-meniscus|title=Jeremy Lin has torn meniscus|publisher=ESPN|accessdate=2012-03-31|date=2012-03-31|archive-date=2017-02-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170205021712/http://www.espn.com/new-york/nba/story/_/id/7759848/jeremy-lin-new-york-knicks-surgery-torn-meniscus|dead-url=no}}</ref>。林書豪在作為日常球員（everyday player）的26場比賽中，場均18.5分和7.6助攻<ref name="beck_07062012">{{cite news |last=Beck |first=Howard |title=Knicks Know Lin's Price, but Value? Not Exactly |date=2012-07-07 |newspaper=The New York Times |accessdate=2020-09-04 |url=https://www.nytimes.com/2012/07/07/sports/basketball/uncertain-about-his-value-knicks-expected-to-match-jeremy-lins-offer.html |archive-date=2018-09-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180930194801/https://www.nytimes.com/2012/07/07/sports/basketball/uncertain-about-his-value-knicks-expected-to-match-jeremy-lins-offer.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>；在此期間，球隊取得16勝10負的戰績<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://nationalpost.com/pmn/sports-pmn/basketball-sports-pmn/linsanity-revisited-a-look-at-jeremy-lins-brief-time-as-a-basketball-phenomenon|title=‘Linsanity’ revisited – A look at Jeremy Lin’s brief time as a basketball phenomenon | National Post|first=P. M. N.|last=Basketball|date=2019-02-11|accessdate=2020-09-04}}</ref>。紐約尼克以36勝30負的戰績結束賽季，並獲得東區季後賽的第七種子<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.cbssports.com/nba/news/2012-nba-playoffs-preview-miami-heat-vs-new-york-knicks/|title=2012 NBA Playoffs Preview: Miami Heat vs. New York Knicks|website=CBSSports.com|date=2012-04-27|accessdate=2020-09-04|archive-date=2020-05-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200516052315/https://www.cbssports.com/nba/news/2012-nba-playoffs-preview-miami-heat-vs-new-york-knicks/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。在少了受傷的林書豪的情況下<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.newsday.com/sports/basketball/jeremy-lin-wins-the-epic-award-1.3796431|title=Jeremy Lin wins 'The Epic Award'|author=Bobby Bonett|date=2012-06-21|website=Newsday|accessdate=2020-09-04|archive-date=2020-06-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200603031708/https://www.newsday.com/sports/basketball/jeremy-lin-wins-the-epic-award-1.3796431|dead-url=no}}</ref>，紐約尼克在季後賽首輪被最終贏得NBA總冠軍的邁阿密熱火以5場比賽擊敗<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.nytimes.com/2012/05/10/sports/basketball/knicks-season-ends-in-a-game-5-rout-by-the-heat.html|title=Knicks’ Season Ends in a Game 5 Rout by the Heat|first=Howard|last=Beck|date=2012-05-09|work=NYTimes|accessdate=2020-09-04|archive-date=2019-05-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190529093158/https://www.nytimes.com/2012/05/10/sports/basketball/knicks-season-ends-in-a-game-5-rout-by-the-heat.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.miaminewtimes.com/news/miami-heat-are-2012-nba-finals-champions-6526110|title=MIAMI HEAT ARE 2012 NBA FINALS CHAMPIONS|first=Chris|last=Joseph|date=2012-06-22|work=Miami New Times|accessdate=2020-09-04|archive-date=2019-05-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190529093158/https://www.miaminewtimes.com/news/miami-heat-are-2012-nba-finals-champions-6526110|dead-url=no}}</ref>；林書豪在[[NBA进步最快球员|NBA进步最快球员]]的投票中獲得第六名<ref>{{cite web |title=Magic’s Ryan Anderson wins 2011-12 Kia NBA Most Improved Player Award |url=https://pr.nba.com/ryan-anderson-2011-12-kia-nba-most-improved-player-award/ |website=NBA Communications |accessdate=2020-07-09 |archive-date=2020-07-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200712070246/https://pr.nba.com/ryan-anderson-2011-12-kia-nba-most-improved-player-award/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

林書豪在賽季結束後成為受限自由球員<ref name="beck_02122012">{{cite news|last=Beck|first=Howard|title=Knicks in a Position to Keep Lin|date=2012-02-11|newspaper=The New York Times|page=SP3|url=http://offthedribble.blogs.nytimes.com/2012/02/11/knicks-in-a-position-to-keep-lin/|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120214110058/http://offthedribble.blogs.nytimes.com/2012/02/11/knicks-in-a-position-to-keep-lin/|dead-url=yes|archive-date=2012-02-14|accessdate=2012-02-13}}</ref>。《紐約時報》稱林書豪為「（紐約尼克）過去十年來最受歡迎的球員」，並斷言他拯救球隊的賽季<ref>{{cite news |last=Beck |first=Howard |title=Growing Doubts on Lin's Return to the Knicks |date=2012-07-16 |newspaper=The New York Times |accessdate=2020-09-04 |url=https://www.nytimes.com/2012/07/16/sports/basketball/jeremy-lin-may-not-return-to-the-knicks.html |archive-date=2019-04-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190402030622/https://www.nytimes.com/2012/07/16/sports/basketball/jeremy-lin-may-not-return-to-the-knicks.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。然而他僅在26場比賽中取得成功，讓各隊對他在聯盟控衛中的整體地位感到不確定；一些人仍然認為林書豪是板凳球員<ref name="beck_07062012"/>。

2016年7月，前紐約尼克總教練迈克·德安东尼回憶說，在林來瘋時期，一些紐約尼克球員對林書豪感到憎惡，林書豪的前紐約尼克隊友阿玛雷·斯塔德迈尔也證實該說法<ref>{{Cite web |author=Stefan Bondy |date=2016-07-13 |title=Some Knicks had 'real' resentment for Jeremy Lin, says D'Antoni |url=https://www.nydailynews.com/sports/basketball/nets/mike-antoni-knicks-real-resentment-jeremy-lin-article-1.2710144 |work=New York Daily News |access-date=2016-09-28 |quote=The current Rockets coach also acknowledged what Amar'e Stoudemire previously stated: there was resentment from players, including Anthony, for Jeremy Lin. |archive-date=2017-01-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170128154201/http://www.nydailynews.com/sports/basketball/nets/mike-antoni-knicks-real-resentment-jeremy-lin-article-1.2710144 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.nydailynews.com/sports/basketball/knicks/amar-stoudemire-throws-shade-carmelo-anthony-article-1.2546844|title=Amar'e Stoudemire throws shade at Carmelo Anthony prior to Knicks game vs. Heat|work=New York Daily News|first=Stefan|last=Bondy|date=2016-03-01|accessdate=2016-09-28|archive-date=2016-10-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161002092839/http://www.nydailynews.com/sports/basketball/knicks/amar-stoudemire-throws-shade-carmelo-anthony-article-1.2546844|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

=== 休士頓火箭（2012年至2014年） ===
[[File:Jeremy_Lin_and_Chandler_Parsons.jpg|thumb]]在板凳席交談]]
2012年休賽期間，紐約尼克鼓勵林書豪尋求其他報價，但鑑於紐約尼克需要一名年輕後衛、他的優異表現以及席捲全球的人氣，林書豪和媒體都預計紐約尼克會重新簽下他；ESPN報導稱，紐約尼克會跟進任何其他報價，「最高可達10億美元」<ref name="leitch201211">{{cite news|url=https://www.gq.com/story/jeremy-lin-gq-november-2012-cover-story|title=Rocket Man|work=GQ|date=November 2012|accessdate=2012-10-17|author=Leitch, Will|archive-date=2015-09-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150929005414/http://www.gq.com/story/jeremy-lin-gq-november-2012-cover-story|dead-url=no}}</ref>。休士頓火箭開出一份4年2880萬美元的合約，第四年為球隊選擇權<ref name="taylor">{{cite news|url=https://www.nytimes.com/2012/07/14/sports/basketball/jeremy-lin-signs-offer-sheet-putting-knicks-on-the-clock.html|title=Lin Signs Offer Sheet With Rockets, Putting Knicks on the Clock|date=2012-07-14|work=The New York Times|first=Nate|last=Taylor|accessdate=2020-09-04|archive-date=2019-04-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190402043307/https://www.nytimes.com/2012/07/14/sports/basketball/jeremy-lin-signs-offer-sheet-putting-knicks-on-the-clock.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。麥克·伍德森表示，紐約尼克會跟進休士頓火箭的報價，林書豪將成為他的先發控衛<ref name="taylor"/>。隨後休士頓火箭開出一份修改後的3年2500萬美元合約，卡梅隆·安东尼稱其為「荒謬」<ref name="beck_07162012"/><ref>{{cite magazine |last=Saslow |first=Eli |title=Carmelo Anthony Means Business |date=2014-11-20 |magazine=ESPN The Magazine |accessdate=2020-09-04 |url=http://www.espn.com/espn/feature/story/_/id/11904296/new-york-knicks-forward-carmelo-anthony-wants-bulletproof-reputation |archive-date=2020-01-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200127182635/http://www.espn.com/espn/feature/story/_/id/11904296/new-york-knicks-forward-carmelo-anthony-wants-bulletproof-reputation |dead-url=no }}</ref>。林書豪從紐約尼克簽下[[雷蒙德·费尔顿|雷蒙德·费尔顿]]的決定推斷出，紐約尼克沒有跟進這份合約{{r|leitch201211}}。休士頓火箭開給林書豪的條件為，第一年500萬、第二年520萬、第三年1490萬美元的年薪<ref>{{cite news |title=Knicks won't keep Jeremy Lin |date=2012-07-17 |publisher=ESPN |accessdate=2020-09-04 |url=https://www.espn.com/new-york/nba/story/_/id/8175591/new-york-knicks-confirm-match-houston-rockets-offer-jeremy-lin |archive-date=2020-05-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200525053003/https://www.espn.com/new-york/nba/story/_/id/8175591/new-york-knicks-confirm-match-houston-rockets-offer-jeremy-lin |dead-url=no }}</ref>，最後一年較高的薪水，被稱為毒藥合約，目的是為了阻止紐約尼克跟進報價<ref>{{cite news |last=Manfred |first=Tony |title=A Quick Explanation Of The 'Poison Pill' Contract That Could Stop The Knicks From Signing Jeremy Lin |date=2012-07-02 |publisher=businessinsider |accessdate=2020-09-04 |url=https://www.businessinsider.com/jeremy-lin-could-leave-knicks-2012-7 |archive-date=2019-09-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190917152930/https://www.businessinsider.com/jeremy-lin-could-leave-knicks-2012-7 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。紐約尼克沒有跟進報價讓評論員們感到驚訝，其中ESPN的{{tsl|en|Stephen A. Smith|史蒂芬·史密斯}}表示，根據紐約尼克的高薪歷史，林書豪能成為第四高薪的紐約尼克球員{{r|leitch201211}}。

休士頓火箭將林書豪作為季前賽「新時代」（A New Age）宣傳活動的中心，同時也是他們在{{tsl|en|Comcast SportsNet Houston|康卡斯特體育網休士頓}}最初的廣告門面<ref name="barron_07112014">{{cite news |last=Barron |first=David |title=Jeremy Lin: From face of Rockets to trade to Lakers in two years |date=2014-07-11 |newspaper=Houston Chronicle |accessdate=2020-09-04 |url=https://blog.chron.com/ultimaterockets/2014/07/jeremy-lin-from-face-of-rockets-to-trade-to-lakers-in-two-years/ |archive-date=2019-03-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190327101913/https://blog.chron.com/ultimaterockets/2014/07/jeremy-lin-from-face-of-rockets-to-trade-to-lakers-in-two-years/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。休士頓火箭總教練[[凯文·麦克海尔|凯文·麦克海尔]]表示，從林書豪在紐約的林來瘋出現以來，人們對林書豪的期待是不恰當的。凯文·麦克海尔緊接說，眾人相信林書豪會「場均28（分）和11（助攻）」，但他之前從未打滿整整82場比賽<ref name="longman_04212013">{{cite news |last=Longman |first=Jere |title=From Phenom to Everyday N.B.A. Player |date=2013-04-22 |newspaper=The New York Times |accessdate=2020-09-04 |url=https://www.nytimes.com/2013/04/22/sports/basketball/rockets-jeremy-lin-has-focused-on-improving-his-game.html |archive-date=2018-12-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181203055910/https://www.nytimes.com/2013/04/22/sports/basketball/rockets-jeremy-lin-has-focused-on-improving-his-game.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。在10月例行賽開賽前不久，休士頓火箭透過交易獲得[[詹姆斯·哈登|詹姆斯·哈登]]，詹姆斯·哈登取代林書豪成為球隊的代言人<ref name="barron_07112014"/><ref name="barron_05042013">{{cite news |last=Barron |first=David |title=Rockets' oft-criticized Lin promises improvement |date=2013-05-04 |accessdate=2020-09-04 |newspaper=Houston Chronicle |url=https://blog.chron.com/ultimaterockets/2013/05/jeremy-lin-i-have-a-really-long-way-to-go/ |archive-date=2019-03-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190327102723/https://blog.chron.com/ultimaterockets/2013/05/jeremy-lin-i-have-a-really-long-way-to-go/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。詹姆斯·哈登和林書豪一樣，都是大量持球者、會執行擋拆戰術的球員<ref name="espn_10172015">{{cite news |title=Jeremy Lin: Was open to return to Knicks, but team not interested |date=2015-10-17 |website=ESPN |accessdate=2020-09-04 |url=https://www.espn.com/nba/story/_/id/13909889/jeremy-lin-says-agent-contacted-newyork-knicks-return-team-not-interested |archive-date=2019-12-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191226043908/https://www.espn.com/nba/story/_/id/13909889/jeremy-lin-says-agent-contacted-newyork-knicks-return-team-not-interested |dead-url=no }}</ref>，凯文·麦克海尔選擇讓更有經驗的詹姆斯·哈登來進行球隊的進攻<ref name="devine_12122012"/><ref>{{cite news |last=Jones |first=Tao |title=Linsanity Redux: How Much Does New York Miss Jeremy Lin? |date=2013-11-15 |newspaper=The Wall Street Journal |accessdate=2020-09-04 |url=https://www.wsj.com/articles/BL-SEB-78282 |archive-date=2020-11-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201121173606/https://www.wsj.com/articles/BL-SEB-78282 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

林書豪在賽季初期表現掙扎、開始失去上場時間，被替補[[托尼·道格拉斯|托尼·道格拉斯]]取代。2012年12月10日，林書豪在詹姆斯·哈登因傷缺席的情況下於以126比134延長賽輸給[[圣安东尼奥马刺|圣安东尼奥马刺]]的比賽中得到38分，讓人們想起他在林來瘋時期的表現<ref>{{cite news |last=Joseph |first=Adi |title=Linsanity: Jeremy Lin finally breaks out for Houston Rockets |date=2012-12-11 |newspaper=USA Today |accessdate=2020-09-04 |url=https://www.usatoday.com/story/sports/nba/rockets/2012/12/11/jeremy-lin-linsanity-houston-san-antonio-spurs/1760257/ |archive-date=2019-12-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191225152500/https://www.usatoday.com/story/sports/nba/rockets/2012/12/11/jeremy-lin-linsanity-houston-san-antonio-spurs/1760257/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |last=Freeman |first=Eric |title=Jeremy Lin recaptures Linsanity in loss to Spurs |date=2012-12-11 |publisher=Yahoo |accessdate=2020-09-04 |url=https://sports.yahoo.com/jeremy-lin-recaptures-linsanity-loss-spurs-video-144626985--nba.html |archive-date=2020-11-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201121175903/https://sports.yahoo.com/jeremy-lin-recaptures-linsanity-loss-spurs-video-144626985--nba.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。整個賽季的數據表明，詹姆斯·哈登和林書豪在對方坐板凳的情況下，個人效率會更高<ref name="devine_12122012"/>。林書豪在回到紐約的首場比賽面對紐約尼克之前說，「我會成為自己最嚴厲的批評者，但我會繼續說下去：我做得很糟糕」<ref name="devine_12122012">{{cite news |last=Devine |first=Dan |title=Jeremy Lin on his play with Rockets before return to MSG to face Knicks: 'I'm doing terrible' |date=2012-12-12 |publisher=Yahoo |accessdate=2020-09-04 |url=https://sports.yahoo.com/jeremy-lin-play-rockets-return-msg-vs-knicks-204143447--nba.html |archive-date=2020-11-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201121173630/https://sports.yahoo.com/jeremy-lin-play-rockets-return-msg-vs-knicks-204143447--nba.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。12月17日，休士頓火箭以109比96擊敗紐約尼克，送給紐約尼克過去11場主場的首場敗北。林書豪該場得到22分和9助攻。他在賽前介紹中得到全場歡呼，但比賽開始後卻遭到噓聲伺候<ref>{{cite news |last=Taylor |first=Nate |title=In Return, Lin Plays as if He Never Left |date=2012-12-18 |newspaper=New York Times |accessdate=2020-09-04 |url=https://www.nytimes.com/2012/12/18/sports/basketball/jeremy-lin-helps-hand-knicks-their-first-home-loss.html |archive-date=2018-12-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181203061524/https://www.nytimes.com/2012/12/18/sports/basketball/jeremy-lin-helps-hand-knicks-their-first-home-loss.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

[[File:Kevin_McHale_2013_playoffs.jpg|thumb]]期間，休士頓火箭總教練[[凯文·麦克海尔|凯文·麦克海尔]]與林書豪（7號）和他的隊友對話]]
林書豪沒有參加2013年在休士頓舉行的[[2013年NBA全明星賽|NBA全明星賽]]，他在[[西區聯盟_(NBA)|西區]]後衛的投票中僅次於科比·布莱恩特和[[克里斯·保罗|克里斯·保罗]]、排名第三{{notetag|[[科比·布莱恩特|科比·布莱恩特]]以1,591,437票領先所有NBA球員，[[克里斯·保罗|克里斯·保罗]]則有929,155票，領先林書豪的883,809票<ref>{{cite news |last=Barron |first=David |title=Familiar faces dominate All-Star starters |date=2013-01-17 |newspaper=Houston Chronicle |accessdate=2020-09-04 |url=https://blog.chron.com/ultimaterockets/2013/01/lebron-and-wade-named-all-star-starters/ |archive-date=2018-07-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180725112431/https://blog.chron.com/ultimaterockets/2013/01/lebron-and-wade-named-all-star-starters/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。}}；但他代表球隊參加全明星周末期間的[[NBA技巧赛|技術挑戰賽]]，以35.8秒完成賽事，排名第四<ref>{{cite news |last=Deveney |first=Sean |title=Jeremy Lin learned a lot in 12 months, but this Rocket still hasn't launched |date=2013-02-16 |publisher=SportingNews |accessdate=2020-09-04 |url=https://www.sportingnews.com/us/nba/story/2013-02-16/all-star-game-2013-jeremy-lin-linsanity-skill-challenge-future-rockets |archive-date=2020-11-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201121173648/https://www.sportingnews.com/us/nba/story/2013-02-16/all-star-game-2013-jeremy-lin-linsanity-skill-challenge-future-rockets |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |title=NBA／「技術挑戰賽」！林書豪35.8秒完賽　居第4 |url=https://news.tvbs.com.tw/tech/195314 |accessdate=2020-08-26 |work=TVBS |date=2013-02-17 |archive-date=2020-08-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200826142338/https://news.tvbs.com.tw/tech/195314 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。全明星賽後，他的得分、投籃命中率和三分球命中率都有所提升<ref name="barron_05042013"/>。《紐約時報》在2013年2月報導稱他與休士頓火箭「融合地很好」<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.nytimes.com/2013/02/24/sports/basketball/jeremy-lin-is-fitting-in-well-with-the-rockets.html|title=Lin Does a Lot by Not Doing Too Much|first=Beckley|last=Mason|date=2013-02-23|via=NYTimes|accessdate=2020-09-04|archive-date=2020-02-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200221180244/https://www.nytimes.com/2013/02/24/sports/basketball/jeremy-lin-is-fitting-in-well-with-the-rockets.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。該賽季例行賽結束後，林書豪完成生涯首次參與整個賽季，全勤打滿82場球賽，每場皆擔任先發，繳出場均13.4分和6.1助攻的成績<ref name="longman_04212013"/><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.cna.com.tw/News/FirstNews/201304180072-1.aspx|title=林書豪全勤 率火箭飛進季後賽|agency=中央通訊社|date=2013-04-18|access-date=2013-05-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130510020428/http://www.cna.com.tw/News/FirstNews/201304180072-1.aspx|archive-date=2013-05-10|dead-url=no}}</ref>。休士頓火箭獲得季後賽資格，但在首輪以6場比賽輸給第一號種子[[俄克拉何马城雷霆|俄克拉何马城雷霆]]。4月21日，林書豪生涯首次在季後賽出賽，上場32分鐘，2罰2中，繳出4分、4助攻、3籃板、2抄截<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.cna.com.tw/News/aSaM/201304220283-1.aspx|title=季後賽首戰落敗 豪：還要學習|agency=中央通訊社|date=2013-04-22|access-date=2013-05-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130424010652/http://www.cna.com.tw/News/aSaM/201304220283-1.aspx|archive-date=2013-04-24|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。林書豪在第二戰右胸挫傷，這限制他在第三戰和之後兩場比賽的表現<ref>{{cite news |title=Jeremy Lin back for Game 6 |date=2013-05-03 |publisher=ESPN |accessdate=2020-09-04 |url=https://www.espn.com/nba/playoffs/2013/story/_/id/9239363/2013-nba-playoffs-jeremy-lin-houston-rockets-return-game-6 |archive-date=2019-07-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190717101322/https://www.espn.com/nba/playoffs/2013/story/_/id/9239363/2013-nba-playoffs-jeremy-lin-houston-rockets-return-game-6 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。他在最後一場比賽回歸，替補出賽13分鐘得到3分<ref name="barron_05042013"/>。在季後賽他一共出戰的4場比賽中，僅留下場均4分、2助攻、2籃板的成績<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.ettoday.net/news/20130514/207125.htm|title=坦言季後賽受挫　林書豪喊話：想成為全方位射手|publisher=ETtoday|date=2013-05-14|access-date=2013-05-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130607234252/http://www.ettoday.net/news/20130514/207125.htm|archive-date=2013-06-07|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

{{tsl|en|2013–14 Houston Rockets season|2013-14 休士頓火箭賽季|2013–14年賽季}}，林書豪在休士頓火箭先發陣容中被[[帕特里克·贝弗利|帕特里克·贝弗利]]取代，成為球隊的[[第六人|第六人]]，為第二陣容的主要控球者和得分選擇<ref>{{cite news |last=Araton |first=Harvey |title=Lin Is Better Off (and Better) |date=2013-11-13 |newspaper=The New York Times |accessdate=2020-09-04 |url=https://www.nytimes.com/2013/11/14/sports/basketball/jeremy-lin-got-away-from-the-knicks-then-got-better-with-the-rockets.html |archive-date=2018-12-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181205150252/https://www.nytimes.com/2013/11/14/sports/basketball/jeremy-lin-got-away-from-the-knicks-then-got-better-with-the-rockets.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |last=Devine |first=Dan |title=Surging Jeremy Lin hopes to 'be a subplot' as Rockets visit MSG to take on Knicks |date=2013-11-14 |publisher=Yahoo |accessdate=2020-09-04 |url=https://sports.yahoo.com/surging-jeremy-lin-hopes-subplot-rockets-visit-msg-214543980--nba.html |archive-date=2020-11-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201121173747/https://sports.yahoo.com/surging-jeremy-lin-hopes-subplot-rockets-visit-msg-214543980--nba.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |last=Lynam |first=Dei |title=Sixers' hands full with super-sub Jeremy Lin |date=2013-11-13 |publisher=nbcsports |accessdate=2020-09-04 |url=http://www.csnphilly.com/basketball-philadelphia-sixers/sixers-hands-full-super-sub-jeremy-lin |archive-date=2013-11-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131114013000/http://www.csnphilly.com/basketball-philadelphia-sixers/sixers-hands-full-super-sub-jeremy-lin |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。11月林書豪代替受傷的詹姆斯·哈登出賽，創下職業生涯最高的兩場比賽總得分65分，其中包括賽季最高的34分和11助攻，還包括締造休士頓火箭隊史紀錄的9記三分球<ref name="ap_11142013"/><ref name="freidman">{{cite news |last=Friedman |first=Jason |title=Year In Review: Jeremy Lin |website=Rockets |accessdate=2020-09-04 |url=http://www.nba.com/rockets/news/year-review-jeremy-lin |archive-date=2014-06-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140601040534/http://www.nba.com/rockets/news/year-review-jeremy-lin |dead-url=no }}</ref>。林書豪緊接著在戰勝紐約尼克的比賽中得到21分<ref name="ap_11142013">{{cite news |title=Rockets withstand Carmelo Anthony's 45 points to down Knicks |date=2013-11-14 |publisher=ESPN |agency=Associated Press |accessdate=2020-09-04 |url=https://www.espn.com/nba/recap?id=400488996 |archive-date=2020-05-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200525065731/https://www.espn.com/nba/recap?id=400488996 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。11月27日，他在對陣[[亚特兰大老鹰|亚特兰大老鹰]]的比賽中扭傷右膝；因傷缺席6場比賽<ref>{{cite news |title=Jeremy Lin (knee) out 2 weeks |date=2013-11-29 |publisher=ESPN |accessdate=2020-09-04 |url=https://www.espn.com/nba/story/_/id/10052443/jeremy-lin-houston-rockets-miss-2-week-knee-sprain |archive-date=2019-12-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191225191703/https://www.espn.com/nba/story/_/id/10052443/jeremy-lin-houston-rockets-miss-2-week-knee-sprain |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |title=LaMarcus Aldridge scores 31, gets 25 rebounds as Blazers top Rockets |date=2013-12-12 |publisher=ESPN |agency=Associated Press |accessdate=2020-09-04 |url=https://www.espn.com/nba/recap?gameId=400489201 |archive-date=2020-05-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200525055517/https://www.espn.com/nba/recap?gameId=400489201 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。12月他又因為[[背痛|背痛]]缺席4場比賽<ref>{{cite news |title=Rockets report: Lin back in fold, aims to improve |date=2013-12-23 |newspaper=Houston Chronicle |accessdate=2020-09-04 |url=https://www.houstonchronicle.com/sports/rockets/article/Rockets-report-Lin-returns-from-back-issues-5089866.php |archive-date=2020-11-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201121173753/https://www.houstonchronicle.com/sports/rockets/article/Rockets-report-Lin-returns-from-back-issues-5089866.php |dead-url=no }}</ref>。2014年2月1日，林書豪在主場以106比92戰勝克里夫蘭騎士的比賽中，替補上場29分鐘，攻下15分、11籃板、10助攻、2抄截，寫下個人NBA生涯首度大三元<ref>{{cite news|title=Jeremy Lin's 1st career triple-double propels Rockets|date=2014-02-01|publisher=ESPN|agency=Associated Press|accessdate=2020-09-04|url=https://www.espn.com/nba/recap?gameId=400489574|archive-date=2019-12-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191226201153/https://www.espn.com/nba/recap?gameId=400489574|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news |author1=杜奕君 |title=姚明也做不到！ 林書豪生涯「大三元」寫歷史 |url=https://sports.ettoday.net/news/321791 |accessdate=2020-08-26 |work=ETtoday |date=2014-02-02 |archive-date=2016-08-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160826153947/http://sports.ettoday.net/news/321791 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。然而他的投籃手感在全明星賽後陷入低迷<ref>{{cite news |last=Dial Creech |first=Jenny |title=Jeremy Lin mired in shooting slump |date=2014-03-02 |newspaper=Houston Chronicle |accessdate=2020-09-04 |url=https://blog.chron.com/ultimaterockets/2014/03/jeremy-lin-mired-in-shooting-slump/ |archive-date=2019-03-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190327135456/https://blog.chron.com/ultimaterockets/2014/03/jeremy-lin-mired-in-shooting-slump/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>，並再次出現背部問題<ref>{{cite news |last=Riccobono |first=Anthony |title=Jeremy Lin Injury News: Has Rockets Point Guard Played Hurt In Recent Games? |newspaper=International Business Times |date=2014-03-05 |accessdate=2020-09-04 |url=https://www.ibtimes.com/jeremy-lin-injury-news-has-rockets-point-guard-played-hurt-recent-games-1559541 |archive-date=2019-03-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190327102625/https://www.ibtimes.com/jeremy-lin-injury-news-has-rockets-point-guard-played-hurt-recent-games-1559541 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |last=Feigen |first=Jonathan |title=Dwight Howard and Jeremy Lin miss practice due to back issues |date=2014-03-04 |newspaper=Houston Chronicle |accessdate=2020-09-04 |url=https://blog.chron.com/ultimaterockets/2014/03/dwight-howard-and-jeremy-lin-miss-practice-due-to-back-issues/ |archive-date=2019-03-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190327161950/https://blog.chron.com/ultimaterockets/2014/03/dwight-howard-and-jeremy-lin-miss-practice-due-to-back-issues/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

林書豪在該賽季完成33次先發，場均12.5分和4.1助攻，同時在場均命中率（44.6%）、三分球命中率（35.8%）和罰球命中率（82.3%）上都創下生涯新高<ref name="barron_07112014"/><ref name="pincus_08212014">{{cite news |last=Pincus |first=Eric |title=San Francisco's Madame Tussauds to unveil Jeremy Lin figure |date=2014-08-21 |newspaper=Los Angeles Times |accessdate=2020-09-04 |url=https://www.latimes.com/sports/lakers/lakersnow/la-sp-ln-madame-tussauds-jeremy-lin-figure-20140821-story.html |archive-date=2019-12-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191226074606/https://www.latimes.com/sports/lakers/lakersnow/la-sp-ln-madame-tussauds-jeremy-lin-figure-20140821-story.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。林書豪在季後賽中場均11.3分，休士頓火箭以6場比賽輸給[[波特兰开拓者|波特兰开拓者]]。在第五戰的勝利中，他攻下21分，為休士頓火箭延長該賽季的賽程<ref name="freidman"/>。休士頓火箭於休賽期間在自由市場追求林書豪的前紐約尼克隊友卡梅隆·安东尼，並在其場館外展示卡梅隆·安东尼身穿印有林書豪的背號7號的休士頓火箭球衣照片<ref>{{cite news |author1=Ian Begley |title=Rockets show image of Melo in No. 7 |url=https://www.espn.com/nba/story/_/id/11168612/houston-rockets-dis-jeremy-lin-image-carmelo-anthony-no-7 |accessdate=2020-09-04 |work=ESPN |date=2014-07-03 |archive-date=2019-12-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191228020052/https://www.espn.com/nba/story/_/id/11168612/houston-rockets-dis-jeremy-lin-image-carmelo-anthony-no-7 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |last=Pincus |first=Eric |title=Jeremy Lin knows there's a lot of work ahead for Lakers and himself |date=2014-07-24 |newspaper=Los Angeles Times |accessdate=2020-09-04 |url=https://www.latimes.com/sports/lakers/la-sp-jeremy-lin-lakers-20140725-story.html |archive-date=2019-12-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191228020924/https://www.latimes.com/sports/lakers/la-sp-jeremy-lin-lakers-20140725-story.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

=== 洛杉磯湖人（2014年至2015年） ===
[[File:John_Wall_vs_Jeremy_Lin.jpg|thumb]]的[[約翰·沃爾|約翰·沃爾]]]]
2014年7月13日，林書豪連同2015年第一輪選秀權及第二輪選秀權被交易到[[洛杉矶湖人|洛杉矶湖人]]，換回{{tsl|en|Serhiy Lishchuk|謝爾蓋·利甚丘克}}的簽約權<ref>{{cite news|title=Lakers Acquire Jeremy Lin and Draft Choices in Trade with Rockets|date=2014-07-13|accessdate=2014-07-13|publisher=NBA|url=https://www.nba.com/lakers/news/140713jeremylin|archive-date=2014-07-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140714203358/http://www.nba.com/lakers/news/140713jeremylin|dead-url=no}}</ref>；休士頓火箭此舉是為了清理薪資上限空間，試圖簽下自由球員克里斯·波什<ref>{{cite news |last=Lowe |first=Zach |title=Free Agency Winners and Losers |date=2014-07-15 |publisher=grantland |accessdate=2020-09-04 |url=http://grantland.com/features/2014-nba-free-agency-winners-and-losers-houston-rockets-chandler-parsons/ |archive-date=2020-01-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200104073021/http://grantland.com/features/2014-nba-free-agency-winners-and-losers-houston-rockets-chandler-parsons/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。林書豪在賽季中的三分球命中率達到生涯最高的36.9%，但他在球隊的角色定位並沒有很明確<ref>{{cite news |last=Pandian |first=Anath |title=Jeremy Lin enjoying consistent role in his new home with Charlotte Hornets |date=2015-11-08 |website=CBSSports.com |accessdate=2020-09-04 |url=https://www.cbssports.com/nba/news/jeremy-lin-enjoying-consistent-role-in-his-new-home-with-charlotte-hornets/ |archive-date=2020-11-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201121173849/https://www.cbssports.com/nba/news/jeremy-lin-enjoying-consistent-role-in-his-new-home-with-charlotte-hornets/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

林書豪在[[罗尼·普莱斯|罗尼·普莱斯]]受傷後，於季前賽後期進入先發陣容，他在該賽季前20場比賽都先發上場<ref name="helin_12072014"/>。然而他在總教練[[拜伦·斯科特|拜伦·斯科特]]的進攻模式中表現得很掙扎，而這種進攻模式是基於{{tsl|en|Princeton offense|普林斯頓進攻}}中井然有序的球員和球的流動。林書豪對於效力紐約尼克和休士頓火箭時，大量持球和執行擋拆戰術感到舒適<ref name="torre_03272015"/><ref name="helin_12072014">{{cite news|last=Helin|first=Kurt|title=Jeremy Lin, Carlos Boozer benched by Lakers; Ronnie Price, Ed Davis start|date=2014-12-07|publisher=NBC Sports|accessdate=2020-09-04|url=http://probasketballtalk.nbcsports.com/2014/12/07/jeremy-lin-carlos-boozer-benched-by-lakers-ronnie-price-ed-davis-to-start/|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20141208053019/http://probasketballtalk.nbcsports.com/2014/12/07/jeremy-lin-carlos-boozer-benched-by-lakers-ronnie-price-ed-davis-to-start/|archivedate=2014-12-08|dead-url=no}}</ref>。拜伦·斯科特在球隊5勝15負的糟糕開局後試圖改善洛杉磯湖人糟糕的防守，於是將林書豪調整至替補，改讓籃球浪人罗尼·普莱斯出賽<ref>{{cite news|last=Ramirez|first=Joey|title=Price, Davis to Start Against Pelicans|date=2014-12-07|publisher=NBA|accessdate=2020-09-04|url=http://www.nba.com/lakers/141207_pricedavis|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20141208053240/http://www.nba.com/lakers/141207_pricedavis|archivedate=2014-12-08|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|last=Pincus|first=Eric|title=Lakers' Byron Scott trades offense for better defense in starting lineup|date=2014-12-09|newspaper=Los Angeles Times|url=https://www.latimes.com/sports/lakers/lakersnow/la-sp-ln-lakers-byron-scott-offense-for-defense-20141209-story.html|accessdate=2014-12-12|archive-date=2014-12-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141210220725/http://www.latimes.com/sports/lakers/lakersnow/la-sp-ln-lakers-byron-scott-offense-for-defense-20141209-story.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="beacham_01252015">{{cite news |last=Beacham |first=Greg |title=Lin disappointed by benching, but not giving up on Lakers |date=2015-01-25 |publisher=NBA |accessdate=2020-09-04 |agency=Associated Press |url=http://www.nba.com/2015/news/01/25/jeremy-lin-disappointed-by-benching.ap/ |archive-date=2018-10-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181006035854/http://www.nba.com/2015/news/01/25/jeremy-lin-disappointed-by-benching.ap/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。林書豪對於調整感到失望，他稱這是「我經歷過最艱難的情況之一」<ref>{{cite news|last=Bresnahan|first=Mike|title=Lakers Coach Byron Scott fires back at Carlos Boozer|date=2014-12-09|newspaper=Los Angeles Times|url=https://www.latimes.com/sports/lakers/lakersnow/la-sp-ln-lakers-byron-scott-carlos-boozer-20141209-story.html|accessdate=2014-12-12|archive-date=2014-12-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141211062612/http://www.latimes.com/sports/lakers/lakersnow/la-sp-ln-lakers-byron-scott-carlos-boozer-20141209-story.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|last=Medina|first=Mark|title=Lakers' Kobe Bryant could have more point guard duties|date=2014-12-10|newspaper=LA Daily News|accessdate=2020-09-04|url=http://www.dailynews.com/sports/20141210/lakers-kobe-bryant-could-have-more-point-guard-duties/1|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20141213035213/http://www.dailynews.com/sports/20141210/lakers-kobe-bryant-could-have-more-point-guard-duties/1|archivedate=2014-12-13|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2015年1月23日，拜伦·斯科特在爆冷輸給聖安東尼奧馬刺的比賽中選擇不讓健康的林書豪出賽，而是提拔新秀[[喬丹·克拉克森|喬丹·克拉克森]]頂替罗尼·普莱斯的先發位置<ref name="bresnahan_01232015"/><ref>{{cite news |last=Holmes |first=Baxter |title=Spurs 99, Lakers 85: No Kobe, inspiration |date=2015-01-23 |publisher=ESPN |accessdate=2020-09-04 |url=https://www.espn.com/blog/los-angeles/lakers/post/_/id/41011/spurs-99-lakers-85-no-kobe-inspiration |archive-date=2019-12-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191225194644/https://www.espn.com/blog/los-angeles/lakers/post/_/id/41011/spurs-99-lakers-85-no-kobe-inspiration |dead-url=no }}</ref>。林書豪在該賽季已上場的43場比賽，場均10.5分和4.5助攻<ref>{{cite news |last=Wise |first=Brandon |title=Lakers guard Jeremy Lin benched during Friday's loss to Spurs |date=2015-01-23 |publisher=CBS Sports |accessdate=2020-09-04 |url=https://www.cbssports.com/nba/news/lakers-guard-jeremy-lin-benched-during-fridays-loss-to-spurs/ |archive-date=2018-07-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180725153144/https://www.cbssports.com/nba/news/lakers-guard-jeremy-lin-benched-during-fridays-loss-to-spurs/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。這是他自2012年2月2日以來首次身體健康但沒有出賽<ref name="beacham_01252015"/><ref name="bresnahan_01232015">{{cite news |last=Bresnahan |first=Mike |title=Lakers sit Jeremy Lin, go with younger starters in 99–85 loss to Spurs |date=2015-01-23 |newspaper=Los Angeles Times |accessdate=2020-09-04 |url=https://www.latimes.com/sports/lakers/la-sp-lakers-spurs-20150124-story.html |archive-date=2019-02-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190220235936/https://www.latimes.com/sports/lakers/la-sp-lakers-spurs-20150124-story.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。3月22日，林書豪在戰勝[[费城76人|费城76人]]的比賽中攻下賽季新高的29分後，拜伦·斯科特讓他回到先發陣容<ref>{{cite news |last=Barnes |first=Evan |title=Lakers' Jeremy Lin, Ryan Kelly to return to starting lineup |date=2015-03-23 |newspaper=Los Angeles Daily News |accessdate=2020-09-04 |url=https://www.dailynews.com/2015/03/23/lakers-jeremy-lin-ryan-kelly-to-return-to-starting-lineup/ |archive-date=2018-10-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181003013828/https://www.dailynews.com/2015/03/23/lakers-jeremy-lin-ryan-kelly-to-return-to-starting-lineup/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。3月24日，林書豪和具有菲律賓血統的隊友喬丹·克拉克森，成為NBA歷史上首對在後場一同先發的亞裔美籍球員<ref>{{cite news |last=Medina |first=Mark |title=Lakers' Jeremy Lin, Jordan Clarkson thrive as backcourt duo in loss to Thunder |date=2015-03-25 |publisher=Inside the Lakers |accessdate=2020-09-04 |url=http://www.insidesocal.com/lakers/2015/03/25/lakers-jeremy-lin-jordan-clarkson-thrive-as-backcourt-duo-in-loss-to-thunder/ |archive-date=2018-10-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181002180534/http://www.insidesocal.com/lakers/2015/03/25/lakers-jeremy-lin-jordan-clarkson-thrive-as-backcourt-duo-in-loss-to-thunder/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。林書豪因為[[上呼吸道感染|上呼吸道感染]]缺席該賽季最後5場比賽<ref>{{cite web|url=http://en.yibada.com/articles/23086/20150329/jeremy-lin-shut-down-with-upper-respiratory-infection-lakers-fall-anew-to-nets.htm|title=Jeremy Lin Shut Down with Upper Respiratory Infection; Lakers Fall Anew to Nets|first=Nel|last=Imperial|date=2015-03-29|work=YIBADA|accessdate=2020-09-04|archive-date=2018-10-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181002141755/http://en.yibada.com/articles/23086/20150329/jeremy-lin-shut-down-with-upper-respiratory-infection-lakers-fall-anew-to-nets.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

=== 夏洛特黃蜂（2015年至2016年） ===
2015年7月9日，林書豪與[[夏洛特黃蜂|夏洛特黃蜂]]簽下一份兩年430萬美元合約<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.nba.com/hornets/hornets-sign-free-agent-guard-jeremy-lin|title=Hornets Sign Free Agent Guard Jeremy Lin|publisher=NBA|date=2015-07-09|accessdate=2015-07-13|archive-date=2015-07-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150711214340/http://www.nba.com/hornets/hornets-sign-free-agent-guard-jeremy-lin|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.espn.com/nba/story/_/id/13224585/free-agent-guard-jeremy-lin-announces-join-charlotte-hornets|title=Jeremy Lin gets Hornets' bi-annual exception of 2 years, $4.3M|publisher=ESPN|date=2015-07-08|accessdate=2015-07-08|archive-date=2019-01-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190120093530/http://www.espn.com/nba/story/_/id/13224585/free-agent-guard-jeremy-lin-announces-join-charlotte-hornets|dead-url=no}}</ref>。林書豪曾對重新加盟紐約尼克持開放態度，但紐約尼克對他並不感興趣，他們於選秀上在得分後衛的位置選中後衛[[傑萊恩·葛蘭特|傑萊恩·葛蘭特]]與老將[[何塞·卡尔德隆|何塞·卡尔德隆]]作搭檔<ref name="espn_10172015"/>。林書豪被預測為夏洛特黃蜂得分後衛[[肯巴·沃克|肯巴·沃克]]的替補，總教練[[史蒂夫·克利福德|史蒂夫·克利福德]]則設想這兩名能執行擋拆戰術的後衛有時能一起上場<ref>{{cite news |last=Bonnell |first=Rick |title=Coach Steve Clifford looking forward to more shooting, passing from new-look Hornets |date=2015-08-29 |newspaper=The Charlotte Observer |accessdate=2020-09-04 |url=https://www.charlotteobserver.com/sports/charlotte-hornets/article32740182.html |archive-date=2020-11-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201121174025/https://www.charlotteobserver.com/sports/charlotte-hornets/article32740182.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="fowler_07092015"/>。

10月28日，林書豪在球隊對陣邁阿密熱火的賽季開幕戰中代表夏洛特黃蜂先發上場，在以104比94輸掉的比賽中，他替補出賽得到17分<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.nba.com/games/20151028/CHAMIA/gameinfo.html|title=Bosh returns, Heat top Hornets 104–94 in season opener|work=NBA|date=2015-10-28|accessdate=2015-10-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151027165717/http://www.nba.com/games/20151028/CHAMIA/gameinfo.html|archive-date=2015-10-27|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。12月17日，他在以109比99延長賽戰勝多倫多暴龍的比賽中攻下賽季最高的35分<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.nba.com/games/20151217/TORCHA/gameinfo.html|title=Lin scores 35 points, Hornets beat Raptors 109–99 in OT|work=NBA|date=2015-12-17|accessdate=2015-12-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160406104449/http://www.nba.com/games/20151217/TORCHA/gameinfo.html|archive-date=2016-04-06|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。2016年3月21日，他在第四節拿下球隊29分中的15分，包括在還剩48秒時的領先跳投，幫助夏洛特黃蜂在第二節以7比30落後的情況下，最終以91比88逆轉戰勝馬刺<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.nba.com/games/20160321/SASCHA/gameinfo.html|title=Lin, Hornets erase 23-point deficit, beat Spurs 91–88|work=NBA|date=2016-03-21|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20190429021113/https://www.nba.com/games/20160321/SASCHA/gameinfo.html|archivedate=2019-04-29|dead-url=yes|accessdate=2016-04-15}}</ref>。林書豪在夏洛特黃蜂的唯一賽季於季後賽首輪被熱火以7場擊敗後結束。[[NBA年度最佳第六人|NBA年度最佳第六人]]的投票中林書豪名列第7名<ref name="devine_08272019"/>。在拒絕執行2016–17年賽季220萬美元的球員選擇權後，林書豪於7月1日成為不受限自由球員<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.espn.com/nba/story/_/id/16439073/2016-nba-free-agency-jeremy-lin-charlotte-hornets-declines-player-option|title=Sources: Lin declines player option with Hornets|author=Marc Stein|date=2016-06-23|work=ESPN|accessdate=2020-09-04|archive-date=2019-12-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191225023236/https://www.espn.com/nba/story/_/id/16439073/2016-nba-free-agency-jeremy-lin-charlotte-hornets-declines-player-option|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

=== 布魯克林籃網（2016年至2018年） ===
2016年7月7日，林書豪與[[布魯克林籃網|布魯克林籃網]]簽下一份3年3600萬美元的合約<ref>{{cite web |title=Brooklyn Nets Sign Jeremy Lin |date=2016-07-07 |website=NBA.com |url=https://www.nba.com/nets/news/2016/07/07/brooklyn-nets-sign-jeremy-lin |access-date=2019-11-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190831084608/https://www.nba.com/nets/news/2016/07/07/brooklyn-nets-sign-jeremy-lin |archive-date=2019-08-31 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=Sources: Jeremy Lin agrees to 3-year deal with Nets|date=2016-07-01|website=ESPN.com|url=http://www.espn.com/nba/story/_/id/16672051/jeremy-lin-agrees-three-year-deal-brooklyn-nets|accessdate=2016-10-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161031033939/http://www.espn.com/nba/story/_/id/16672051/jeremy-lin-agrees-three-year-deal-brooklyn-nets|archive-date=2016-10-31|dead-url=no}}</ref>。林來瘋時期的紐約尼克助教[[肯尼·阿特金森|肯尼·阿特金森]]此時擔任布魯克林籃網新任總教練<ref name="devine_08272019"/>。10月26日，賽季開幕賽客場以122比117敗給[[波士顿凯尔特人|波士顿凯尔特人]]，林書豪初登板先發27分鐘，攻下18分<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.espn.com/nba/recap?gameId=400899380|title=Thomas scores 25, Celtics fight off Nets 122-117|work=ESPN.com|date=2016-10-26|accessdate=2016-10-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161029175358/http://www.espn.com/nba/recap?gameId=400899380|archive-date=2016-10-29|dead-url=no}}</ref>。兩天後的主場開幕戰，林書豪繳出21分9助攻9籃板的「準大三元」表現，帶領布魯克林籃網以103比94擊敗[[印第安那溜馬|印第安那溜馬]]<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.espn.com/nba/recap?gameId=400899452|title=Lin leads Nets past Pacers, 103-94 in home opener|work=ESPN.com|date=2016-10-28|accessdate=2016-10-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161029174224/http://www.espn.com/nba/recap?gameId=400899452|archive-date=2016-10-29|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2017年2月24日，錯失26場的林書豪傷癒歸隊，先發上場15分鐘，攻下7分、5助攻，布魯克林籃網以129比109輸給[[丹佛掘金|丹佛掘金]]<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.espn.com/nba/recap?gameId=400900270|title=Harris scores 25 points in Nuggets' 129-109 win over Nets|work=ESPN|date=2017-02-24|accessdate=2017-02-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170226045922/http://www.espn.com/nba/recap?gameId=400900270|archive-date=2017-02-26|dead-url=no}}</ref>。4月6日，林書豪對上[[奥兰多魔术|奥兰多魔术]]時，攻下賽季新高32分<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.espn.com/nba/recap?gameId=400900552|title=Elfrid Payton has 22 points, Magic beat Nets 115-107|work=ESPN|date=2017-04-06|accessdate=2017-04-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170407083320/http://www.espn.com/nba/recap?gameId=400900552|archive-date=2017-04-07|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

10月18日，新賽季開幕戰對上印第安納溜馬，林書豪在一次上籃中，落地時失去平衡跌倒傷到右膝。經檢查後證實右膝髕骨肌腱韌帶斷裂，剩餘賽季報銷<ref>{{cite web|title=Brooklyn Nets' Jeremy Lin suffers ruptured patella tendon; expected to miss season|url=https://www.nba.com/article/2017/10/18/nets-lin-out-season-ruptured-patella-tendon|website=NBA|accessdate=2017-10-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200325185724/https://www.nba.com/article/2017/10/18/nets-lin-out-season-ruptured-patella-tendon|archive-date=2020-03-25|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

=== 亞特蘭大老鷹（2018年至2019年） ===
2018年7月13日，布魯克林籃網將林書豪和選秀籤交易至[[亞特蘭大老鷹|亞特蘭大老鷹]]，換回後衛{{tsl|en|Isaia Cordinier|伊薩亞·柯迪尼耶}}的簽約權和未來第二輪選秀籤<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.nba.com/nets/news/2018/07/13/brooklyn-nets-complete-trade-with-atlanta-hawks|title=Brooklyn Nets Complete Trade With Atlanta Hawks|work=NBA.com|date=2018-07-13|accessdate=2018-07-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180714033925/https://www.nba.com/nets/news/2018/07/13/brooklyn-nets-complete-trade-with-atlanta-hawks|archive-date=2018-07-14|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news |author1=尹俊傑 |title=林書豪轉戰老鷹 老東家籃網發文感謝 |url=https://www.cna.com.tw/news/aspt/201807140046.aspx |accessdate=2019-11-17 |agency=中央通訊社 |date=2018-07-14 |archive-date=2020-08-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200826142339/https://www.cna.com.tw/news/aspt/201807140046.aspx |dead-url=no }}</ref>。亞特蘭大老鷹安排林書豪擔任新秀[[崔·楊|崔·楊]]的導師<ref>{{cite news|last=Cunningham|first=Michael|title=Hawks add ‘high-character’ Jeremy Lin, continue to seek trades for Dennis Schroder|date=2018-07-16|newspaper=The Atlanta Journal-Constitution|url=https://www.ajc.com/blog/atlanta-hawks/hawks-add-high-character-jeremy-lin-continue-seek-trades-for-dennis-schroder/z3obP48bsM2cAmA4U52FkO/|accessdate=2019-02-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190214002710/https://www.ajc.com/blog/atlanta-hawks/hawks-add-high-character-jeremy-lin-continue-seek-trades-for-dennis-schroder/z3obP48bsM2cAmA4U52FkO/|archive-date=2019-02-14|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|last=Kirschner|first=Chris|title=If Hawks deal Lin, he accomplished exactly what the team wanted — to mentor Young|date=2019-01-31|work=The Athletic|url=https://theathletic.com/793275/2019/01/31/if-the-hawks-deal-jeremy-lin-he-accomplished-exactly-what-the-team-wanted-out-of-him-mentor-trae-young/|access-date=2019-11-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190731023519/https://theathletic.com/793275/2019/01/31/if-the-hawks-deal-jeremy-lin-he-accomplished-exactly-what-the-team-wanted-out-of-him-mentor-trae-young/|archive-date=2019-07-31|dead-url=no}}</ref>。11月15日面對[[丹佛金塊|丹佛金塊]]，林書豪拿到NBA生涯第5000分<ref>{{cite news |author1=黃巧雯 |title=林書豪生涯得分破5000分 老鷹仍吞敗 |url=https://www.cna.com.tw/news/aspt/201811160111.aspx |accessdate=2019-11-17 |agency=中央通訊社 |date=2018-11-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181116090452/https://www.cna.com.tw/news/aspt/201811160111.aspx |archive-date=2018-11-16 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。2019年2月11日，亞特蘭大老鷹和林書豪談妥買斷合約，後將林書豪釋出<ref>{{cite web|title=Atlanta Hawks Request Waivers On Jeremy Lin|date=2019-02-11|publisher=Atlanta Hawks|url=https://www.nba.com/hawks/atlanta-hawks-request-waivers-jeremy-lin|accessdate=2019-02-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190212131441/https://www.nba.com/hawks/atlanta-hawks-request-waivers-jeremy-lin|archive-date=2019-02-12|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|last=Wojnarowski|first=Adrian|title=Jeremy Lin finalizing buyout with Hawks, to sign with Raptors|date=2019-02-11|website=ESPN.com|url=http://www.espn.com/nba/story/_/id/25973589/jeremy-lin-finalizing-buyout-hawks-sign-raptors|accessdate=2019-02-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190211230056/http://www.espn.com/nba/story/_/id/25973589/jeremy-lin-finalizing-buyout-hawks-sign-raptors|archive-date=2019-02-11|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

=== 多倫多暴龍（2019年） ===
2019年2月13日，林書豪與[[多倫多暴龍|多倫多暴龍]]簽下合約<ref>{{cite press release|title=Raptors Sign Jeremy Lin|date=2019-02-13|publisher=Toronto Raptors|url=https://www.nba.com/raptors/press-release/raptors-sign-jeremy-lin|accessdate=2019-02-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190214054313/https://www.nba.com/raptors/press-release/raptors-sign-jeremy-lin|archive-date=2019-02-14|dead-url=no}}</ref>。隨著多倫多暴龍打進季後賽，季後賽期間因[[弗瑞德·范弗利特|弗瑞德·范弗利特]]和[[凯尔·洛里|凯尔·洛里]]為球隊的先發控衛，因此也作為控衛的林書豪只能在垃圾時間上場<ref name="devine_08272019">{{cite news|last=Devine|first=Dan|title=In China, Jeremy Lin Will Get to Control the Game, Again|date=2019-08-27|work=The Ringer|url=https://www.theringer.com/nba/2019/8/27/20835588/jeremy-lin-beijing-ducks|accessdate=2019-08-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190828054647/https://www.theringer.com/nba/2019/8/27/20835588/jeremy-lin-beijing-ducks|archive-date=2019-08-28|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="torstar_08272019"/>，總計季後賽共上場27分鐘，其中總決賽只在第3戰上場51秒<ref>{{cite news|last=Wong|first=Alex|title=Jeremy Lin, ‘Reppin’ Asians With Everything I Have,’ Is Bigger Than an N.B.A. Title|date=2019-06-18|newspaper=The New York Times|url=https://www.nytimes.com/2019/06/18/sports/basketball/jeremy-lin-toronto-raptors.html|accessdate=2019-06-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190620181124/https://www.nytimes.com/2019/06/18/sports/basketball/jeremy-lin-toronto-raptors.html|archive-date=2019-06-20|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news |author1=體育中心 |title=林書豪首位亞裔上場並奪冠軍戒 6戰出賽51秒 |url=https://sports.ettoday.net/news/1467189 |accessdate=2020-03-31 |work=ETtoday |date=2019-06-14 |archive-date=2020-08-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200826142333/https://sports.ettoday.net/news/1467189 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，成為第二位亞裔美籍球員於總決賽上場<ref name="blennerhassett_06062019">{{Cite news|first=Patrick|last=Blennerhassett|url=https://www.scmp.com/sport/basketball/article/3013373/jeremy-lin-becomes-first-east-asian-american-play-nba-finals|title=Jeremy Lin becomes first East Asian-American to play in NBA Finals|date=2019-06-06|newspaper=South China Morning Post|access-date=2019-06-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190610003337/https://www.scmp.com/sport/basketball/article/3013373/jeremy-lin-becomes-first-east-asian-american-play-nba-finals|archive-date=2019-06-10|dead-url=no}}</ref>{{notetag|首位是菲裔美籍的[[喬丹·克拉克森|喬丹·克拉克森]]，[[2018年NBA總決賽|2018年]]跟隨克里夫蘭騎士打進總決賽<ref name="blennerhassett_06062019"/>。}}。多倫多暴龍取得當年度NBA總冠軍，林書豪成為首位獲得NBA冠軍戒的的亞裔美籍球員<ref>{{Cite news|first=Gillian|last=Brockell|title=He broke pro basketball’s color barrier. Now Jeremy Lin joins him in the history books.|date=2019-06-15|newspaper=The Washington Post|url=https://www.washingtonpost.com/history/2019/06/15/he-broke-pro-basketballs-color-barrier-now-jeremy-lin-joins-him-history-books/|accessdate=2019-06-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190616021909/https://www.washingtonpost.com/history/2019/06/15/he-broke-pro-basketballs-color-barrier-now-jeremy-lin-joins-him-history-books/|archive-date=2019-06-16|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news |author1=龍柏安 |title=林書豪隨暴龍奪冠 亞裔美籍球員第一人 |url=https://www.cna.com.tw/news/firstnews/201906140091.aspx |accessdate=2019-11-17 |agency=中央通訊社 |date=2019-06-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190614172436/https://www.cna.com.tw/news/firstnews/201906140091.aspx |archive-date=2019-06-14 |dead-url=no }}</ref>{{notetag|林書豪2019年獲得NBA冠軍戒前，已有下列來自亞洲的球員獲得NBA冠軍戒：[[孟克巴特尔|孟克巴特尔]]（中華人民共和國，[[2003年NBA總決賽|2003年]]聖安東尼奧馬刺）和[[孙悦_(篮球运动员)|孙悦]]（中華人民共和國，[[2009年NBA總決賽|2009年]]洛杉磯湖人）<ref>{{cite news|last=White|first=Jonathan|title=Jeremy Lin not the first Asian player to win the NBA – inside the bizarre tale of Sun Yue’s 2009 championship with Kobe Bryant’s LA Lakers|date=2019-06-19|newspaper=South China Morining Post|url=https://www.scmp.com/sport/basketball/article/3015119/jeremy-lin-not-first-asian-player-win-nba-inside-bizarre-tale-sun|accessdate=2019-07-03|archive-date=2019-07-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190703020107/https://www.scmp.com/sport/basketball/article/3015119/jeremy-lin-not-first-asian-player-win-nba-inside-bizarre-tale-sun|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news |author1=徐邦印 |title=搭猛龙便车 林书豪成第一个夺冠的华裔球员 |url=https://news.sina.com.cn/c/2019-06-14/doc-ihvhiqay5612737.shtml |accessdate=2020-09-04 |work=新京报 |date=2019-06-14 |archive-date=2019-09-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190923094148/http://news.sina.com.cn/c/2019-06-14/doc-ihvhiqay5612737.shtml |dead-url=no }}</ref>。}}。

7月1日，林書豪成為自由球員。7月27日，林書豪在臺灣基督頻道[[GOOD_TV|GOOD TV]]舉辦的分享會上表示仍然未被任何球隊簽約。他把自身的狀況比作「人生陷入低潮」，並補充他感覺「好像NBA已經放棄我」<ref name="devine_08272019"/><ref name="torstar_08272019">{{cite news|title=Former Raptors guard Jeremy Lin to play in China, signs with Beijing Ducks|date=2019-08-27|newspaper=The Toronto Star|url=https://www.thestar.com/sports/raptors/2019/08/27/former-raptors-guard-jeremy-lin-to-play-in-china-signs-with-beijing-ducks.html|accessdate=2019-08-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190827162832/https://www.thestar.com/sports/raptors/2019/08/27/former-raptors-guard-jeremy-lin-to-play-in-china-signs-with-beijing-ducks.html|archive-date=2019-08-27|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="espn_08272019">{{cite news|last=Wang|first=Kevin|title=Lin inks pact to play in China with Beijing Ducks|date=2019-08-27|website=ESPN.com|url=https://www.espn.com/nba/story/_/id/27474938/lin-inks-pact-play-china-beijing-ducks|accessdate=2019-08-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200621212841/https://www.espn.com/nba/story/_/id/27474938/lin-inks-pact-play-china-beijing-ducks|archive-date=2020-06-21|dead-url=no}}</ref>。數支球隊對於林書豪在得分後衛的位置上，是否具有足夠機動性感到不確定<ref>{{cite news|last=Stein|first=Marc|title=The Surprises Won't Stop|date=2019-07-23|newspaper=The New York Times|url=https://static.nytimes.com/email-content/MSB_15477.html|accessdate=2019-08-27|archive-date=2020-11-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201121174256/https://static.nytimes.com/email-content/MSB_15477.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

=== 北京首鋼（2019年至2020年） ===
2019年8月27日，林書豪以稅後年薪300萬美元與[[北京鸭首鋼篮球俱乐部|北京首鋼]]簽約，新賽季以外援身份出戰[[中国男子篮球职业联赛|中国男子篮球职业联赛]]（CBA）<ref>{{cite news |author1=廖聿偉 |title=年薪9400萬 豪哥轉戰CBA |url=https://sports.ltn.com.tw/news/paper/1313872 |accessdate=2019-11-17 |work=自由時報 |date=2019-08-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191001133336/https://sports.ltn.com.tw/news/paper/1313872 |archive-date=2019-10-01 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="torstar_08272019"/><ref name="espn_08272019"/>；此前曾有[[莫斯科中央陸軍籃球俱樂部|莫斯科中央陸軍]]、{{link-en|特拉維夫馬卡比籃球俱樂部|Maccabi Tel Aviv B.C.|特拉維夫馬卡比}}等[[歐洲籃球聯賽|歐洲籃球聯賽]]球隊向林書豪提出過合約<ref>{{cite news |author1=龍柏安 |title=歐洲頂級豪門中央陸軍補強 林書豪列頭號人選 |url=https://www.cna.com.tw/news/aspt/201907270021.aspx |accessdate=2019-11-21 |agency=中央通訊社 |date=2019-07-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190727041833/https://www.cna.com.tw/news/aspt/201907270021.aspx |archive-date=2019-07-27 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |title=林書豪再獲報價 這次是以色列馬卡比 |url=https://www.cna.com.tw/news/aspt/201908020340.aspx |accessdate=2019-11-21 |agency=中央通訊社 |date=2019-08-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190803035540/https://www.cna.com.tw/news/aspt/201908020340.aspx |archive-date=2019-08-03 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。林書豪在首場官辦熱身賽中轟下40分、6籃板、3助攻<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.cbssports.com/nba/news/jeremy-lins-40-point-debut-with-beijing-ducks-only-proves-he-still-belongs-in-the-nba/|title=Jeremy Lin's 40-point debut with Beijing Ducks only proves he still belongs in the NBA|website=CBSSports.com|access-date=2019-11-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191112211604/https://www.cbssports.com/nba/news/jeremy-lins-40-point-debut-with-beijing-ducks-only-proves-he-still-belongs-in-the-nba/|archive-date=2019-11-12|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news |author1=龍柏安 |title=林來瘋重現 CBA熱身賽林書豪狂轟40分 |url=https://www.cna.com.tw/news/aspt/201910100271.aspx |accessdate=2019-11-17 |agency=中央通訊社 |date=2019-10-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191010190609/https://www.cna.com.tw/news/aspt/201910100271.aspx |archive-date=2019-10-10 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。於例行賽首秀繳出25分、9助攻、6籃板，率領北京首鋼以103比81擊敗[[天津荣钢先行者篮球俱乐部|天津先行者]]<ref>{{cite news |author1=龍柏安 |title=林書豪CBA首秀轟25分 率北京首鋼擊敗天津先行者 |url=https://www.cna.com.tw/news/firstnews/201911030212.aspx |accessdate=2019-11-17 |agency=中央通訊社 |date=2019-11-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191105032637/https://www.cna.com.tw/news/firstnews/201911030212.aspx |archive-date=2019-11-05 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。北京首鋼在12月30日安排林書豪輪休，更換成{{tsl|en|Justin Hamilton (basketball, born 1990)|賈斯汀·漢密爾頓}}與{{tsl|en|Ekpe Udoh|艾派·尤度}}組合出賽<ref>{{cite news |title=北京首钢紧急激活汉密尔顿！提前轮休林书豪！ |url=https://sports.sina.com.cn/basketball/cba/2019-12-29/doc-iihnzahk0723501.shtml |accessdate=2020-10-28 |work=新浪体育 |date=2019-12-29 |archive-date=2020-11-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201106001938/https://sports.sina.com.cn/basketball/cba/2019-12-29/doc-iihnzahk0723501.shtml |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite press release |title=同意北京首钢队更换外籍球员官方公告 |url=https://www.cbaleague.com/#/announcement/detail/152 |publisher=中篮联（北京）体育有限公司 |accessdate=2021-06-13 |date=2019-12-30 |archive-date=2020-08-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200817211410/https://www.cbaleague.com/#/announcement/detail/152 |dead-url=no }}</ref>；2020年1月16日北京首鋼啟用林書豪替換艾派·尤度<ref>{{cite news |title=北京男篮惨败后立刻更换外援：林书豪替换尤度 |url=https://sports.sina.com.cn/basketball/cba/2020-01-16/doc-iihnzhha2903622.shtml |accessdate=2020-10-28 |work=新浪体育 |date=2020-01-16 |archive-date=2020-11-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201121174411/https://sports.sina.com.cn/basketball/cba/2020-01-16/doc-iihnzhha2903622.shtml |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite press release |title=同意北京首钢队更换外籍球员官方公告 |url=https://www.cbaleague.com/#/announcement/detail/179 |publisher=中篮联（北京）体育有限公司 |accessdate=2021-06-13 |date=2020-01-16 |archive-date=2020-08-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200817211410/https://www.cbaleague.com/#/announcement/detail/179 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。林書豪以10萬9969票、北區最高票，入選[[2020年中国男子篮球职业联赛全明星赛|CBA全明星賽]]先發名單<ref>{{cite news |author1=黃巧雯 |title=CBA明星賽先發名單 林書豪北區最高票 |url=https://www.cna.com.tw/news/aspt/201912270338.aspx |accessdate=2019-12-28 |agency=中央通訊社 |date=2019-12-27 |archive-date=2019-12-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191228061410/https://www.cna.com.tw/news/aspt/201912270338.aspx |dead-url=no }}</ref>；在CBA全明星賽中攻下全場最高分41分，而北方隊最終以166比167落敗給南方隊<ref>{{cite news |author1=黃巧雯 |title=CBA明星賽砍41分 林書豪與MVP擦身而過 |url=https://www.cna.com.tw/news/aspt/202001120236.aspx |accessdate=2020-08-26 |agency=中央通訊社 |date=2020-01-12 |archive-date=2020-05-31 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200531070347/https://www.cna.com.tw/news/aspt/202001120236.aspx |dead-url=no }}</ref>。[[2019-20年中国男子篮球职业联赛|CBA賽季]]在2月1日因[[2019冠状病毒病中国大陆疫情|2019冠状病毒病疫情]]停賽至6月20日<ref>{{cite press release |title=比赛延期公告 |url=https://www.cbaleague.com/#/announcement/detail/189 |publisher=中篮联（北京）体育有限公司 |accessdate=2021-06-13 |date=2020-01-24 |archive-date=2020-08-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200817211410/https://www.cbaleague.com/#/announcement/detail/189 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |author1=黃巧雯 |title=CBA兩地開打20日復賽 林書豪喊Yes |url=https://www.cna.com.tw/news/aspt/202006040326.aspx |accessdate=2020-08-26 |agency=中央通訊社 |date=2020-06-04 |archive-date=2020-06-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200604151027/https://www.cna.com.tw/news/aspt/202006040326.aspx |dead-url=no }}</ref>。林書豪在CBA賽季第16週以兩場出賽，場均27分、6.5籃板、5.5助攻、2.5抄截，當選CBA單週最佳外籍球員<ref>{{cite news |author1=梁偉銘 |title=例行賽壓軸週MVP 林書豪無愧史上頭號高薪外援 |url=https://sports.ltn.com.tw/news/breakingnews/3242566 |accessdate=2020-09-18 |work=自由時報 |date=2020-07-28 |archive-date=2020-09-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200923144924/https://sports.ltn.com.tw/news/breakingnews/3242566 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。林書豪在該賽季入圍[[中国男子篮球职业联赛最佳防守球员|年度最佳防守球員]]決選名單<ref>{{cite news |author1=黃建霖 |title=和易建聯競爭！林書豪將拚生涯首座最佳防守球員獎 |url=https://www.nownews.com/news/sport/5038612 |accessdate=2020-08-26 |work=NOWnews |date=2020-07-29 |archive-date=2020-08-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200801050948/https://www.nownews.com/news/sport/5038612 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |author1=TDZ |title=周琦当选本赛季最佳防守球员 场均1.2断2.3帽 |url=https://sports.sina.com.cn/basketball/cba/2020-07-30/doc-iivhvpwx8222839.shtml |accessdate=2020-08-26 |work=新浪体育 |date=2020-07-30 |archive-date=2020-08-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200826142334/https://sports.sina.com.cn/basketball/cba/2020-07-30/doc-iivhvpwx8222839.shtml |dead-url=no }}</ref>。北京首鋼在[[2020年CBA季后赛|季後賽]]半決賽中以1比2輸給最終奪下CBA總冠軍的[[广东宏远篮球俱乐部|廣東宏遠]]<ref>{{cite news |author1=黃巧雯 |title=CBA北京首鋼無緣冠軍戰 林書豪一夜未眠 |url=https://www.cna.com.tw/news/aspt/202008090122.aspx |accessdate=2020-08-26 |agency=中央通訊社 |date=2020-08-09 |archive-date=2020-08-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200826142340/https://www.cna.com.tw/news/aspt/202008090122.aspx |dead-url=no }}</ref>。林書豪9月透過[[新浪微博|新浪微博]]表示，還懷抱NBA夢想，將不回北京首鋼<ref>{{cite news |author1=黃巧雯 |title=林書豪：還懷抱NBA夢 不回CBA北京首鋼 |url=https://www.cna.com.tw/news/firstnews/202009155010.aspx |accessdate=2020-09-15 |agency=中央通訊社 |date=2020-09-15 |archive-date=2021-03-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210305223606/https://www.cna.com.tw/news/firstnews/202009155010.aspx |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

=== 聖克魯斯勇士（2021年） ===
2020年12月16日，林書豪以練習球員的身份加入[[NBA_G聯盟引爆者|NBA G聯盟引爆者]]，在打完一場隊內分組賽後就離開球隊<ref>{{cite news |author1=林宏翰 |title=林書豪加入G聯盟培訓隊 與18歲新秀實戰等機會 |url=https://www.cna.com.tw/news/firstnews/202012160012.aspx |accessdate=2020-12-18 |agency=中央通訊社 |date=2020-12-16 |archive-date=2021-02-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210213062958/https://www.cna.com.tw/news/firstnews/202012160012.aspx |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |author1=李晉緯(譯) |title=林書豪離開G聯盟球隊 總教練：想去能發揮的地方 |url=https://www.cna.com.tw/news/aspt/202012180064.aspx |accessdate=2020-12-18 |agency=中央通訊社 |date=2020-12-17}}</ref>。之後林書豪原本能與NBA金州勇士先簽約後釋出，效力附屬球隊[[聖克魯斯勇士|聖克魯斯勇士]]，因[[國際籃球總會|國際籃球總會]]（FIBA）適逢週末未辦公，無法取得CBA的澄清信而未完成<ref>{{cite news |author1=Marc Spears |title=Jeremy Lin doesn't end up signing with Golden State Warriors' G League team |url=https://www.espn.com/nba/story/_/id/30545720/source-jeremy-lin-sign-golden-state-warriors-g-league-team |accessdate=2020-12-18 |work=ESPN |date=2020-12-18 |archive-date=2021-01-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210110110405/https://www.espn.com/nba/story/_/id/30545720/source-jeremy-lin-sign-golden-state-warriors-g-league-team |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |author1=黃巧雯 |title=勇士等不到中國職籃發離隊證明 捨林書豪改簽新秀 |url=https://www.cna.com.tw/news/firstnews/202012200202.aspx |accessdate=2021-02-11 |work=中央通訊社 |date=2020-12-20 |archive-date=2020-12-31 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201231124040/https://www.cna.com.tw/news/firstnews/202012200202.aspx |dead-url=no }}</ref>。NBA於年底制定一個新條款，放寬NBA G聯盟對資深球員招募和簽約的限制，讓擁有NBA資歷五年以上的自由球員能夠加入NBA G聯盟球隊<ref>{{cite news |author1=Jonathan Givony |title=NBA eliminating restrictions on recruiting veteran players for G League rosters |url=https://www.espn.com/nba/story/_/id/30594111/nba-eliminating-restrictions-recruiting-veteran-players-g-league-rosters |accessdate=2021-02-11 |work=ESPN |date=2020-12-25 |archive-date=2021-01-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210127000915/https://www.espn.com/nba/story/_/id/30594111/nba-eliminating-restrictions-recruiting-veteran-players-g-league-rosters |dead-url=no }}</ref>；此條款被有些NBA G聯盟的觀察家稱作「林書豪條款」<ref>{{cite news |author1=Marc Stein |title=From Kobe to LeBron: Tragedy and Triumph in the N.B.A. |url=https://www.nytimes.com/2020/12/30/sports/basketball/nba-kobe-bryant-lebron-james.html |accessdate=2021-02-11 |work=The New York Times |date=2020-12-30 |quote=Neither the Golden State Warriors nor the Santa Cruz Warriors would sign Lin. He would have to sign with the G League first and then be allocated to Santa Cruz via the new rule, which some G League observers are even calling “the Jeremy Lin rule.” |archive-date=2021-02-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210223130335/https://www.nytimes.com/2020/12/30/sports/basketball/nba-kobe-bryant-lebron-james.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。2021年1月9日，林書豪以NBA新條款加入聖克魯斯勇士<ref>{{cite press release |title=Santa Cruz Warriors Adds NBA Veteran Jeremy Lin |publisher=Santa Cruz Warriors |date=2021-01-09 |url=https://santacruz.gleague.nba.com/news/santa-cruz-warriors-adds-nba-veteran-jeremy-lin/ |accessdate=2021-01-10 |archive-date=2021-01-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210112122402/https://santacruz.gleague.nba.com/news/santa-cruz-warriors-adds-nba-veteran-jeremy-lin/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。2月10日，林書豪在例行賽首秀攻下18分、5助攻、3籃板、3抄截<ref>{{cite news |author1=蔡佳霖 |title=G聯盟正式開打 林書豪首戰先發獲18分 |url=https://udn.com/news/story/7002/5247583 |accessdate=2021-03-10 |work=NBA台灣 |date=2021-02-11}}</ref>。2月17日起，林書豪因為背傷連續缺席5場比賽<ref>{{cite news |author1=RotoWire Staff |title=Jeremy Lin: Battling back soreness |url=https://www.cbssports.com/fantasy/basketball/news/jeremy-lin-battling-back-soreness/ |accessdate=2021-03-10 |work=CBSSports.com |date=2021-02-17}}</ref><ref>{{cite news |author1=陳元廷 |title=缺賽5場強勢回歸 林書豪關鍵發揮助隊奪8連勝 |url=https://udn.com/news/story/7002/5285001 |accessdate=2021-03-10 |work=NBA台灣 |date=2021-03-01}}</ref>。3月9日，聖塔克魯茲勇士以96比108輸給[[萊克蘭魔術|萊克蘭魔術]]，止步於季後四強賽<ref>{{cite news |author1=蔡佳霖 |title=勇士不敵魔術四強止步 林書豪進帳20分 |url=https://udn.com/news/story/7002/5307135 |accessdate=2021-03-10 |work=NBA台灣 |date=2021-03-10 |archive-date=2021-03-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210321025023/https://udn.com/news/story/7002/5307135 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

=== 北京首鋼（2021年至2022年） ===
2021年6月12日，林書豪在個人社群媒體宣佈將重返CBA北京首鋼<ref>{{cite news |author1=龍柏安 |title=林書豪推特宣布 將重返CBA北京首鋼 |url=https://www.cna.com.tw/news/firstnews/202106120068.aspx |accessdate=2021-06-12 |agency=中央通訊社 |date=2021-06-12 |archive-date=2021-08-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210807054513/https://www.cna.com.tw/news/firstnews/202106120068.aspx |dead-url=no }}</ref>。8月7日，林書豪在個人社群媒體表示確診[[2019冠状病毒病|2019冠状病毒病]]<ref>{{cite news |author1=黃巧雯 |title=林書豪臉書自爆染疫 美國飛抵上海隔離時確診 |url=https://www.cna.com.tw/news/firstnews/202108075004.aspx |accessdate=2021-08-07 |agency=中央通訊社 |date=2021-08-07 |archive-date=2021-08-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210807054328/https://www.cna.com.tw/news/firstnews/202108075004.aspx |dead-url=no }}</ref>。9月3日，林書豪在個人社群媒體表示已經痊癒出院<ref>{{cite news |author1=黃及人 |title=住院30天 豪哥痊癒吃披薩解饞 |url=https://www.chinatimes.com/newspapers/20210904000534-260111?chdtv |accessdate=2022-01-03 |work=中國時報 |date=2021-09-04 |archive-date=2022-01-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220103084417/https://www.chinatimes.com/newspapers/20210904000534-260111?chdtv |dead-url=no }}</ref>。11月30日，北京首鋼宣布林書豪已完成註冊手續<ref>{{cite news |author1=邓睿侃 |title=林书豪正式回归北京首钢：回中国打球就像回家 |url=https://www.guancha.cn/sports/2021_11_30_616799.shtml |accessdate=2021-12-01 |work=观察者网 |date=2021-11-30 |archive-date=2021-12-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211201130434/https://www.guancha.cn/sports/2021_11_30_616799.shtml |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |title=2021-2022赛季CBA联赛外籍球员注册信息（11月30日） |url=https://www.cbaleague.com/#/news-register/detail/61a590b14c |website=中篮联 |accessdate=2021-12-01 |date=2021-11-30 |archive-date=2020-08-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200817211410/https://www.cbaleague.com/#/news-register/detail/61a590b14c |dead-url=no }}</ref>；年薪為税前不足200萬美元<ref>{{cite news |title=曝林书豪年薪腰斩，不足税前200万美元，为北京首钢做出巨大牺牲 |url=https://new.qq.com/omn/20211223/20211223A0BSY300.html |accessdate=2022-01-03 |work=腾讯新闻 |date=2021-12-23 |archive-date=2022-01-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220103084410/https://new.qq.com/omn/20211223/20211223A0BSY300.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。林書豪於例行賽首秀繳出23分、6助攻、4籃板，幫助北京首鋼以99比76擊退[[辽宁沈阳三生飞豹篮球俱乐部|遼寧本鋼]]<ref>{{cite news |author1=黃及人 |title=林書豪回歸摘23分6助攻 北京斬斷遼寧9連勝 |url=https://www.chinatimes.com/realtimenews/20211225003597-260403?chdtv |accessdate=2022-01-03 |work=中國時報 |date=2021-12-25 |archive-date=2022-01-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220103084414/https://www.chinatimes.com/realtimenews/20211225003597-260403?chdtv |dead-url=no }}</ref>。球隊在[[2022年CBA季后赛|季後賽]]首輪不敵[[吉林东北虎|吉林东北虎]]<ref>{{cite news |author1=游郁香 |title=林書豪拿11分「決勝時刻被冰」 首鋼季後賽爆冷出局被罵翻 |url=https://sports.ettoday.net/news/2222725 |accessdate=2022-04-05 |work=ETtoday |date=2022-04-04 |archive-date=2022-04-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220404142616/https://sports.ettoday.net/news/2222725 }}</ref>。

== 國家隊生涯 ==
2010年7月底，林書豪針對媒體謠傳將代表[[中華台北男子籃球代表隊|中華男籃]]出賽一事回應「現在一切都還沒決定，我無法回答這個問題。」<ref>{{cite news |author1=彭薇霓 |title=代表中華隊？八字還沒有一撇啦 |work=聯合報 |date=2010-07-29}}</ref>

2011年4月24日，時任中華男籃總教練[[周俊三|周俊三]]透露希望能徵召林書豪列入2011年[[東亞籃球錦標賽|東亞籃球錦標賽]]中華男籃24人培訓名單<ref>{{cite news |author1=葉士弘 |title=接掌台灣男籃隊 周俊三盼徵召林書豪 |url=https://sports.ltn.com.tw/news/paper/487079 |accessdate=2022-05-17 |work=自由時報 |date=2011-04-25 |archive-date=2022-05-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220517083839/https://sports.ltn.com.tw/news/paper/487079 }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |author1=楊育欣 |title=周俊三組夢幻隊 想挖林書豪 |work=聯合報 |date=2011-04-25}}</ref>。5月4日，周俊三提交24人培訓名單時表示答應林書豪未取得同意前不會擅自將他列入24人培訓名單，但名單備註中載明若取得林書豪的同意，將建議[[中華民國籃球協會|中華民國籃球協會]]特別徵召他入隊<ref>{{cite news |author1=葉士弘 |title=亞錦賽 特案徵召豪小子 |url=https://sports.ltn.com.tw/news/paper/489687 |accessdate=2022-05-17 |work=自由時報 |date=2011-05-05 |archive-date=2022-05-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220517083832/https://sports.ltn.com.tw/news/paper/489687 }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |author1=楊育欣 |title=男籃國家隊名單 林書豪暫不入列 |work=聯合報 |date=2011-05-05}}</ref>。6月1日，林書豪受訪時對於代表中華男籃或[[中国国家男子篮球队|中國男籃]]出賽的問題回應「這個問題我考慮很久，但我覺得，近期很難有答案。」<ref>{{cite news |author1=黄维 |title=林书豪坦言考虑加入中国男篮:这问题我思索了很久 |url=http://sports.sina.com.cn/cba/2011-06-01/04115601456.shtml |accessdate=2022-05-17 |work=广州日报大洋网 |date=2011-06-01 |archive-date=2011-06-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110604222420/http://sports.sina.com.cn/cba/2011-06-01/04115601456.shtml }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |author1=王樹衡 |title=林書豪 國家隊站哪邊？ |work=聯合晚報 |date=2011-06-02}}</ref>6月27日，時任中華民國籃球協會理事長[[丁守中|丁守中]]表示曾在5月底飛往美國舊金山與林書豪全家會談，稱林書豪當時回覆代表中華男籃出賽的機率是一半，因此考慮將林書豪列入[[2011年亞洲籃球錦標賽|2011年亞洲籃球錦標賽]]中華男籃24人培訓名單<ref>{{cite news |title=亞錦賽中華隊24人 林書豪將列入 |url=https://udn.com/NEWS/SPORTS/SPO5/6422828.shtml |accessdate=2021-10-17 |agency=中央通訊社 |date=2011-06-27 |via=聯合新聞網 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110630082313/https://udn.com/NEWS/SPORTS/SPO5/6422828.shtml |archivedate=2011-06-30 |dead-url=yes }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |author1=楊湘鈞 |title=阿豪征男籃亞錦賽？「有一半機會」 |work=聯合報 |date=2011-06-28}}</ref><ref>{{cite news |author1=陳雍仁 |title=林書豪披中華隊戰袍 八字已有一撇 |url=https://tw.appledaily.com/sports/20110628/YWXNZO5PI74OVWPTEOHGUVRIXA/ |accessdate=2021-10-17 |work=蘋果日報 |date=2011-06-28 |location=臺灣 |archive-date=2021-10-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211019212739/https://tw.appledaily.com/sports/20110628/YWXNZO5PI74OVWPTEOHGUVRIXA/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |author1=顏若瑾 |title=林書豪若出征 決不代表中國 |url=https://sports.ltn.com.tw/news/paper/504038 |accessdate=2021-10-17 |work=自由時報 |date=2011-06-28 |archive-date=2021-10-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211019131319/https://sports.ltn.com.tw/news/paper/504038 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。7月15日，丁守中表示林書豪因膝蓋受傷正在休養，[[金州勇士|金州勇士]]的醫療團隊建議林書豪不要參賽<ref>{{cite news |url=http://fibaasia.net/NewsDetails.aspx?id=1129 |title=TPE - Knee injury likely to keep Jeremy Lin out of Taipei NT |publisher=FIBA Asia |date=2011-07-16 |accessdate=2011-08-04 |archive-date=2012-06-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120619020117/http://fibaasia.net/NewsDetails.aspx?id=1129 |dead-url=yes }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |author1=葉士弘 |title=意願不敵膝傷 林書豪無緣亞錦賽 |url=https://sports.ltn.com.tw/news/paper/508884 |accessdate=2021-10-17 |work=自由時報 |date=2011-07-15 |archive-date=2021-11-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211111195327/https://sports.ltn.com.tw/news/paper/508884 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |author1=黃及人 |title=林書豪膝傷 無緣亞錦賽 |url=https://www.chinatimes.com/newspapers/20110716000773-260111?chdtv |accessdate=2021-10-17 |work=中國時報 |date=2011-07-16 |archive-date=2021-10-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211019211824/https://www.chinatimes.com/newspapers/20110716000773-260111?chdtv |dead-url=no }}</ref>。8月5日，林書豪受訪時表示（2011年）夏天有收到中華男籃與中國男籃的邀請，但與家人討論後決定2011年不會代表中國男籃出賽，至於中華男籃是因為膝蓋傷勢而無法加入<ref>{{cite news |author1=LMJ |title=林书豪明确拒绝中国男篮邀请 称退役后想当牧师 |url=https://sports.sohu.com/20110805/n315565561.shtml |accessdate=2022-05-17 |work=搜狐体育 |date=2011-08-05}}</ref><ref>{{cite news |author1=彭薇霓 |title=來台顯身手? 哈佛小子也OK 林書豪原屬意加入中華隊 但因膝傷作罷 面對大陸隊招手 他今年拒絕了 |work=聯合報 |date=2011-08-05}}</ref>。

2012年2月，時任[[中国篮球协会|中国篮球协会]]副主席胡-{加}-时針對媒體詢問關於中國籃球協會是否曾邀請過林書豪加入中國男籃一事回覆，中國籃球協會從來沒有邀請過林書豪，不過2008年以前時任中國男籃總教練[[尤纳斯·卡兹劳斯卡斯|尤纳斯]]有跟胡-{加}-时提過林書豪<ref>{{cite news |author1=盖源源 |title=篮协否认曾邀请林书豪入男篮 4年前他被尤帅提起 |url=http://sports.sina.com.cn/cba/2012-02-09/14525936348.shtml |accessdate=2022-05-17 |work=成都商报 |date=2012-02-09 |archive-date=2012-08-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120806203205/http://sports.sina.com.cn/cba/2012-02-09/14525936348.shtml }}</ref>。同年夏天，林書豪入選美國奧運男籃靶子隊（Select Team）與[[2012年夏季奥林匹克运动会美国男子篮球队|2012年夏季奥林匹克运动会美国男子篮球队]]選手陪練，但因為與[[紐約尼克|紐約尼克]]的受限制自由球員身份而未參與<ref>{{cite news |title=Jeremy Lin off U.S. select team because of free agency |date=2012-07-02 |agency=Associated Press |newspaper=USA Today |accessdate=2020-09-04 |url=https://usatoday30.usatoday.com/sports/basketball/nba/story/2012-07-02/Jeremy-Lin-off-US-select-team-because-of-free-agency/55991488/1 |archive-date=2018-07-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180725110703/https://usatoday30.usatoday.com/sports/basketball/nba/story/2012-07-02/Jeremy-Lin-off-US-select-team-because-of-free-agency/55991488/1 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |last=Stein |first=Marc |title=Coach K eyes end to Team USA stint |date=2012-05-14 |publisher=ESPN |url=https://www.espn.com/olympics/basketball/story/_/id/7928951/usa-basketball-coach-mike-krzyzewski-not-likely-return-2016-olympic-games |accessdate=2012-05-14 |archive-date=2016-09-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160901015844/http://www.espn.com/olympics/basketball/story/_/id/7928951/usa-basketball-coach-mike-krzyzewski-not-likely-return-2016-olympic-games |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.nownews.com/2012/07/03/11490-2830439.htm |title=合約喬不攏　林書豪退出奧運靶子隊 |publisher=Nownews |author=邵瑞峰 |date=2012-07-03 |accessdate=2012-09-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120709070027/http://www.nownews.com/2012/07/03/11490-2830439.htm |archive-date=2012-07-09 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

