== 球員資料 ==
除了傳球能力強之外，林書豪還透過攻擊籃框、擅長執行擋拆戰術，將自己打造成強壯、快節奏的進攻球員。他在職業生涯中改善自己的外線投籃，並在三分球線外造成威脅<ref name="fowler_07092015">{{cite news |last=Fowler |first=Scott |title=Jeremy Lin makes Hornets better, but hype beyond that is 'Linsanity' |date=2015-07-09 |newspaper=The Charlotte Observer |url=https://www.charlotteobserver.com/sports/spt-columns-blogs/scott-fowler/article26893057.html |accessdate=2020-09-04 |archive-date=2018-12-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181211035839/https://www.charlotteobserver.com/sports/spt-columns-blogs/scott-fowler/article26893057.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web|last=Pina|first=Michael|title=Finding the Ideal System and Role for Houston Rockets' Jeremy Lin|url=https://bleacherreport.com/articles/1899943-finding-the-ideal-system-and-role-for-houston-rockets-jeremy-lin|publisher=Bleacher Report|date=2013-12-25|accessdate=2014-02-09|archive-date=2014-01-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140129001057/http://bleacherreport.com/articles/1899943-finding-the-ideal-system-and-role-for-houston-rockets-jeremy-lin|dead-url=no}}</ref>。他因為有能力吸引到對手犯規，被認為很難防守<ref>{{cite web|last=Mihaly|first=Martin|title=Houston Rockets' Jeremy Lin showing his value|url=http://www.rantsports.com/nba/2014/02/03/houston-rockets-jeremy-lin-showing-his-value/|publisher=Rant Sports|date=2014-02-03|accessdate=2014-02-09|archive-date=2014-02-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140223001704/http://www.rantsports.com/nba/2014/02/03/houston-rockets-jeremy-lin-showing-his-value/|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。林書豪自認是冒險嘗試者<ref name="freidman"/>，但一直被批評他的失誤傾向和被認為缺乏有效的防守<ref>{{cite web|last=Wilmes|first=John|title=Why Jeremy Lin Is More Important to Houston Rockets Than Most Think|url=https://bleacherreport.com/articles/1926068-why-jeremy-lin-is-more-important-to-houston-rockets-than-most-think|publisher=Bleacher Report|date=2014-01-17|accessdate=2014-02-09|archive-date=2014-01-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140129000836/http://bleacherreport.com/articles/1926068-why-jeremy-lin-is-more-important-to-houston-rockets-than-most-think|dead-url=no}}</ref>。在2012年林來瘋過後，林書豪努力克服傷病<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.firstpost.com/sports/first-asian-american-nba-champion-jeremy-lin-struggles-to-find-takers-in-usa-joins-chinese-team-beijing-shougang-ducks-7273521.html|title=First Asian-American NBA champion Jeremy Lin struggles to find takers in USA, joins Chinese team Beijing Shougang Ducks|work=Firstpost|date=2019-09-03|accessdate=2020-09-04|archive-date=2020-08-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200828045610/https://www.firstpost.com/sports/first-asian-american-nba-champion-jeremy-lin-struggles-to-find-takers-in-usa-joins-chinese-team-beijing-shougang-ducks-7273521.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

== 個人生活 ==
林書豪是虔誠[[福音主義|福音派]]新教徒，在[[哈佛大學|哈佛大學]]期間擔任哈佛亞裔美國基督徒協會的主管<ref>{{cite news |title=Jeremy Lin: Taking Harvard basketball to new levels |url=https://studentsoul.intervarsity.org/jeremy-lin |date=2010-03-12 |accessdate=2020-09-04 |work=InterVarsity Christian Fellowship |archive-date=2017-06-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170615203858/http://studentsoul.intervarsity.org/jeremy-lin |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |author1=Michael Luo |title=Lin’s Appeal: Faith, Pride and Points |url=https://www.nytimes.com/2012/02/12/sports/basketball/the-knicks-jeremy-lin-faith-pride-and-points.html |accessdate=2020-09-04 |work=The New York Times |date=2012-02-11 |archive-date=2019-10-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191006040205/https://www.nytimes.com/2012/02/12/sports/basketball/the-knicks-jeremy-lin-faith-pride-and-points.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。他將自己於NBA的成功歸功於在沒有壓力的環境下打球，並說「我已經把這些交給上帝，我不再和別人的想法起爭執」<ref name="thompson_02132012">{{cite news |author=Thompson II, Marcus |title=Exclusive: Jeremy Lin says 'Lin-sanity' was triggered by a leap of faith |date=2012-02-13 |accessdate=2012-02-13 |newspaper=San Jose Mercury News |url=https://www.mercurynews.com/2012/02/13/exclusive-jeremy-lin-says-faith-in-god-triggered-lin-sanity/ |archive-date=2017-01-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170116032535/http://www.mercurynews.com/2012/02/13/exclusive-jeremy-lin-says-faith-in-god-triggered-lin-sanity/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。他曾希望成為牧師，從事能領導美國或國外的[[非營利組織|非營利組織]]服務工作<ref>{{cite news|last=Hughes|first=Frank|title=Former Harvard standout Lin ready to prove himself with Warriors|publisher=SI.com|date=2010-07-26|url=https://www.si.com/more-sports/2010/07/26/jeremy-linwarriors|accessdate=2010-10-23|quote=You do not hear too many NBA players talk like this, seeds of self-doubt occasionally sprouting. You also rarely hear this sentence: 'I compare myself to [Suns backup point guard] Goran Dragic.'|archive-date=2020-11-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201121174620/https://www.si.com/more-sports/2010/07/26/jeremy-linwarriors|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.nbadraft.net/jeremy-lin-interview/|title=Jeremy Lin Interview|publisher=NBADraft.net|date=2010-06-16|accessdate=2010-10-23|quote=I would be a pastor. It is something I think about doing when my playing days are over.|archive-date=2010-09-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100923202025/http://www.nbadraft.net/jeremy-lin-interview|dead-url=no}}</ref>，並談到曾在市中心社區工作、幫助弱勢孩童<ref>{{cite interview|last=Lin|first=Jeremy|interviewer=Michel Martin|title=Tell Me More|url=https://www.npr.org/templates/story/story.php?storyId=123368990|work=NPR|date=2010-02-04|accessdate=2010-10-25|quote=I mean, I get Asian jokes and, you know, when other fans try to heckle us, I don't really hear from other players very much.|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110207095259/http://www.npr.org/templates/story/story.php?storyId=123368990|archivedate=2011-02-07|deadurl=no}}</ref>。

林書豪曾表示能夠說[[現代標準漢語|中文]]、聽得懂中文，但只能夠讀寫一些；在哈佛大學時上過幾堂課程提升讀寫的能力<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.nbadraft.net/jeremy-lin-interview|title=Jeremy Lin Interview|publisher=NBADraft.net|date=2010-06-16|accessdate=2011-03-08|archive-date=2012-02-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120211003932/http://www.nbadraft.net/jeremy-lin-interview|dead-url=no|quote=I speak Mandarin and can read and write a little. I took a few classes at Harvard to get better in my reading and writing skills.}}</ref><ref>{{cite AV media |date=2010-07-28 |title=講到台灣美食... 林書豪中文超溜 |url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=SIhRTIkGYkA |access-date=2020-09-23 |time=00:55~01:02 |publisher=中華電視公司 |quote=My level? Well, I can understand it, I can speak some. |archive-date=2020-11-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201121174640/https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=SIhRTIkGYkA |dead-url=no }}</ref>。2012年加盟紐約尼克後，林書豪睡在他哥哥位於紐約[[曼哈頓|曼哈頓]][[下东区|下东区]]公寓裡的沙發上<ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.nytimes.com/2012/02/08/sports/basketball/jeremy-lin-has-burst-from-nba-novelty-act-to-knicks-star.html|title=From Ivy Halls to the Garden, Surprise Star Jolts the N.B.A.|author=Howard Beck|newspaper=The New York Times|date=2012-02-08|accessdate=2012-02-16|archive-date=2012-02-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120216025314/http://www.nytimes.com/2012/02/08/sports/basketball/jeremy-lin-has-burst-from-nba-novelty-act-to-knicks-star.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>，在他打出成績的前一天晚上，則睡在隊友[[兰德里·菲尔兹|兰德里·菲尔兹]]的沙發上，與紐約尼克的合約轉成保障後，他搬到紐約[[白原市_(紐約州)|白原市]]的豪華公寓<ref>{{cite web|url=http://espn.go.com/new-york/nba/story/_/id/7577073/report-new-york-knicks-jeremy-lin-moving-couch-apartment|date=2012-02-15|title=Jeremy Lin finds apartment|publisher=ESPN|accessdate=2012-03-04|archive-date=2012-02-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120218154034/http://espn.go.com/new-york/nba/story/_/id/7577073/report-new-york-knicks-jeremy-lin-moving-couch-apartment|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

林書豪是電子遊戲《[[Dota_2|Dota 2]]》的愛好者，從高中十年級就開始玩該系列遊戲的首款作品《[[DotA|DotA]]》。他出現在2014年以遊戲為中心的紀錄片《{{tsl|en|Free to Play (film)|免費遊玩}}》，他將《Dota 2》描述為一種「生活方式」，幫助他與家人和朋友相處地更好<ref>{{cite web|last=Breslau|first=Rod|url=https://www.gamespot.com/articles/nba-s-jeremy-lin-dota-2-is-more-than-just-a-game/1100-6437367/|title=NBA's Jeremy Lin: "Dota 2 is more than just a game"|date=2014-04-04|publisher=GameSpot|accessdate=2020-09-04|archive-date=2020-11-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201121174715/https://www.gamespot.com/articles/nba-s-jeremy-lin-dota-2-is-more-than-just-a-game/1100-6437367/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2016年林書豪組建名為「[[VG電子競技俱樂部#VGJ|VGJ]]」的個人《Dota 2》職業戰隊<ref>{{cite web|last1=Van Allen|first1=Eric|title=Jeremy Lin endorses new Dota 2 team VGJ|url=https://www.espn.com/esports/story/_/id/17579673/jeremy-lin-endorse-new-dota-2-team-vgj|website=ESPN|accessdate=2016-10-05|archive-date=2016-10-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161006054430/http://www.espn.com/esports/story/_/id/17579673/jeremy-lin-endorse-new-dota-2-team-vgj|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news |last1=Lin |first1=Jeremy |title=Esports vs. pro sports: Jeremy Lin is betting on both |url=https://qz.com/1438337/esports-vs-pro-sports-jeremy-lin-is-betting-on-both/ |accessdate=2018-10-31 |work=[[石英财经网|石英财经网]] |date=2018-10-31 |archive-date=2018-11-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181101015414/https://qz.com/1438337/esports-vs-pro-sports-jeremy-lin-is-betting-on-both/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

