林書豪的父親林繼明生於臺灣，就讀[[國立臺灣大學|國立臺灣大學]]，1977年考取[[中華民國教育部|中華民國教育部]][[公費留考#中華民國政府遷台後的公費留學|公費赴美留學]]，在[[老道明大學|老道明大學]]認識林書豪的母親吳信信；吳信信生於臺灣，在高中畢業前夕隨著她母親陳意子移民美國，就讀老道明大學，之後與林繼明一同到[[普渡大學|普渡大學]]攻讀更高學位<ref name="New York Times"/><ref name="harvard_school"/><ref name="caplan"/><ref name="豪小子是台灣人"/><ref name="bradsherny"/>。

林書豪的祖父林新懇生於現今臺灣[[彰化縣|彰化縣]][[北斗鎮_(台灣)|北斗鎮]]{{notetag|其家族1707年從中國大陸福建[[漳州府|漳州府]][[漳浦縣|漳浦縣]]移居臺灣，林新懇為家族在臺第七代<ref name="New York Times"/><ref name="豪小子是台灣人"/><ref name="bradsherny"/>。}}，在[[台灣日治時期|日治時期]]畢業自[[台北高等商業學校|台北高等商業學校]]，曾被外派到印尼峇里島火腿工廠擔任翻譯，於1947年[[二二八事件|二二八事件]]中倖存下來，在林繼明5歲時逝世，林書豪的祖母林朱阿麵則帶著五名孩子搬到臺北<ref name="New York Times"/><ref name="豪小子是台灣人"/><ref name="bradsherny"/>。林書豪1996年在國小六年級時到過臺灣，在2010年7月再次到臺灣，受邀參加於[[臺北小巨蛋|臺北小巨蛋]]舉辦的「[[姚明|姚]]基金慈善之旅」慈善義演賽，並前往[[總統府_(臺灣)|總統府]]與時任[[中華民國總統|中華民國總統]][[馬英九|馬英九]]見面<ref>{{cite news |author1=曹郁芬 |title=林書豪10事測驗 |work=自由時報 |date=2010-07-28 |page=A5 |quote=十、（曹郁芬問）想到台灣嗎？（林書豪答）想要回台見親人，上一次全家回台灣是一九九六年。}}</ref><ref>{{cite news |author1=曹郁芬 |title=林書豪進NBA 首戰獻給台灣 |url=https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/focus/paper/414795 |accessdate=2020-09-23 |work=自由時報 |date=2010-07-28 |archive-date=2020-11-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201121174728/https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/focus/paper/414795 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |author1=蔡裕隆 |title=NBA姚明邀約 林書豪返台秀球技 |url=https://tw.appledaily.com/headline/20100728/56SSUKO36EYLVFSTWDWQKF7H5E/ |accessdate=2020-09-15 |work=蘋果日報 |date=2010-07-28 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20200916070556/https://tw.appledaily.com/headline/20100728/56SSUKO36EYLVFSTWDWQKF7H5E/ |archivedate=2020-09-16 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |title=總統接見美國職籃NBA球員林書豪及其家人 |url=https://www.president.gov.tw/NEWS/14516 |accessdate=2020-09-16 |work=中華民國總統府 |date=2010-07-29 |archive-date=2020-11-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201121174744/https://www.president.gov.tw/NEWS/14516 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

林書豪的外曾祖父[[陳惟儉|陳惟儉]]與外祖母陳意子，皆生於現今中國大陸浙江省[[平湖市|平湖市]][[新仓镇_(平湖市)|新仓镇]]。陳意子1949年畢業於[[浙江省立醫學院|浙江省立醫學院]]，同年與她弟弟陳又軍隨[[中華民國政府遷台|中華民國政府來到臺灣]]，1969年舉家移民美國，在[[紐約州|紐約州]]執業行醫<ref name="brandsher02152012">{{cite news|last=Bradsher|first=Keith|title=In China, Lin Is a Star and a Symbol|date=2012-02-15|url=https://www.nytimes.com/2012/02/15/sports/basketball/in-china-knicks-lin-emerges-as-a-star-and-a-symbol.html|newspaper=The New York Times|page=B12|access-date=2019-11-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191031214418/https://www.nytimes.com/2012/02/15/sports/basketball/in-china-knicks-lin-emerges-as-a-star-and-a-symbol.html|archive-date=2019-10-31|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="豪小子是台灣人"/><ref name="bradsherny"/><ref name="平湖1"/><ref name="平湖2"/>。1998年陳意子與陳又軍在[[浙江省平湖中学|浙江省平湖中学]]設立「陳惟儉沈雪如獎學金」紀念林書豪的外曾祖父母，2008年後因陳意子年事已高，獎學金改由林書豪的父母親負責<ref name="平湖1">{{cite news|editor=鲍春伟|url=http://ph2009.zjol.com.cn/phnews/system/2010/07/25/012422741.shtml|title=NBA新秀林书豪与平湖有渊源|work=嘉兴日报|date=2010-07-26|accessdate=2014-08-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140427071923/http://ph2009.zjol.com.cn/phnews/system/2010/07/25/012422741.shtml|archive-date=2014-04-27|dead-url=no}}{{Cbignore}}</ref><ref name="平湖2">{{cite news |author1=徐文燕 |title=美籍华人陈意子回平捐送奖学金 |url=http://szb.ph2009.com/Html/Jxrb/20120601/Jxrb10575.Html |accessdate=2020-09-15 |work=嘉兴日报 |date=2012-06-01 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20200916004758/http://szb.ph2009.com/Html/Jxrb/20120601/Jxrb10575.Html |archivedate=2020-09-16 |dead-url=yes }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |title=乡聚千里之外 思怀故土情缘——平湖市侨务部门探访旅美乡贤 |url=http://www.zjsql.com.cn/index.php?m=content&c=index&a=show&catid=16&id=32673 |accessdate=2020-09-15 |work=浙江省归国华侨联合会 |date=2017-07-07 |archive-date=2020-09-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200915150900/http://www.zjsql.com.cn/index.php?m=content&c=index&a=show&catid=16&id=32673 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="平湖3"/>。2011年5月，林書豪首次到中國大陸浙江省平湖市，並在平湖中學與學生打場表演賽<ref name="平湖3">{{cite news |author1=古其铮 |title=华裔球星林书豪曾浙江寻亲 家族为中学奖学14年 |url=http://www.chinanews.com/ty/2012/02-16/3675179.shtml |accessdate=2020-09-18 |work=中国新闻网 |date=2012-02-16 |archive-date=2020-09-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200923145439/http://www.chinanews.com/ty/2012/02-16/3675179.shtml |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |author1=马国强 |title=林书豪外婆是浙江平湖人 曾多次祭祖寻根捐资助学 |url=http://sports.sina.com.cn/k/2011-05-30/16335945705.shtml |accessdate=2020-09-15 |work=嘉兴日报 |date=2011-05-30 |archive-date=2020-09-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200915145017/http://sports.sina.com.cn/k/2011-05-30/16335945705.shtml |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |editor=严国平 |title=追寻林书豪平湖中学印记 三分神准球技高深莫测 |url=https://sports.sohu.com/20120224/n335797194.shtml |accessdate=2020-09-18 |work=新民晚报 |date=2012-02-24 |archive-date=2020-09-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200923145455/https://sports.sohu.com/20120224/n335797194.shtml |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

=== 國籍 ===
林書豪的父母皆從臺灣移民至美國，均具美國和中華民國[[雙重國籍|雙重國籍]]<ref name="New York Times">{{cite news|last=Borden|first=Sam|url=https://www.nytimes.com/2012/02/26/sports/basketball/tight-knit-family-shares-lins-achievement.html|date=2012-02-26|work=New York Times|title=Tight-Knit Family Shares Lin's Achievement|accessdate=2014-08-24|archive-date=2020-08-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200820071942/https://www.nytimes.com/2012/02/26/sports/basketball/tight-knit-family-shares-lins-achievement.html|dead-url=no}}{{Cbignore}}</ref><ref name="豪小子是台灣人"/><ref name="bradsherny"/><ref name="caplan"/>。[[中華民國內政部|中華民國內政部]]在2012年表示，林書豪生於美國，除了是[[美國公民|美國公民]]，還透過父母的國籍成為中華民國[[無戶籍國民|無戶籍國民]]{{notetag|根據採[[屬人主義|屬人主義]]的《[[:s:國籍法_(民國105年)|中華民國國籍法]]》第二條「出生時父或母為[[中華民國國民|中華民國國民]]」之要件<ref name="中央通訊社"/>。}}，而當時林書豪沒有放棄中華民國籍，亦未辦理[[中華民國護照|中華民國護照]]<ref name="中央通訊社">{{cite news |author1=李明宗 |title=簡太郎：林書豪是中華民國國民 |url=https://www.cna.com.tw/news/firstnews/201206070004.aspx |accessdate=2019-10-24 |agency=中央通訊社 |date=2012-06-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120610035510/http://www.cna.com.tw/News/FirstNews/201206070004.aspx |archive-date=2012-06-10 |dead-url=yes }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |author1=陳思豪 |url=http://www.nownews.com/n/2012/02/17/418863 |title=內政部：林書豪有中華民國國籍 |work=NOWnews |date=2012-02-17 |accessdate=2013-11-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131113123030/http://www.nownews.com/n/2012/02/17/418863 |archive-date=2013-11-13 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。2020年7月30日，林書豪取得中華民國護照<ref>{{cite news |author1=鄭媁 |author2=楊正海 |author3=劉肇育 |author4=李隆揆 |title=林書豪申請入籍 取得中華民國護照 |url=https://udn.com/news/story/7003/4795456 |accessdate=2020-08-22 |work=聯合報 |date=2020-08-19 |archive-date=2020-08-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200826142355/https://udn.com/news/story/7003/4795456 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |author1=劉建邦 |title=林書豪取得中華民國護照 父親林繼明感謝徐國勇協助 |url=https://www.cna.com.tw/news/firstnews/202008195007.aspx |accessdate=2020-08-22 |agency=中央通訊社 |date=2020-08-19 |archive-date=2020-08-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200820092839/https://www.cna.com.tw/news/firstnews/202008195007.aspx |dead-url=no }}</ref>{{notetag|林書豪取得中華民國護照時在[[臺灣地區|臺灣地區]]並沒有設立戶籍，仍屬於[[無戶籍國民|無戶籍國民]]<ref>{{cite web |title=常見問答 > 移民 > 什麼是無戶籍國民？能不能領振興券？ |url=https://www.moi.gov.tw/chi/chi_faq/faq_detail.aspx?t=2&n=16838&p=11&f=10 |website=中華民國內政部全球資訊網 |accessdate=2020-10-18 |quote=無戶籍國民是指未曾在臺灣地區設有戶籍之僑居國外國民(例 如林書豪，他出生時父母為國民，其在國外出生但迄今尚未回臺設籍) |archive-date=2020-11-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201121174921/https://www.moi.gov.tw/chi/chi_faq/faq_detail.aspx?t=2&n=16838&p=11&f=10 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |author1=陳俊華 |title=役政署：林書豪若未設戶籍 就沒服兵役問題 |url=https://www.cna.com.tw/news/firstnews/202008190384.aspx |accessdate=2020-09-04 |agency=中央通訊社 |date=2020-08-19 |archive-date=2020-08-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200821000106/https://www.cna.com.tw/news/firstnews/202008190384.aspx |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |title=林書豪「入籍」台灣再次引發中國大陸「惠台」措施討論 |url=https://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/trad/chinese-news-53860791 |accessdate=2020-09-04 |work=BBC |date=2020-08-22 |archive-date=2020-11-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201121174908/https://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/trad/chinese-news-53860791 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。}}。

=== 血統 ===
{{quote box|align=right|width=30%|style=padding:10px|quote=我當然與臺灣有深厚的連結，我有很多親戚在那裡，每次我返回（臺灣）我都會感受到，我與父母來自的地方的連結。而我對中國（大陸）也有同樣的感受，因為我的外祖父母來自那裡。在我（2011年）來到中國（大陸）時，我前往外祖母長大的村莊，那是一個很棒的經歷。|source=—林書豪2012年接受《[[運動畫刊|運動畫刊]]》專訪<ref>{{cite news |author1=Albert Chen |title=The Politicization of Jeremy Lin |url=https://vault.si.com/vault/2012/12/17/the-politicization-of-jeremy-lin |accessdate=2021-03-15 |work=Sports Illustrated Vault |date=2012-12-17 |quote="I definitely have strong ties to Taiwan," Lin said. "I have a ton of cousins there, and every time I go back, I feel this connection to this place where my parents came from." He added, "And I feel the same way about China because my grandparents came from there. When I went to China [in 2011], I went to the village where my grandmother grew up, and that was an amazing experience." |archive-date=2020-11-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201112032004/https://vault.si.com/vault/2012/12/17/the-politicization-of-jeremy-lin |dead-url=no }}</ref>}}
林書豪2010年於「姚基金慈善之旅」慈善義演賽的記者會上表示，「你可以稱我為一位臺灣（Taiwanese）籃球運動員<!-- 中文翻譯同「https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Category:Taiwanese_basketball_players」 -->、一位中國（大陸）（Chinese）籃球運動員<!-- 中文翻譯同「https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Category:Chinese_basketball_players」 -->或只是一位籃球運動員」<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.taiwannews.com.tw/en/news/1331817|title=NBA player Jeremy Lin focused on the court, skirts national team issues for now|publisher=Taiwan News|author=Joseph Yeh|date=2010-07-29|accessdate=2012-02-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200325190013/https://www.taiwannews.com.tw/en/news/1331817|archive-date=2020-03-25|dead-url=no|quote=You can call me a Taiwanese basketball player, a Chinese basketball player or just a basketball player.}}</ref>；2011年接受[[美国在线|美国在线]]旗下《{{tsl|en|Fanhouse|Fanhouse}}》記者{{tsl|en|Elie Seckbach|艾莉·塞克巴赫}}訪問時說，「我以身為一位華人（Chinese）感到自豪，我為我的父母來自臺灣感到驕傲」<ref>{{cite AV media |date=2011-01-10 |title=NBA Star Jeremy Lin Is A Smart Player |url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ARFmtP8tzms |access-date=2011-03-08 |time=01:04~01:16 |publisher=Fanhouse |quote=It’s humbling, a privilege, and an honor. I’m really proud of being Chinese. I’m really proud of my parents being from Taiwan. I just thank God for the opportunity. |archive-date=2020-11-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201121174913/https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ARFmtP8tzms |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |author1=Gene Wang |title=Sports Jeremy Lin can be inspiration to Chinese Americans |url=https://www.washingtonpost.com/blogs/wizards-insider/post/jeremy-lin-can-be-inspiration-to-chinese-americans/2012/02/09/gIQAtaVo1Q_blog.html |accessdate=2020-09-23 |work=The Washington Post |date=2012-02-09 |quote=It’s humbling, a privilege, and an honor,” Lin said in an interview with AOL Fanhouse’s Elie Seckbach. “I’m really proud of being Chinese. I’m really proud of my parents being from Taiwan. I just thank God for the opportunity. |archive-date=2020-09-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200923145616/https://www.washingtonpost.com/blogs/wizards-insider/post/jeremy-lin-can-be-inspiration-to-chinese-americans/2012/02/09/gIQAtaVo1Q_blog.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。2012年2月，其父親林繼明接受[[美國之音|美國之音]]採訪時說，「我的籍貫是臺灣彰化北斗鎮，林書豪是臺灣人的第9代，祖先來自福建漳浦」、「林書豪既是臺灣人、也是中國（大陸）人，不介意中國大陸媒體有意強調林書豪的中國大陸籍貫，或許出於與有榮焉的原因」<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.voachinese.com/a/article-20120213-jeremy-lin-ancestry-139246878/804103.html|title=“林来疯”引发林书豪籍贯之争|publisher=美国之音|date=2012-02-13|accessdate=2017-05-19|archive-date=2020-08-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200826142342/https://www.voachinese.com/a/article-20120213-jeremy-lin-ancestry-139246878/804103.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>；其伯父林繼宗在接受[[紐約時報|紐約時報]]專訪時表示，「他們一家、包括林書豪，肯定是臺灣人」，還補充說「依中國大陸和臺灣的文化傳統，林書豪的身份要看父親這邊來決定」<ref name="豪小子是台灣人">{{Cite web|url=http://www2.cna.com.tw/News/aSPT/201202160057.aspx|title=林父：豪小子是台灣人|publisher=中央通訊社|date=2012-02-15|accessdate=2012-02-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120217045223/http://www2.cna.com.tw/News/aSPT/201202160057.aspx|archive-date=2012-02-17|dead-url=yes}}</ref><ref name="bradsherny">{{Cite web|url=https://www.nytimes.com/2012/02/16/sports/basketball/jeremy-lins-grandmother-watches-along-with-taiwan.html|title=An Odd Game a Grandmother Can Appreciate|publisher=The New York Times|author=Keith Bradsher|date=2012-02-15|accessdate=2012-02-15|archive-date=2020-05-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200521125958/https://www.nytimes.com/2012/02/16/sports/basketball/jeremy-lins-grandmother-watches-along-with-taiwan.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

== 種族議題 ==
林書豪在籃球生涯中曾遭遇與自身亞裔（Asian）血統有關的種族歧視。他在哈佛大學打球時經常聽到諸如「[[馄饨|馄饨]]湯」、「[[糖醋排骨|糖醋排骨]]」、「睜開你的眼睛」、「回中國（大陸）去」、「管弦樂隊在校園的另一邊」等偏激嘲笑語句，或者是假扮成華人（Chinese）的胡言亂語<ref name="harvard_school">{{cite news |author1=Pablo S. Torre |title=HARVARD SCHOOL OF BASKETBALL |url=https://vault.si.com/vault/2010/02/01/harvard-school-of-basketball |date=2010-02-01 |accessdate=2020-09-04 |work=Sports Illustrated Vault |quote=What's most surprising? The possibility that he might become the first Asian-American draft pick in NBA history? The bigoted jeers he regularly hears at games (everything from "wonton soup" to "Open your eyes!")? |archive-date=2021-02-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210216070427/https://vault.si.com/vault/2010/02/01/harvard-school-of-basketball |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="asian_american"/><ref name="harvards_hoops"/>。哈佛隊友奧利弗·麥納利（Oliver McNally）表示，曾有一位常春藤聯盟的球員在比賽中用「[[Chink|Chink]]」辱罵林書豪<ref name="harvards_hoops"/>。

2012年2月10日，林書豪在紐約尼克對戰洛杉磯湖人的比賽中攻下38分，[[FOX_Sports|FOX Sports]]專欄作家{{tsl|en|Jason Whitlock|傑森·惠洛克}}於推特上發布以下關於林書豪性功能的語句，「紐約市的某位幸運女士今晚會感受到幾英寸的疼痛」<ref name="Whitlock-1"/><ref name="Whitlock-2"/>。《{{tsl|en|Hyphen (magazine)|Hyphen}}》寫道，傑森·惠洛克「強化『亞洲小陰莖』這無趣又陰險的刻板印象」<ref>{{cite magazine |last=Kim |first=Sylvie |title=Spike, Jeremy, and Stopping "Asian Profi'Lin" |date=2012-02-13 |magazine=Hyphen |accessdate=2020-09-04 |url=https://hyphenmagazine.com/blog/2012/2/13/spike-jeremy-and-stopping-asian-profilin |archive-date=2019-06-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190630231138/https://hyphenmagazine.com/blog/2012/2/13/spike-jeremy-and-stopping-asian-profilin |dead-url=no }}</ref>。[[美國亞裔記者協會|美國亞裔記者協會]]要求其向林書豪道歉。傑森·惠洛克道歉說，「我貶低一個令人愉悅的體育時刻，為此我真的很抱歉」<ref name="Whitlock-1">{{cite news |last=Schilken |first=Chuck |title=Fox Sports' Jason Whitlock apologizes for Jeremy Lin tweet |date=2012-02-13 |newspaper=Los Angeles Times |accessdate=2020-09-04 |url=https://latimesblogs.latimes.com/sports_blog/2012/02/fox-sports-jason-whitlock-apologizes-for-jeremy-lin-tweet.html |archive-date=2018-12-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181203152217/https://latimesblogs.latimes.com/sports_blog/2012/02/fox-sports-jason-whitlock-apologizes-for-jeremy-lin-tweet.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="Whitlock-2">{{cite news |last=Dwyer |first=Kelly |title=Jason Whitlock apologizes for his unfunny Jeremy Lin comment on Twitter |date=2012-02-13 |publisher=Yahoo |accessdate=2020-09-04 |url=https://sports.yahoo.com/jason-whitlock-apologizes-unfunny-jeremy-lin-twitter-145934497.html |archive-date=2021-07-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210713012411/https://sports.yahoo.com/jason-whitlock-apologizes-unfunny-jeremy-lin-twitter-145934497.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

同樣是在2012年2月，拳擊手[[弗洛伊德·梅威瑟|弗洛伊德·梅威瑟]]於推特上寫道，「林書豪是位好球員，但只因為他是亞裔（Asian）而被爭相報導，黑人球員每天晚上都能打出相同出色的成績，卻得不到同樣的讚揚」<ref>{{cite news|last=Weir|first=Tom|title=Floyd Mayweather Jr. plays the race card on Jeremy Lin|date=2012-02-13|work=USA Today|accessdate=2020-09-04|url=http://content.usatoday.com/communities/gameon/post/2012/02/floyd-mayweather-jr-plays-the-race-card-on-jeremy-lin/1|archive-date=2012-02-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120216205622/http://content.usatoday.com/communities/gameon/post/2012/02/floyd-mayweather-jr-plays-the-race-card-on-jeremy-lin/1|dead-url=no}}</ref>。NBC紐約為了回應弗洛伊德·梅威瑟而指出，「在籃球歷史上，不論何種膚色球員在前四次先發，都難以達到林書豪上週為紐約尼克所打出的表現」<ref>{{cite news |last=Alper |first=Josh |title=Jeremy Lin Isn't Totally Without Precedent |date=2012-02-14 |publisher=NBC New York |accessdate=2020-09-04 |url=https://www.nbcnewyork.com/news/sports/jeremy-lin-mark-fidrych-floyd-mayweather-hype-linsanity/1971828/ |archive-date=2020-05-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200522040611/https://www.nbcnewyork.com/news/sports/jeremy-lin-mark-fidrych-floyd-mayweather-hype-linsanity/1971828/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

2012年2月17日，[[ESPN|ESPN]]對林書豪使用種族歧視的口吻。在林書豪輸給夏洛特黃蜂的比賽中出現9次失誤，ESPN貼出標題名為「盔甲上的裂縫（[[Chink|Chink]] in the Armor）」的文章。該標題在35分鐘後被移除，ESPN則進行道歉<ref>{{cite news |agency=Associated Press |date=2012-02-18 |newspaper=The Washington Post |accessdate=2020-09-04 |url=https://www.washingtonpost.com/blogs/early-lead/post/espn-apologizes-for-offensive-headline-that-appeared-on-jeremy-lin-knicks-story/2012/02/18/gIQAANz0LR_blog.html |title=ESPN apologizes for offensive headline on mobile sites for Jeremy Lin story |archive-date=2020-03-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200301051022/https://www.washingtonpost.com/blogs/early-lead/post/espn-apologizes-for-offensive-headline-that-appeared-on-jeremy-lin-knicks-story/2012/02/18/gIQAANz0LR_blog.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。寫下標題的ESPN編輯表示，標題沒有任何種族含義，但還是遭到ESPN解僱。林書豪後來聯繫到這位編輯，並與他共進午餐，林書豪告訴他，他不認為標題帶有種族歧視的意思<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.wbur.org/onlyagame/2020/01/10/anthony-federico-espn-priesthood-jeremy-lin|title=Linsanity, A Botched Headline And An ESPN Editor's Journey To The Priesthood|website=wbur|accessdate=2020-09-04|archive-date=2020-06-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200618041107/https://www.wbur.org/onlyagame/2020/01/10/anthony-federico-espn-priesthood-jeremy-lin|dead-url=no}}</ref>。紐約尼克電台主持人{{tsl|en|Spero Dedes|斯佩羅·戴德斯}}在{{tsl|en|1050 ESPN New York|1050 ESPN 紐約}}也使用過該措辭<ref>{{cite news |last=Boren |first=Cindy |title=ESPN fires employee for offensive Jeremy Lin headline; "SNL" weighs in |date=2012-02-19 |newspaper=The Washington Post |accessdate=2020-09-04 |url=https://www.washingtonpost.com/blogs/early-lead/post/espn-fires-employee-for-offensive-jeremy-lin-headline-snl-weighs-in-video/2012/02/19/gIQAYO7qNR_blog.html |archive-date=2012-02-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120220112955/http://www.washingtonpost.com/blogs/early-lead/post/espn-fires-employee-for-offensive-jeremy-lin-headline-snl-weighs-in-video/2012/02/19/gIQAYO7qNR_blog.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |last=Collins |first=Scott |title=Jeremy Lin and ESPN: Network rushes to quell furor over 'chink' comments |date=2012-02-19 |newspaper=Los Angeles Times |accessdate=2020-09-04 |url=https://latimesblogs.latimes.com/showtracker/2012/02/espn-jeremy-lin-chink-comments-fired-suspended.html |archive-date=2020-01-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200101162603/https://latimesblogs.latimes.com/showtracker/2012/02/espn-jeremy-lin-chink-comments-fired-suspended.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |last=Spar |first=Jerry |title=Mashup: Lin accepts ESPN apology for slur |date=2012-02-20 |publisher=Entercom Boston |accessdate=2020-09-04 |url=http://www.weei.com/sports/boston/this-just-in/21178076/mashup-lin-accepts-espn-apology-slur |archive-date=2012-02-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120222193703/http://www.weei.com/sports/boston/this-just-in/21178076/mashup-lin-accepts-espn-apology-slur |dead-url=no }}</ref>。2013年11月14日，ESPN《{{tsl|en|SportsCenter|體育中心}}》主播{{tsl|en|Jorge Andres|豪爾赫·安德烈斯}}在林書豪以21分的表現幫助休士頓火箭戰勝紐約尼克後，於直播中評論林書豪「在使用一些熱花生油做飯」，豪爾赫·安德烈斯事後對此表示歉意<ref>{{cite news |title=ESPN anchor apologizes for making racially insensitive comment about Jeremy Lin |date=2013-11-16 |newspaper=New York Daily News |accessdate=2020-09-04 |url=https://www.nydailynews.com/sports/basketball/espn-anchor-apologizes-making-racially-insensitive-comment-lin-article-1.1518953 |archive-date=2019-04-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190405165550/https://www.nydailynews.com/sports/basketball/espn-anchor-apologizes-making-racially-insensitive-comment-lin-article-1.1518953 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。
{{quote box|align=left|width=30%|style=padding:10px|quote=我知道很多人說我「擅長運動」和「做事情迅速」都只是錯覺，而我不確定什麼是錯覺。但可能因為我是美國亞裔的事實。但我認為沒關係，這還在我能夠接受的範圍之內，雖然會讓我耿耿於懷。而我很自豪作為美國亞裔，並樂愛這個事實。|source=—林書豪在2012年[[NBA全明星周末|NBA全明星周末]]的訪問<ref>{{cite news |title=NBA: Jeremy Lin embracing his first all-star weekend |url=https://taipeitimes.com/News/sport/archives/2012/02/26/2003526406 |accessdate=2020-10-26 |agency=AFP |date=2012-02-26 |quote=I know a lot of people say I’m ‘deceptively athletic’ and ‘deceptively quick,’ and I’m not sure what’s deceptive, but it could be the fact that I’m Asian-American. But I think that’s fine. It’s something that I embrace, and it gives me a chip on my shoulder. But I’m very proud to be Asian-American and I love it. |archive-date=2020-11-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201121175040/https://taipeitimes.com/News/sport/archives/2012/02/26/2003526406 |dead-url=no }}</ref>}}
林書豪被推測在職業生涯中受到外界對美國亞裔運動能力的刻板印象的負面影響。《時代雜誌》的肖恩·格雷戈里（Sean Gregory）在2009年對於林書豪沒有收到第一級別學校的籃球獎學金寫道，「（林書豪）很瘦骨嶙峋，但不要質疑這一點點有意或無意的[[种族归纳|種族刻板印象]]，都導致他未獲錄取」<ref name="harvards_hoops">{{cite magazine |last=Gregory |first=Sean |title=Harvard's Hoops Star Is Asian. Why's That a Problem? |magazine=Time |date=2009-12-31 |url=http://content.time.com/time/magazine/article/0,9171,1953708,00.html |accessdate=2010-11-08 |quote='I've heard it at most of the Ivies if not all of them,' he says. Lin is reluctant to mention the specific nature of such insults, but according to Harvard teammate Oliver McNally, another Ivy League player called him a C word that rhymes with ink during a game last season. |archive-date=2013-09-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130923065536/http://content.time.com/time/magazine/article/0,9171,1953708,00.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。林書豪2008年表示，「我並不是說前五名的州立大學會自動發送邀請，但我真的覺得（我的[[種族|種族]]）確實影響教練招募我的方式。我想如果我是不同的種族，我會受到不一樣的待遇」<ref name="asian_american">{{cite news |last=Chu |first=Bryan |title=Asian Americans remain rare in men's college basketball |newspaper=San Francisco Chronicle |date=2008-12-16 |url=https://www.sfgate.com/sports/article/Asian-Americans-remain-rare-in-men-s-college-3258007.php |accessdate=2010-11-08 |quote='I hear everything: "Go back to China. Orchestra is on the other side of campus. Open up your eyes,"' Lin said. 'They're yelling at me before, during and after. I'm an easy target because I'm Asian. Sometimes it makes me uncomfortable, but it's part of the game.' |archive-date=2012-11-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121105014848/http://www.sfgate.com/sports/article/Asian-Americans-remain-rare-in-men-s-college-3258007.php |dead-url=no }}</ref>。在林書豪的大學生涯中，只有不到0.5%的第一級別男子籃球運動員是美國亞裔<ref name="harvards_hoops"/><ref name="asian_american"/>。林書豪的高中籃球教練彼得·迪彭布洛克（Peter Diepenbrock）原本並不認為林書豪的種族會影響到他的招募意願，但在2012年看到10名第一級別教練對一位他評價為「不錯的大專球員」的黑人學生表達興趣後改變了想法<ref>{{cite news|url=https://latimesblogs.latimes.com/sports_blog/2012/02/jeremy-lins-high-school-coach-says-race-hindered-opportunities.html|title=Jeremy Lin's high school coach says race hindered opportunities|work=Los Angeles Times|date=2012-02-13|accessdate=2012-02-14|author=Bolch, Ben|archive-date=2012-02-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120215070331/http://latimesblogs.latimes.com/sports_blog/2012/02/jeremy-lins-high-school-coach-says-race-hindered-opportunities.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。基於對其天賦具有「錯覺性」評價，林書豪在2013年接受《[[60分鐘|60分鐘]]》採訪時表示，他有種「直覺」認為自己的種族是導致他落選的原因之一<ref name="barron">{{cite news |last=Barron |first=David |title=Lin tells "60 Minutes" his ethnicity played a role in him going undrafted |date=2013-04-05 |newspaper=Houston Chronicle |accessdate=2020-09-04 |url=https://blog.chron.com/sportsupdate/2013/04/lin-tells-60-minutes-his-ethnicity-may-have-stymied-college-recruiting-offers/ |archive-date=2019-10-31 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191031214446/https://blog.chron.com/sportsupdate/2013/04/lin-tells-60-minutes-his-ethnicity-may-have-stymied-college-recruiting-offers/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。時任NBA主席[[大卫·斯特恩|大卫·斯特恩]]也認為林書豪會落選是因為受到歧視。大卫·斯特恩在2013年說，「我不知道他是否因為就讀哈佛大學而受到歧視，還是因為他是亞裔（Asian）」<ref name="barron"/>。一些球迷和評論員認為金州勇士和林書豪簽約只是宣傳噱頭<ref name="beck_12292011"/>。球隊總管{{tsl|en|Larry Riley (basketball)|拉里·萊利}}則否認是為了迎合[[舊金山灣區|舊金山灣區]]龐大的亞裔人口，他明白有些人會如此看待。拉里·萊利說，「我們在整個夏季聯賽中對他進行過評估，在他身上所發生的事就是證實過去我們已經相信的」<ref name="culpepper"/>。當時球隊以他為中心創立一場特別活動，拉里·萊利表示，如果林書豪並不是優先作為籃球運動員，那些是不明智的想法<ref>{{cite news|last=Castillo|first=Jorge|title=Harvard graduate Jeremy Lin blazes unique trail to Golden State Warriors|newspaper=The Washington Post|date=2010-07-28|url=https://www.washingtonpost.com/wp-dyn/content/article/2010/07/27/AR2010072705802.html|accessdate=2010-10-21|quote='If he didn't have the skill set to go with it, that's not something you want to get into,' Riley said.|archive-date=2010-08-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100812084125/http://www.washingtonpost.com/wp-dyn/content/article/2010/07/27/AR2010072705802.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。{{tsl|en|Rex Walters|雷克斯·沃爾特斯}}補充道，「那些不認為刻板印象存在的人瘋了。如果（林書豪）是白人，他會是位神射手，或是令人陶醉的球員。但如果他是亞裔（Asian），他的數學會很好，我們並不會想要他」<ref>{{cite news |last=Reilly |first=Rick |title=How do you like me now? |date=2012-02-14 |publisher=ESPN |accessdate=2020-09-04 |url=https://www.espn.com/espn/story/_/id/7574087/overlooking-jeremy-lin |archive-date=2020-05-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200525055832/https://www.espn.com/espn/story/_/id/7574087/overlooking-jeremy-lin |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

林書豪參加NBA選秀的經歷被[[迈克尔·刘易斯|迈克尔·刘易斯]]所著的《{{tsl|en|The Undoing Project|失敗計劃}}》作為例子，書中詳細介紹刻板印象是如何壓倒性影響人的決策，甚至在面對相互矛盾的證據時也會如此。休士頓火箭總管[[达雷尔·莫雷|达雷尔·莫雷]]在書中表示，林書豪於選秀前的測試中表現非常出色，「他在我們的（統計）模型中表現亮眼，我們的模型說他是首輪第15順位」<ref name="Lewis">{{cite book |author1=Michael Lewis |title=The Undoing Project: A Friendship That Changed Our Minds |date=2016-12-06 |isbn=9780393254594}}</ref>{{rp|19}}。在休士頓火箭未選擇林書豪的一年後，開始測量球員第一步和第二步的爆發速度，林書豪比所有測量球員還要快，他改變方向的速度遠超過大多數NBA球員。达雷尔·莫雷表示，「他有著令人難以置信的運動能力，但現實中的每個人，包含我在內，都認為他缺乏運動能力，除了他是亞裔（Asian）外，我想不出其他理由」<ref name="Lewis"/>{{rp|20}}<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.slate.com/articles/arts/books/2016/12/how_daryl_morey_used_behavioral_economics_to_revolutionize_the_art_of_nba.html|title=Basketball's Nerd King|first=Michael|last=Lewis|date=2016-12-06|via=Slate|accessdate=2020-09-04|archive-date=2020-08-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200809210950/http://www.slate.com/articles/arts/books/2016/12/how_daryl_morey_used_behavioral_economics_to_revolutionize_the_art_of_nba.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.cbsnews.com/news/michael-lewis-the-undoing-project-a-friendship-that-changed-our-minds-amos-tversky-daniel-kahneman/|title=Author Michael Lewis on "the best two characters I've ever had as a writer"|date=2016-12-06|website=cbsnews|accessdate=2020-09-04|archive-date=2020-07-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200722070655/https://www.cbsnews.com/news/michael-lewis-the-undoing-project-a-friendship-that-changed-our-minds-amos-tversky-daniel-kahneman/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news |author1=體育中心 |title=林書豪在選秀會沒球隊要 只因他是亞洲人？ |url=https://sports.ltn.com.tw/news/breakingnews/2005093 |accessdate=2020-08-26 |work=自由時報 |date=2017-03-15 |archive-date=2018-12-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181216210543/http://sports.ltn.com.tw/news/breakingnews/2005093 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

林書豪第一次前往舊金山{{tsl|en|Kezar Pavilion|基薩場館}}參與職業運動員與業餘運動員之間的比賽（pro-am game）時，有位保全告訴他，「對不起先生，今晚這裡沒有排球（比賽），只有籃球（比賽）」<ref>{{cite news|last=Knapp|first=Gwen|title=Bay Area appeal makes Lin good bet|newspaper=San Francisco Chronicle|date=2010-07-22|url=https://www.sfgate.com/warriors/knapp/article/Bay-Area-appeal-makes-Lin-good-bet-3180646.php|accessdate=2010-08-28|quote=He pointed out that even people who don't mean any harm assume that Lin, whose parents came to the United States from Taiwan, doesn't have game.|archive-date=2019-12-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191212085340/https://www.sfgate.com/warriors/knapp/article/Bay-Area-appeal-makes-Lin-good-bet-3180646.php|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news |last=Yng |first=Jeff |title=Jeremy Lin's Pop Culture Slam Dunk |date=2012-05-10 |work=The Wall Street Journal |accessdate=2020-09-04 |url=https://www.wsj.com/articles/BL-SEB-68924 |archive-date=2021-06-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210608231957/https://www.wsj.com/articles/BL-SEB-68924 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。早在為紐約尼克效力時，麥迪遜廣場花園的一名保全就曾誤以為林書豪是訓練師，阻止他進入球員入口<ref>{{cite news |last=Yang |first=Jeff |title=Yes, 'Linsanity' Is Still a Thing |date=2013-03-18 |work=The Wall Street Journal |accessdate=2020-09-04 |url=https://www.wsj.com/articles/BL-SEB-73967 |archive-date=2020-11-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201121175138/https://www.wsj.com/articles/BL-SEB-73967 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。在與夏洛特黃蜂簽約後，這位在NBA已經打滾5年的老將不得不說服夏洛特[[光譜中心|光譜中心]]的保全相信他是球員<ref>{{cite news |last=Pandian |first=Anath |title=Jeremy Lin had to persuade Hornets security he plays for team |date=2015-09-12 |publisher=CBS Sports |accessdate=2020-09-04 |url=https://www.cbssports.com/nba/news/jeremy-lin-had-to-persuade-hornets-security-he-plays-for-team/ |archive-date=2016-12-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161210152726/http://www.cbssports.com/nba/news/jeremy-lin-had-to-persuade-hornets-security-he-plays-for-team/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。而林書豪在2019年多倫多暴龍與[[密爾瓦基公鹿|密爾瓦基公鹿]]的東區冠軍賽第二場賽事結束後，要登上球隊巴士時被公鹿主場的保全攔下來<ref>{{cite news |title=豪囧！季後賽成邊緣人 林書豪賽後竟被警衛刁難 |url=https://sports.ltn.com.tw/news/breakingnews/2801469 |accessdate=2020-10-27 |work=自由時報 |date=2019-06-25 |archive-date=2020-11-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201121175149/https://sports.ltn.com.tw/news/breakingnews/2801469 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

2015年林書豪在接受《{{tsl|en|ESPN The Magazine|ESPN雜誌}}》{{tsl|en|Pablo S. Torre|巴柏羅·S·托雷}}採訪時表示，他認為人們對於亞裔（Asians）的易於失誤或無法好好使用雙手的見解，影響到他作為一位球員的聲望，儘管數據顯示他在這兩個方面都有所提高。他還指出自己是缺乏速度的差勁後衛的聲望，而迈克·德安东尼則表示林書豪「是我們訓練過速度最快的運動員之一」<ref name="torre_03272015"/>。林書豪還認為，他在紐約尼克的表現可能因為他的種族而獲得過多的關注，「人們只是不習慣看到亞裔（Asians）能夠做到某些事，所以造成一種很極端影響」<ref name="torre_03272015"/>。林書豪還表示，「人們只是不尊重亞裔（Asians）能夠做到的某些事情，比如運動、籃球方面等等」<ref>{{cite video|title=First Person: Jeremy Lin (Full Interview)|date=2011-12-15|publisher=Palo Alto Online|series=First Person|url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=gqrrKLcvPSE|accessdate=2012-02-11|archive-date=2020-11-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201121175152/https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=gqrrKLcvPSE|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2016年回到紐約為布魯克林籃網效力後，林書豪在認真思考種族問題時表示，「從某些方面來說，如果我擁有不同膚色，林來瘋就不會是林來瘋，這是很有可能的，但這還不是個大問題。而這也成為我的優勢，但如果你看到在我獲得可以上場的位置之前有很多障礙，那些很多陳舊刻板印象絕對是障礙，我必須與之對抗。而我一直都明白有好有壞，你必須要把它們放在一起，然後感謝這一切」<ref>{{Cite web | last=Botte | first=Peter | date=2016-09-26 | title=Lin: If I wasn't Asian, Linsanity wouldn't have been a big deal – NY Daily News | url=https://www.nydailynews.com/sports/basketball/nets/lin-wasn-asian-linsanity-wouldn-big-deal-article-1.2807193 | work=Daily News | access-date=2016-09-28 | archive-date=2016-09-27 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160927182208/http://www.nydailynews.com/sports/basketball/nets/lin-wasn-asian-linsanity-wouldn-big-deal-article-1.2807193 | dead-url=no }}</ref>。

ESPN網站的{{tsl|en|J. A. Adande|J·A·阿丹德}}寫道，提高對美國亞裔的種族敏感性是「（林書豪）在麥迪遜廣場花園産生迴盪的另一種影響方式」<ref>{{cite news |last=Adande |first=J.A. |title=Jeremy Lin, race and lessons learned |date=2012-02-22 |publisher=ESPN |accessdate=2020-09-04 |url=https://www.espn.com/nba/story/_/id/7595841/nba-jeremy-lin-race-lessons-learned |archive-date=2020-05-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200525082901/https://www.espn.com/nba/story/_/id/7595841/nba-jeremy-lin-race-lessons-learned |dead-url=no }}</ref>。美國亞裔記者協會向媒體發佈一套指導方針，回應協會所稱「關於林書豪背景的不準確事實，以及數量驚人、報導亞裔（Asians）或美國亞裔的刻板印象的文章」<ref>{{cite news |last=Stableford |first=Dylan |title=Asian American Journalists Association releases guidelines on Jeremy Lin media coverage |date=2012-02-23 |publisher=Yahoo |accessdate=2020-09-04 |url=https://news.yahoo.com/blogs/cutline/asian-american-journalists-association-releases-guidelines-jeremy-lin-155822233.html |archive-date=2020-05-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200522173911/https://news.yahoo.com/blogs/cutline/asian-american-journalists-association-releases-guidelines-jeremy-lin-155822233.html |dead-url=no }}{{Cbignore}}</ref><ref>{{cite news |title=AAJA Media Advisory on Jeremy Lin News Coverage |date=2012-02-23 |publisher=channelapa |accessdate=2020-09-04 |url=http://www.channelapa.com/2012/02/aaja-media-advisory-on-jeremy-lin-news-coverage.html |archive-date=2012-03-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120301110134/http://www.channelapa.com/2012/02/aaja-media-advisory-on-jeremy-lin-news-coverage.html |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。

2021年2月，林書豪透過社群媒體發文表示，「身為美國亞裔並不代表沒有歷經過貧窮和種族歧視，身為擁有9年NBA資歷的老將，仍無法保護我免於在球場上被人稱作『冠狀病毒』」<ref>{{cite news |author1=Janie McCauley |title=Warriors G League G Jeremy Lin experienced racism on court |url=https://apnews.com/article/nba-steve-kerr-jeremy-lin-san-francisco-media-ab2442fc2113603f23382298c5074049 |accessdate=2021-03-02 |work=AP |date=2021-02-27 |quote=Being an Asian American doesn’t mean we don’t experience poverty and racism. Being a 9-year NBA veteran doesn’t protect me from being called ‘coronavirus’ on the court. |archive-date=2021-02-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210228080730/https://apnews.com/article/nba-steve-kerr-jeremy-lin-san-francisco-media-ab2442fc2113603f23382298c5074049 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。NBA G聯盟對於林書豪被人稱作「冠狀病毒」一事展開調查<ref>{{cite news |author1=Nick Friedell |title=G League looking into claim made by Jeremy Lin that he was called 'coronavirus' on court |url=https://www.espn.com/nba/story/_/id/30971234/g-league-looking-claim-made-jeremy-lin-was-called-coronavirus-court |accessdate=2021-03-01 |work=ESPN |date=2021-02-27 |archive-date=2021-03-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210305044504/https://www.espn.com/nba/story/_/id/30971234/g-league-looking-claim-made-jeremy-lin-was-called-coronavirus-court |dead-url=no }}</ref>。林書豪則再次發文表示，自己並沒有要點名或羞辱任何人<ref>{{cite news |title=Jeremy Lin says he's 'not naming or shaming anyone' in wake of claim he was called 'coronavirus' on court |url=https://www.espn.com/nba/story/_/id/30973491/jeremy-lin-says-not-naming-shaming-anyone-wake-claim-was-called-coronavirus-court |accessdate=2021-03-01 |work=ESPN |date=2021-02-27 |archive-date=2021-03-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210305223633/https://www.espn.com/nba/story/_/id/30973491/jeremy-lin-says-not-naming-shaming-anyone-wake-claim-was-called-coronavirus-court |dead-url=no }}</ref>。林書豪在3月接受[[CNN|CNN]]專訪時說，大學時期就曾多次遭受種族歧視言論攻擊，但從未透露這些球員是誰，並相信[[2019冠状病毒病|2019冠状病毒病]]只是暴露其中一個潛在問題，「比起審判或譴責，我更希望看到人們花很多時間去聆聽」<ref>{{cite news |author1=Don Lemon |author2=Ben Church |title='Boiling up': Former NBA star Jeremy Lin says Covid-19 has sparked anti-Asian violence in the US |url=https://edition.cnn.com/2021/03/03/sport/nba-jeremy-lin-racism-asian-american-spt-intl/index.html |accessdate=2021-03-04 |work=CNN |date=2021-03-03 |archive-date=2021-03-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210307160515/https://edition.cnn.com/2021/03/03/sport/nba-jeremy-lin-racism-asian-american-spt-intl/index.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。事後NBA G聯盟以林書豪支持的內部方式完成調查，林書豪與該名球員見面，談及美國亞裔遭受種族歧視與暴力事件增加的情況，該名球員則了解其用詞對林書豪造成的影響。而NBA G聯盟不會對外公開該名球員的身份<ref>{{cite news |author1=Shams Charania |author2=The Athletic Staff |title=G League completes investigation into Lin's claim he was called 'coronavirus' |url=https://theathletic.com/news/g-league-completes-investigation-into-lins-claim-he-was-called-coronavirus/dgBXPaHsVi1w |accessdate=2021-03-13 |work=The Athletic |date=2021-03-12 |archive-date=2021-03-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210316184242/https://theathletic.com/news/g-league-completes-investigation-into-lins-claim-he-was-called-coronavirus/dgBXPaHsVi1w |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

