林書豪擁有一個受歡迎的[[YouTube|YouTube]]帳號<ref>{{cite web | last=Roberts | first=Daniel | title=Can YouTube revive Linsanity? | website=Fortune | date=2014-09-26 | url=https://fortune.com/2014/09/26/youtube-jeremy-lin/ | accessdate=2016-05-14 | archive-date=2016-05-15 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160515083142/http://fortune.com/2014/09/26/youtube-jeremy-lin/ | dead-url=no }}</ref>。林書豪與前紐約尼克隊友[[兰德里·菲尔兹|兰德里·菲尔兹]]在頻道影片中展示他們的「秘密握手」<ref>{{cite web |url=http://offthebench.nbcsports.com/2012/03/18/jeremy-lin-and-landry-fields-handshake-finally-revealed-video/ |title=Jeremy Lin and Landry Fields secret handshake finally revealed (video) |publisher=NBC Sports |accessdate=2012-04-22 |archive-date=2012-05-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120519201531/http://offthebench.nbcsports.com/2012/03/18/jeremy-lin-and-landry-fields-handshake-finally-revealed-video/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。2014年{{tsl|en|Whistle Sports Network|哨聲運動網}}以大約40萬訂閱者換取未公開的股權、加入林書豪的YouTube頻道，林書豪則成為哨聲運動網的內容合作夥伴。他是[[北美職業體育聯賽|北美職業體育聯賽]]中首位替數位體育平臺製作內容的運動員<ref name="bloomberg_09262014">{{cite news |title=Jeremy Lin passed up big Linsanity payday |date=2014-09-26 |newspaper=Los Angeles Times |agency=Bloomberg News |accessdate=2020-09-04 |url=https://www.latimes.com/sports/chi-jeremy-lin-passed-up-big-linsanity-payday-20140926-story.html |archive-date=2019-10-31 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191031214417/https://www.latimes.com/sports/chi-jeremy-lin-passed-up-big-linsanity-payday-20140926-story.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

2011年7月，[[海外華人|海外華人]]《生動雜誌》（Vivid Magazine）將林書豪評為八大有影響力的[[华裔美国人|华裔美国人]]之一<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.newsabahtimes.com.my/nstweb/fullstory/50483 |title=New Sabah Times |publisher=New Sabah Times |date=2011-07-17 |accessdate=2011-08-04 |dead-url=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110930131515/http://www.newsabahtimes.com.my/nstweb/fullstory/50483 |archivedate=2011-09-30 }}</ref>。2012年4月，林書豪入選《[[時代雜誌|時代雜誌]]》[[时代百大人物|百大最具影響力人物]]<ref>{{cite news |title=Jeremy Lin - 2012 TIME 100: The Most Influential People in the World |date=2012-04-18 |work=Time |url=http://www.time.com/time/specials/packages/article/0,28804,2111975_2111976_2111945,00.html |accessdate=2012-04-18 |archive-date=2012-04-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120419005414/http://www.time.com/time/specials/packages/article/0,28804,2111975_2111976_2111945,00.html |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。6月18日，[[NBA_TV|NBA TV]]宣布林書豪是首屆「年度社群人氣球員獎」（Social Breakout Player of the Year）得獎者<ref>{{cite news |author1=Jared Zwerling |title=Lin wins 'Social Breakout Player of the Year' |url=https://www.espn.com/blog/new-york-knicks/post/_/id/20937/lin-wins-social-breakout-player-of-the-year |accessdate=2020-09-04 |work=ESPN |date=2012-06-18 |archive-date=2020-11-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201121175240/https://www.espn.com/blog/new-york-knicks/post/_/id/20937/lin-wins-social-breakout-player-of-the-year |dead-url=no }}</ref>，同時還獲頒「史詩獎」（Epic Award）<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.nba.com/2012/news/features/07/09/2012-social-media-awards/index.html|title=2011–12 Social Media Award Winners|publisher=NBA|date=2012-07-12|accessdate=2012-07-18|dead-url=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120713121858/http://www.nba.com/2012/news/features/07/09/2012-social-media-awards/index.html|archivedate=2012-07-13}}</ref>。林書豪同年7月獲頒{{tsl|en|ESPY Award|ESPY獎}}的「{{tsl|en|Best Breakthrough Athlete ESPY Award|ESPY年度最佳突破運動員獎|年度最佳突破運動員獎}}」<ref>{{cite news |title=LeBron James big winner at ESPYS |url=https://www.espn.com/espys/story/_/id/8158208/lebron-james-justin-verlander-robert-griffin-iii-espy-nominees |accessdate=2020-09-04 |work=ESPN |date=2012-07-12 |archive-date=2019-01-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190120093921/http://www.espn.com/espys/story/_/id/8158208/lebron-james-justin-verlander-robert-griffin-iii-espy-nominees |dead-url=no }}</ref>。2014年[[杜莎夫人蠟像館|杜莎夫人蠟像館]]舊金山分館推出林書豪的肖像蠟像<ref name="pincus_08212014"/>。

=== 「林來瘋」 ===
{{Redirect|Linsanity|林來瘋的紀錄片|林書豪旋瘋}}
在林書豪成為紐約尼克的先發球員後，[[美联社|美联社]]稱林書豪是「NBA最令人驚訝的故事」<ref>{{cite news |title=It's Lin-Mania in the NBA as Jeremy jams Kobe |date=2012-02-11 |location=Canada |publisher=[[加拿大廣播公司|加拿大廣播公司]] |agency=Associated Press |accessdate=2020-09-04 |url=https://www.cbc.ca/sports/basketball/nba/it-s-lin-mania-in-the-nba-as-jeremy-jams-kobe-1.1145877 |archive-date=2020-03-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200325190150/https://www.cbc.ca/sports/basketball/nba/it-s-lin-mania-in-the-nba-as-jeremy-jams-kobe-1.1145877 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。[[彭博新聞社|彭博新聞社]]寫道，林書豪「已經成為最著名的（亞裔美籍NBA球員）」。紐約尼克的球迷以姓氏「林」（Lin）為林書豪取許多綽號<ref>{{cite news |last=Hsu |first=Hua |title=Love Jeremy Lin Without Asian, Harvard, NBA Stereotypes: Hua Hsu |date=2012-02-10 |agency=Bloomberg News |accessdate=2020-09-04 |url=https://www.bloomberg.com/opinion/articles/2012-02-10/love-lin-without-asian-harvard-nba-stereotypes-commentary-by-hua-hsu |archive-date=2021-03-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210324032735/https://www.bloomberg.com/opinion/articles/2012-02-10/love-lin-without-asian-harvard-nba-stereotypes-commentary-by-hua-hsu |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |last=Flegenheimer |first=Matt |title=A Player's Rise, Charted on Twitter |date=2012-02-12 |page=MB4 |newspaper=The New York Times |accessdate=2020-09-04 |url=https://www.nytimes.com/2012/02/12/nyregion/jeremy-lins-rise-charted-in-tweets.html |archive-date=2019-10-31 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191031214414/https://www.nytimes.com/2012/02/12/nyregion/jeremy-lins-rise-charted-in-tweets.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。其中最受歡迎的綽號是「林來瘋」（Linsanity），意思為對不被看好的林書豪感到興奮<ref>{{cite news |title=Lin-sanity Accepted into English Lexicon ... Lin-ough already!? |date=2012-02-24 |publisher={{tsl|en|Global Language Monitor|全球語言觀察機構}} |accessdate=2020-09-04 |url=https://languagemonitor.com/new-words/lin-sanity-accepted-into-english-lexicon-lin-ough-already |archive-date=2018-10-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181005221205/http://www.languagemonitor.com/new-words/lin-sanity-accepted-into-english-lexicon-lin-ough-already |dead-url=yes }}</ref><ref>{{cite journal |title=Linsanity and the shaking of interethnic boundary |first=Guo-Ming |last=Chen |year=2012 |journal=Asian Ethnicity |volume=13 |issue=4 |pages=469–471 |doi=10.1080/14631369.2012.710070 |quote=Other newly coined words, including English such as 'Lincredible', 'Linpossible', 'Linderella', 'Super Lintendo', and 'Legend in New York', and Chinese such as 'haoshen' (Lin as god), 'haoge' (Lin as brother), and 'haoxiaozi' (Lin as buddy)}}</ref>。《時代雜誌》網頁刊登一篇名為「已經官方認證：林來瘋（Linsanity）是真實」的文章<ref>{{cite news |last=Gregory |first=Sean |title=It's Official: Linsanity Is for Real |date=2012-02-11 |work=Time |accessdate=2020-09-04 |url=https://newsfeed.time.com/2012/02/11/its-official-linsanity-is-for-real/ |archive-date=2020-06-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200602131911/https://newsfeed.time.com/2012/02/11/its-official-linsanity-is-for-real/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。其他雙關語還包括「{{tsl|en|Words with Friends|與朋友對話|與林對話}}」（Words with Lin）、「[[灰姑娘|林灰姑娘]]」（Linderella）、「林驚奇」（Lincredible）和「[[超級任天堂|超級林天堂]]」（Super Lintendo）{{r|mahoney20120211}}。

[[奈史密斯篮球名人纪念堂|名人堂]]球員[[魔术师约翰逊|魔术师约翰逊]]表示，「（林書豪）在<!--原文為「the Garden」-->[[麦迪逊广场花园|（麥迪遜廣場）花園]]<!--原文為「the Garden」-->所引起激動人心的事情，老兄，我已經很久沒目睹過了」。美聯社將林書豪和[[提姆·提伯|提姆·提伯]]作比對<ref name="mahoney20120211">{{cite news |last=Mahoney |first=Brian |title=Linsanity: Knicks benchwarmer becomes a star |date=2012-02-11 |agency=Associated Press |accessdate=2020-09-04 |url=https://www.foxnews.com/sports/linsanity-knicks-benchwarmer-becomes-a-star |archive-date=2020-11-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201106003031/https://www.foxnews.com/sports/linsanity-knicks-benchwarmer-becomes-a-star |dead-url=no }}</ref>。林書豪出現在《[[運動畫刊|運動畫刊]]》的封面，標題是「克服一切困難」；《[[泰晤士報|泰晤士報]]》稱林書豪在《運動畫刊》的封面為「最偉大的致敬」<ref>{{cite news |last=Beck |first=Howard |title=At the Buzzer, It's All Lin |date=2012-02-15 |newspaper=The New York Times |accessdate=2020-09-04 |page=B10 |url=https://www.nytimes.com/2012/02/15/sports/basketball/at-the-buzzer-its-all-jeremy-lin-as-knicks-edge-raptors.html |archive-date=2020-06-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200615142647/https://www.nytimes.com/2012/02/15/sports/basketball/at-the-buzzer-its-all-jeremy-lin-as-knicks-edge-raptors.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。他還登上《時代雜誌》的亞洲封面；《[[福布斯|福布斯]]》寫道，「恭喜林書豪，你現在登上《時代雜誌》封面的次數和[[迈克尔·乔丹|迈克尔·乔丹]]一樣多」<ref>{{cite magazine |last=Badenhausen |first=Kurt |title=Time Magazine Picks Jeremy Lin For Cover After Five Games |date=2012-02-17 |magazine=Forbes |accessdate=2020-09-04 |url=https://www.forbes.com/sites/kurtbadenhausen/2012/02/17/time-magazine-picks-jeremy-lin-for-cover-after-five-games/#564bcdcf2c99 |archive-date=2019-12-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191212153434/https://www.forbes.com/sites/kurtbadenhausen/2012/02/17/time-magazine-picks-jeremy-lin-for-cover-after-five-games/#564bcdcf2c99 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。林書豪的故事也登上許多[[臺北|臺北]]報紙的頭版頭條<ref name="brandsher02152012"/>。時任NBA主席[[大卫·斯特恩|大卫·斯特恩]]表示，「我沒有做過計算，但可以說在我所知道的任何運動項目當中，沒有一位球員能在這麼短的時間內，像林書豪那樣引起人們的興趣與狂熱」<ref>{{cite news |title=David Stern fascinated by Jeremy Lin |date=2012-02-24 |publisher=ESPN |agency=Associated Press |accessdate=2020-09-04 |url=https://www.espn.com/new-york/nba/story/_/id/7608874/david-stern-says-never-seen-anything-jeremy-lin-frenzy |archive-date=2020-05-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200525073931/https://www.espn.com/new-york/nba/story/_/id/7608874/david-stern-says-never-seen-anything-jeremy-lin-frenzy |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

