在他成為紐約尼克先發球員之後不到三週的時間，至少有7本關於林書豪的[[電子書|電子書]]出版<ref>{{cite news | url=https://www.cnet.com/news/linsanity-already-hitting-e-bookstores-near-you/ | title='Linsanity' already hitting e-bookstores near you | publisher=CNet | date=2012-02-22 | accessdate=2012-02-22 | author=Terdiman, Daniel | archive-date=2014-04-19 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140419181314/http://www.cnet.com/news/linsanity-already-hitting-e-bookstores-near-you/ | dead-url=no }}</ref>。{{tsl|en|Global Language Monitor|全球語言觀察機構}}則宣布「林來瘋」（Linsanity）已經達到可被視為英語單字的標準<ref>{{cite news |title='Lin-sanity' becomes part of the English language |date=2012-02-23 |agency=ABS-CBN |accessdate=2020-09-04 |url=https://news.abs-cbn.com/sports/02/23/12/lin-sanity-becomes-part-english-language |archive-date=2019-03-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190327091325/https://news.abs-cbn.com/sports/02/23/12/lin-sanity-becomes-part-english-language |dead-url=no }}</ref>。他連續第二次出現在《運動畫刊》的封面，是該雜誌歷史上首位發生在紐約球隊的運動員身上<ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.foxnews.com/sports/knicks-jeremy-lin-makes-2nd-straight-si-cover|title=Knicks' Jeremy Lin makes 2nd straight SI cover|date=2012-02-22|agency=Associated Press|accessdate=2012-02-22|archive-date=2020-11-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201106003105/https://www.foxnews.com/sports/knicks-jeremy-lin-makes-2nd-straight-si-cover|dead-url=no}}</ref>，也是該雜誌歷史上第三位NBA球員達成此舉<ref>{{cite news|url=https://sports.yahoo.com/jeremy-lin-scores-second-straight-sports-illustrated-cover-183535682.html|title=Jeremy Lin scores his second straight Sports Illustrated cover, joining some lofty company|publisher=Yahoo! Sports|date=2012-02-22|accessdate=2012-02-22|author=Dwyer, Kelly|archive-date=2020-11-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201121175440/https://sports.yahoo.com/jeremy-lin-scores-second-straight-sports-illustrated-cover-183535682.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。紐約市的餐館推出致敬林書豪的新食品和酒吧商品，[[燕京啤酒|燕京啤酒]]的銷量也隨之上升<ref>{{cite news |last=Kayal |first=Michele |title=Jeremy Lin fever reaches into restaurants and bars |date=2012-02-17 |agency=Associated Press |accessdate=2020-09-04 |url=https://www.foxnews.com/food-drink/jeremy-lin-fever-reaches-into-restaurants-and-bars |archive-date=2020-11-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201106003116/https://www.foxnews.com/food-drink/jeremy-lin-fever-reaches-into-restaurants-and-bars |dead-url=no }}</ref>{{r|beck_07162012}}。紐約市約有{{tsl|en|Demographics of New York City|紐約市地理|45萬華裔或臺裔居民}}，比[[迈阿密|迈阿密]]、[[亚特兰大|亚特兰大]]或[[克利夫兰|克利夫兰]]等等同樣擁有NBA球隊的城市的加總人口還要多；觀看林書豪比賽的觀賽派對在[[曼哈頓華埠|曼哈頓華埠]]興盛起來<ref name="beck_07162012">{{cite news |last=Beck |first=Howard |title=For Fans of Knicks, Conflict Over Lin |date=2012-07-17 |newspaper=The New York Times |accessdate=2020-09-04 |url=https://www.nytimes.com/2012/07/17/sports/basketball/jeremy-lins-future-with-new-york-knicks-is-dividing-fans.html |archive-date=2019-03-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190327091914/https://www.nytimes.com/2012/07/17/sports/basketball/jeremy-lins-future-with-new-york-knicks-is-dividing-fans.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="silver_07162012"/>。一家航空公司打出「林-{}-瘋狂低價」（Linsanely low prices）廣告<ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.chicagotribune.com/news/ct-xpm-2012-02-21-ct-talk-jeremy-lin-spirit-airlines-0222-20120222-story.html|title=Airline hopes to score with 'Linsanely low fares'|work=Chicago Tribune|date=2012-02-21|accessdate=2012-02-22|author=Manker, Rob|archive-date=2021-07-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210715215459/https://www.chicagotribune.com/news/ct-xpm-2012-02-21-ct-talk-jeremy-lin-spirit-airlines-0222-20120222-story.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。他的{{tsl|en|rookie card|新秀卡片}}在[[EBay|EBay]]上的競拍價超過2.1萬美元<ref>{{cite news|url=http://content.usatoday.com/communities/gameon/post/2012/02/jeremy-lin-rookie-card-now-past-20000-in-bidding/1|title=Jeremy Lin rookie card now past $20,000 in bidding|work=USA Today|date=2012-02-23|accessdate=2012-02-23|author=Cherner, Reid|archive-date=2012-07-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120714120741/http://content.usatoday.com/communities/gameon/post/2012/02/jeremy-lin-rookie-card-now-past-20000-in-bidding/1|dead-url=no}}</ref>。當時媒體謠傳他與[[金·卡戴珊|金·卡戴珊]]在約會，但被林書豪本人否認<ref>{{cite news|title=Jeremy Lin: I'm not dating divorced Kim Kardashian|url=http://content.usatoday.com/communities/gameon/post/2012/02/jeremy-lin-no-im-not-dating-kim-kardashian-rachel-nichols-espn-abc-new-york-knicks-kris-humphries-new-jersey-nets-abc-good-morning-america/1|work=USA Today|date=2012-02-20|accessdate=2012-02-22|author=McCarthy, Michael|archive-date=2012-02-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120221205426/http://content.usatoday.com/communities/gameon/post/2012/02/jeremy-lin-no-im-not-dating-kim-kardashian-rachel-nichols-espn-abc-new-york-knicks-kris-humphries-new-jersey-nets-abc-good-morning-america/1|dead-url=no}}</ref>。《[[外交政策_(杂志)|外交政策]]》猜測他對[[中美关系|中美关系]]的潛在影響<ref>{{cite news|url=https://foreignpolicy.com/2012/02/22/jeremy-lin-and-u-s-china-relations/|title=Jeremy Lin and U.S.-China relations|work=Foreign Policy|date=2012-02-22|accessdate=2012-02-22|author=Inboden, Will|archive-date=2015-01-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150104163107/http://foreignpolicy.com/2012/02/22/jeremy-lin-and-u-s-china-relations/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。[[傑克·威爾許|傑克·威爾許]]與{{tsl|en|Suzy Welch|蘇茜·威爾許}}撰文指，林書豪的崛起是對商業領袖的一個教訓，別讓官僚主義扼殺冷略具天份的人材<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://blogs.reuters.com/jack-and-suzy-welch/2012/02/24/jeremy-lin-lessons-from-the-lin-sanity/ |title=Jeremy Lin: Lessons from the Lin-sanity |author=[[傑克·威爾許|傑克·威爾許]]、{{tsl|en|Suzy Welch|蘇茜·威爾許}} |date=2012-02-24 |accessdate=2012-09-07 |archive-date=2020-03-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200325190206/http://blogs.reuters.com/jack-and-suzy-welch/2012/02/24/jeremy-lin-lessons-from-the-lin-sanity/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。儘管林書豪突然成名，[[沙加緬度國王|沙加緬度國王]]教練{{tsl|en|Keith Smart|基思·斯馬特}}表示，「在他還是林狂熱（Linmania）之前，我就認識（林書豪）。他還是那位謙遜的傢伙。這傢伙一點都沒變，以年輕人來說真的很特別」<ref>{{cite news|last=Mahoney|first=Brian|title=Lin has 13 assists, Knicks run win streak to 7|url=http://sports.yahoo.com/nba/recap?gid=2012021518|accessdate=2012-02-16|newspaper=AP|date=2012-02-16|archive-date=2012-02-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120216154503/http://sports.yahoo.com/nba/recap?gid=2012021518|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

林書豪2012年註冊「林來瘋」（Linsanity）的商標，防止不明人士從他的肖像中獲利<ref name="torre_03272015">{{cite news |last=Torre |first=Pablo S. |title=Isolation Play |date=2015-03-27 |work=ESPN The Magazine |accessdate=2020-09-04 |url=https://www.espn.com/espn/feature/story/_/id/12561636/inside-jeremy-lin-life-linsanity-new-york-knicks |archive-date=2020-06-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200629070613/https://www.espn.com/espn/feature/story/_/id/12561636/inside-jeremy-lin-life-linsanity-new-york-knicks |dead-url=no }}</ref>。有兩位人士在2月第一週曾試圖註冊該商標，但[[美国专利及商标局|美国专利及商标局]]最終將該商標交由給林書豪註冊<ref>{{cite news |last=Dwyer |first=Kelly |title=Jeremy Lin awarded the trademark to the word 'Linsanity,' but his next deal in New York will be complicated |date=2012-05-30 |publisher=Yahoo! Sports |accessdate=2020-09-04 |url=https://sports.yahoo.com/jeremy-lin-awarded-trademark-word-linsanity-next-deal-135054331.html |archive-date=2020-11-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201121175551/https://sports.yahoo.com/jeremy-lin-awarded-trademark-word-linsanity-next-deal-135054331.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。一部關於林書豪的[[紀錄片|紀錄片]]《[[林書豪旋瘋|林書豪旋瘋]]》2013年1月20日在[[圣丹斯电影节|圣丹斯电影节]]首映<ref>{{cite news |title=Linsanity Comes to CAAMFest Opening Night |date=2013-01-31 |work=Asian Week |accessdate=2020-09-04 |url=http://www.asianweek.com/2013/01/31/linsanity-comes-to-caamfest-opening-night/ |archive-date=2013-02-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130207062813/http://www.asianweek.com/2013/01/31/linsanity-comes-to-caamfest-opening-night/ |dead-url=yes }}</ref>，該片在進入[[藝術電影|藝術影院]]之前，曾在眾多[[电影节|电影节]]放映<ref>{{cite news |last=Freedman |first=Samuel G. |title=Off the Court, a Film's Lens on Asian-American Faith |date=2013-11-16 |newspaper=The New York Times |accessdate=2020-09-04 |url=https://www.nytimes.com/2013/11/16/us/off-the-court-a-documentarys-lens-on-asian-american-christianity.html |archive-date=2020-06-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200607190812/https://www.nytimes.com/2013/11/16/us/off-the-court-a-documentarys-lens-on-asian-american-christianity.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

[[班傑利公司|班傑利公司]]為了致敬林書豪，製作一款名為「嘗嘗林明智（Taste The Lin-Sanity）」的冷凍優格，它包含荔枝蜂蜜醬（lychee honey swirls）和幸運餅乾片。該公司後來用[[窩夫|窩夫]]餅乾取代幸運餅乾，並向任何被「林明智」（Lin-Sanity）味道冒犯的人道歉<ref>{{cite news|last=Rocheleau|first=Matt|title=Ben & Jerry's launches 'Lin-Sanity' flavor, takes out fortune cookie ingredient|date=2012-02-24|newspaper=Boston Globe|url=http://www.boston.com/yourtown/news/cambridge/2012/02/ben_jerrys_launches_limited-re.html|accessdate=2012-02-24|quote='There seemed to be a bit of an initial backlash about it, but we obviously weren't looking to offend anybody and the majority of the feedback about it has been positive,' he said.|archive-date=2016-03-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304194850/http://www.boston.com/yourtown/news/cambridge/2012/02/ben_jerrys_launches_limited-re.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|title=Ben & Jerry's sorry for fortune cookies|date=2012-02-26|publisher=ESPN|url=http://espn.go.com/new-york/nba/story/_/id/7617213/ben-jerry-apologizes-lin-sanity-flavor|accessdate=2012-02-26|quote='We offer a heartfelt apology if anyone was offended by our handmade Lin-Sanity flavor', Ben & Jerry's said in a statement.|archive-date=2012-02-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120229014331/http://espn.go.com/new-york/nba/story/_/id/7617213/ben-jerry-apologizes-lin-sanity-flavor|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

